(24, 1, 'Bastien Industries ', 'bastien.industries@qc.aira.com', '160, rue Jeune Lorette, WENDAKE - Quebec, , ', 'www.bastienindustries.ca', '+1 (418) 842-9819 ', '+1 (418) 842-1330 ', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bastien Industries is a manufacturer of Indian moccasins and leather novelties. Hiawatha trademark Moccasins have been made by local Huron artisans for over 25 years. A catalogue of products is available. BASTIEN INDUSTRIES is located north of Quebec city at Village Huron (Wendake). Our company is famous for the excellence of his moccasins, snowshoes and indian novelties. Maurice Bastien, former Grand Chief of Huron-Wendat tribe, was an expert in the production of snowshoes, to which he confined his manufacturing operations until he started the manufacture of moccasins. The popular HIAWATHA brand of handbeaded moccasins, which bear the skilful needlecraft of the majority of the women of Wendake village, are distributed to many parts of the world. Descendants of the Huron-Wendat tribe will be found carrying on the work of their ancestors, going to their daily work in the Bastien factory, making moccasins and indian novelties. M. Roland Bastien created Bastien Industries in 1972.</p>', ''),
(12, 1, 'Hilal Technology', 'info@hilaltechnology.com', '7433 Wiseman Ave., Montreal, QC, Canada', 'www.hilaltechnology.com', '514-279-5666', '514-991-5677', '', '<p><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #339966\"><em><strong>Hilal Technology</strong></em></span> is an internet based company specializing in web programming and more specifically web based Content Management Systems (CMS). We are constantly pushing the boundaries of cutting edge web technology, with a strong emphasis on object-oriented software design practices and principles. As a collective business unit, we provide our clients with a wide array of technical expertise that are sought after in the industry, including web design, object oriented programming, software engineering, technical documentation, graphic design, internet marketing, search engine optimization and traffic generation.</span></span></p>\r\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">We are a web development/design company specializing in creating unique and effective web solutions. We assist individuals and small businesses through the process of creating professional design projects. As a small business ourselves, we realize how important your time is. Our goal is to handle your design project from start to finish, so you can focus on what you do best: running your business We are shaping the digital future by providing unique online functional and presentational development for the global business community through turnkey web strategy, design and technology solutions.</span></span></p>\r\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: smaller\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #339966\"><em><strong>Hilal Technology</strong></em></span> offers a wide range of services including professional web design and web development, Web Hosting and Domain registrations, customized e-commerce solutions, Internet marketing and promotional services, corporate identity and 3D-modeling services for business owners desiring a cost-effective website and excellent search engine results.</span></span></p>', ''),
(19, 1, 'International Play Company ', 'sales@iplayco.com', '20216-98th Avenue, Langley - BC , , ', 'www.iplayco.com', '+1-604-882-1188', '+1-604-882-1977', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\">We design, manufacture and install affordable indoor and outdoor play structures. Creative theming is available and many activities and interactive events offer fun and excitement for children of all ages. We have installed in over 40 countries worldwide. All of our playgrounds meet the high standards for safety worldwide. The play equipment of both IPC indoor and outdoor divisions are theme orientated and designed to inspire a child&rsquo;s imagination. It is the business objective to provide a line of safe interactive play environments, which stimulate a child&rsquo;s mind and body.</p>', ''),
(25, 1, 'Dylis Innovative Systems Inc.', 'dylis@dylis.com', '1401 Meyerside Dr, MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, , ', 'www.dylis.com', '+1 (905) 564-6436 ', '+1 (905) 564-7840', '', '<p>Dylis Innovative Systems has been a designer and manufacturer of intelligent automation based solutions for more than ten years. Our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction is reflected in all we do from simple workstations to turnkey assembly lines. All of our equipment is built utilizing standard components in a custom engineered solution. Dylis Innovative Systems started out in the field of flexible automation providing robotic tooling and fixturing solutions to local manufacturers. As our company grew, the depth of our staff\'s expertise expended and we began to develop specialpurpose assembly and material handling equipment for applications not suited to robotics. Today we offer a blend of flexible automation and custom engineered solutions to manufacturers through out North America.</p>', ''),
