(54, 1, 'Parfumerie Reynard Ltee', 'reynard@colba.net ', '6465, rte Transcanadienne, SAINT-LAURENT, Quebec, , ', 'www.cires-epilatoires.com ', '+1 (514) 856-6996', '+1 (514) 856-6999 ', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\">Laboratoire Scientifique de Cosm&eacute;tologie specializes in the production of a complete assortment of depilatory products: &middot; COLD WAX (sugar base and water soluble) &middot; LUKEWARM LIQUID WAX (natural rosin base and oil soluble) &middot; HOT HARD WAX (beeswax base) We also manufacture and distribute &quot;Quick Bleach&quot;, a bleaching cream that lightens facial and body hair, as well as &quot;Bibicure After Waxing Cream&quot;. Our line of depilatory products is complemented by waxing accessories that include: cotton and pellon rolls (muslin) and stainless steel spatulas used in the application of wax. For professionals, we have a selection of products that meet the needs of those who specialize in aesthetic and beauty products. Please call us for more information on our professional products. Our hair removal waxes are sold, through representatives, in the United-States as well as in Panama, Japan and Australia.</p>', ''),
