(110, 1, 'A & D Bird Seed Inc.', 'giveusatweet@adbirdseed.com', '7535 Hwy 26, R.R. 2, STAYNER - , Ontario, Canada, ', 'www.adbirdseed.com', '+1-705-428-246', '+1-705-428-246', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi. and welcome to our home web nest, where we truly are &quot;for the birds&quot; and &quot;bird lovers&quot;. We pride ourselves in producing quality seed mixes with absolutely no fillers. Here at A&amp;D Bird Seed we want our feathered friends to enjoy everything you bird lovers put out for them. That means nothing is left on the ground for you to clean up, ok, maybe some sunflower casings but you get the idea. Click on our yummy feeding guide for what birds really like. Click on our &quot;seeds and mixes&quot; to see what we stock. Remember, we specialize in creating custom mixes for the birds you want to attract, so if you don\'t see a mix in stock, just ask and we\'ll make it for you. We will ship anywhere. If you are going to be in our neighborhood (greater downtown Stayner Ontario population 3,100) drop by for a tour of our corporate HQ and manufacturing plant.</p>', ''),
(111, 1, 'L.B. Manufacturing Inc. ', 'info@beaverpro.com', '671 Babin St, DIEPPE, New Brunswick, , ', 'www.beaverpro.com', '+1-506-388-3335', '+1-506- 388-3325', '', '<p>At L.B. Manufacturing we provide you with our own brand of cabs, custom parts, and accessories for your all terrain vehicles or all-terrain utility vehicles. Built tough for maximum dependability and versatility, our Beaver Pro cabs and accessories line gives hunters, farmers, fisherman, commercial, and recreational enthusiasts the opportunity to ride their machine with protection and style.  Using clever innovative design and the highest-quality materials available, we build with our customers in mind. Our products are easy to install and come with detailed instructions. Currently, we specialize in parts for the Arctic Cat Prowler, Polaris Ranger and Yamaha Rhino vehicles.  We are currently in R&amp;D to expand our line to other makes in the future. Contact your local Beaver Pro dealer for more information and pricing.</p>', ''),
(112, 1, 'HORUS Technologies Inc.', 'service@horus.ca ', '11-17075 Leslie St., NEWMARKET, Ontario, , ', 'www.horus.ca  ', '+1 (905) 895-7069', '+1 (905) 895-7069', '', '<p>HORUS Technologies Inc specializes in design, development, and manufacture of electronic control and instrumentation products. HORUS provides design and development expertise in mixed signal designs and embedded processor control solutions. HORUS supports low volume product manufacturing in-house, and provides technical product support for large volume manufacturing. HORUS provides Technical Service Support for Electrical/Electronic Instrumentation &amp; Control , Industrial Controls, Manufacturing Automation, Motion Control &amp; Material Handling Systems. HORUS manufactures and supports HVAC controls, Gas Monitoring Systems, Building Control &amp; Monitoring Systems, Tube Cutter Controls for Converting Industries, Thermal Electronic Controllers, Single Board Controllers, and support modules.</p>', ''),
