(115, 1, 'Plasticity Inc. ', 'jvoisin@go-plasticity.com ', '4620 Hilltop St, PIERREFONDS, Quebec, , ', 'www.go-plasticity.com  ', '+1 (519) 502-5030 ', '+1 (514) 335-6010 ', '', '<p>Along with it\'s partner companies Plasticity S.r.l and Outil DIMCO Tool, Plasticity Inc. designs and manufactures plastic injection moulds and plastic blow moulds for the consumer, recreational, plumbing, packaging and automotive industries. Leading edge technology and old world craftmanship combine to give our customers the advantage of working with a tooling partner that can contribute to their competitiveness. Please visit our website for more details and contact information.</p>', ''),
(116, 1, 'Reliable Food Service Equipment Inc. ', 'admin@restaurantequipmentdepot.com', '8-15 Connie Cres., CONCORD, Ontario, , ', 'www.restaurantequipmentdepot.com', '+1 (905) 738-6840', '+1 (416) 739-7271 ', '', '<p>The Restaurant Equipment Depot is made up of a group of companies that manufacture and distribute products for the local and export food service market since 1989. Our clients range from local restaurants and bakeries to nursing homes to theme parks.   To enter the sites of each of the companies, please click on one of the links below::   P.V.A. Enterprises Inc. The product offering ranges from cooking equipment to refrigerated units to small wares. Go to site   Reliable Food Service Equipment Inc. Reliable is a custom manufacturer of stainless steel products such as sinks, worktables, exhaust hoods, steam tables, dish tables, refrigerators and other custom-made products. Go to site    Waterjetcutting.ca - NEW Introducing the Calypso Shark 612 Waterjet cutting machine, one of the very few waterjets in the market that has dual heads capable of cutting all alloys (Stainless Steel, Steel, Aluminum) Marble, Granite, carbon Fibre, Stone, Glass, Brass, Copper, Corian, Copper ...</p>', ''),
(117, 1, 'IRT Integrated Rectifier Technologies Inc.', 'admin@irtrectifier.com', '15360, 116 Ave NW, EDMONTON, Alberta, , ', 'www.irtrectifier.com', '+1 (780) 447-1114', '+1 (780) 454-0004', '', '<p>IRT Integrated Rectifier Technologies, Inc. is an independent, employee-owned business that designs, manufactures and supplies rectifiers, control panels and related products for the corrosion industry.   As an Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) our company has the ability to meet the specific needs of clientele by ensuring dependable delivery of reliable products for a reasonable price.. The founding shareholders of IRT have over 110 years of combined experience in the rectifier manufacturing and  cathodic protection  industry in Canada, the United States and abroad.   We pride ourselves on our solid reputation knowing that our capabilities provide a solid base for business, which continues to grow through the establishment of strategic alliances with clients and by providing a high level of quality products and customer service.</p>', ''),
(118, 1, 'IRT Integrated Rectifier Technologies Inc.', 'admin@irtrectifier.com', '15360, 116 Ave NW, EDMONTON, Alberta, , ', 'www.irtrectifier.com', '+1 (780) 447-1114', '+1 (780) 454-0004', '', '<p>IRT Integrated Rectifier Technologies, Inc. is an independent, employee-owned business that designs, manufactures and supplies rectifiers, control panels and related products for the corrosion industry.   As an Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) our company has the ability to meet the specific needs of clientele by ensuring dependable delivery of reliable products for a reasonable price.. The founding shareholders of IRT have over 110 years of combined experience in the rectifier manufacturing and  cathodic protection  industry in Canada, the United States and abroad.   We pride ourselves on our solid reputation knowing that our capabilities provide a solid base for business, which continues to grow through the establishment of strategic alliances with clients and by providing a high level of quality products and customer service.</p>', ''),
(119, 1, 'Cobham Tracking & Locating Ltd. ', 'metter@cobhamtl.com', '271 Brownlow Ave, DARTMOUTH, Nova Scotia, , ', 'www.cobhamtl.com ', '+1 (902) 468-3007 ', '+1 (902) 468-3009 ', '', '<p>Cobham Tracking &amp; Locating Ltd. was formed January 2007 following the amalgamation of Orion Electronics Ltd. and Seimac Ltd. Together with its UK subsidiary, Micromill Electronics Ltd., Cobham Tracking &amp; Locating has more than 80 years of experience designing, manufacturing, delivering and supporting quality products.    The Cobham Tracking &amp; Locating Difference  Cobham Tracking &amp; Locating prides itself in providing turnkey solutions from initial concept, through design and manufacture, to training and support.   Research &amp; Development: We employ some of the brightest, most inquisitive minds in the business. Customers can choose from our extensive line of existing products or contract us to create customized solutions.   Quality Assurance: Every product we manufacture must pass a series of rigorous quality assurance tests before it leaves our facilities. Customers can rest easy knowing that the solutions they choose will perform consistently under the harshest of conditions.</p>', ''),
