(1910, 1, 'N. Jefferson Ltd', 'njefferson@shawcable.com', '22 5th Ave E, Vancouver, Br, Canada', 'www.njeffersonltd.com ', '(604) 873-4641', '(604) 873-4644', '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">N. Jefferson Ltd. has  supplied goods and services to Canadian retailers, wholesalers, and  manufacturers since 1926.&nbsp; As one of Canada&rsquo;s largest distributors of  sewing and quilting notions, we stock more than 29,000 sku&rsquo;s in our  30,000 square feet Vancouver warehouse.&nbsp; Our product line is supplied by  hundreds of suppliers from 34 countries around the world.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Our commitment to  provide a service level that sets us apart from our competitors is aimed  at helping you, our customer, reap the rewards of increased sales and  profits.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">We have developed  marketing partnerships with some of our suppliers, which allow us to act  as representatives for them in arranging drop shipments to you at  improved discounts.</p>', ''),
(1911, 1, ' NLP Technologies inc.', 'info@nlptechnologies.ca', '52 Le Royer St W, Montreal, Quebec, Canada', 'www.nlptechnologies.ca ', '(514) 733-8884', '', '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Based on the academic  study and research project of Dr. Atefeh Farzindar, the company was  established in February 2005 by Dr. Farzindar and Massoud Hosseiny, a  graduate of the &Eacute;cole Polytechnique of Montreal.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Through the use of its  patent-pending technologies of intelligent summarization and  translation, NLP Technologies is now providing primary-source legal  information to judges, lawyers, educators and other professionals in a  timely and comprehensive manner. By focusing on specific areas of law  such as Immigration, Intellectual Property, and Taxation, NLP supplies  easy access to case law through weekly bulletins, and specially-adapted  search solutions, as well as government statistics, and a virtual  library of provincial and federal legislation, international  instruments, manuals, forms etc. NLP&rsquo;s platform for presentation of  these materials is unique and user-friendly. NLP Technologies constantly  strives to improve its products and explore new ways to make the  practice of law easier.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">NLP Technologies is able  to produce high quality translation in a timely and cost effective  manner by using translation expertise and the latest in translation  technology in the form of CAT (Computer Aided Translation). Computer  Aided Translation, resulting from internal research and development,  combined with a translation management system (TMS) enabled NLP  Technologies, while maintaining translation quality and accuracy provide  a translation service over a continuous demand cycle, processing large  volumes of government documents.</p>', ''),
(1912, 1, 'Polaris Inflatable Boats (Canada) Ltd.', 'polaris@polarisboats.com', '8-5684 Landmark Way, Surrey, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.polarisboats.com', '(604) 534-5585', '(604) 534-2329', '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Here at Polaris  Inflatable Boats we build new and make replacement parts for high  quality watercraft. Whether you are looking for a durable river boat to  charge rapids or are law enforcement agencies looking for a perfect  rescue boat, we make exactly what you&rsquo;re looking for. Located in Canada,  we are a custom boat builder.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">We pride ourselves on  using state of the art high quality materials; along with exceptional  craftsmanship on everything we build. We have a full line of products to  meet your needs and a custom unit can be designed and built to your  individual requirements. Whether it is new boats, replacement parts or  much needed repairs, we are your one stop shop.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Located in Canada, we  are surrounded by many different sources of open water and understand  the need for diverse products that can survive in unique environments.  Riding tough rapids and rocky waters requires a strong inflatable boat.  Our Aluminum inflatable boats can compensate and withstand rough  surroundings while keeping passengers safe. We have many different sizes  to accommodate tours, guiding, search &amp; rescue and many other  commercial uses.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Fulfilling the needs of  Law Enforcement agencies can be extremely challenging, especially on  water. Here at Polaris Inflatable Boats we manufacture boats that are  fit to keep the United States and Canada safe and sound. Whether it is  foldable inflatable boats for discrete operations or aluminum inflatable  boats made to patrol waters, we are there to help protect and serve.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Our Canadian zodiac type  style inflatable boats are built to order and your boat will be one of a  kind. We specialize in custom accessorizing Polaris Ribs to meet your  needs and expectations. Or, if you are looking for inflatable boat  accessories, we have many available. Feel free to visit us or contact us  for more information on the services and products we provide.</p>', ''),
(1913, 1, 'Portes Garex ', 'info@portesgarex.com ', '610, rue Principale, VAL-ALAIN, Quebec, , ', 'www.portesgarex.com ', '+1 (418) 744-3317 ', '+1 (418) 744-3443 ', '', '<p>Mission Portes Garex is attentive to the tiniest details in the  choices it makes. We spare no effort in offering our customers quality  products, professional service, and fast delivery. Our expertise in  making steel and aluminum garage doors is recognized by industry  specialists. A highly qualified workforce on both the production floor  and in the sales office will guarantee you a product fully in line with  your expectations. Company profile Portes Garex is always looking for  and developing new technologies&mdash;a mark of leadership in a market with  constantly changing needs. The garage doors we market through reputable  specialized dealers result from the commitment of all our staff and  business partners. Portes Garex is an industry frontrunner. We hope to  be your first pick when choosing the garage door that best suits your  needs. Portes Garex is ISO 9001-2000 certified.</p>', ''),
(1914, 1, 'Portes Laforge Doors Ltd./Ltee', 'laforged@nb.aibn.com', '62, ch. Saint-Andre, SAINT-ANDRE, New Brunswick, Canada', 'www.laforgedoors.com ', '(506) 473-4034', '(506) 473-4283', '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Laforge Doors Ltd. is a 100,000 sq. ft. plant located in Grand Falls, New Brunswick, Canada.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">The company began  manufacturing wooden overhead doors in 1981 for residential, commercial  and industrial markets. In 1986, because of a growing demand, aluminum  and steel overhead doors were introduced to the production line.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Laforge Doors products are distributed throughout the world via the intermediary of distributors and dealers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">We know that when you  order a Laforge Door, you want it delivered on time and in one piece.  That is why we operate our own fleet of delivery trucks. Our experienced  team of drivers understand the importance of delivering doors to you  promptly and undamaged.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">We deliver in the Maritimes, Quebec and Ontario to owners and dealers</p>', ''),
