(1895, 253, 'Life Pearls', 'lifepearls04@gmail.com', NULL, 'https://lifepearls.com/', '1-844-331-7504', '', '936 moments to be treasured - Life Pearls is a unique baby shower gift that reminds parents of the importance of cherishing every moment with their child.', 'The Unique Gift For Baby Showers\r\nEvery parent says it, time flies. Each moment shared with your child is unique. Life Pearls is there to remind you of the importance of all these instants. Combining originality and elegance, the vase and pearls were conceived by a mom, for the new parents. With advice, activity ideas and encouragements, Life Pearls accompanies you, so that you can make the most of the joys of parenthood.\r\n', 'Baby shower ideas for a boy, newborn baby gifts, baby shower gift ideas for boys, unique baby boy gifts blog, new baby gift ideas, gifts for new baby, gifts for newborn, About best gift for new mom, cool baby shower gifts, new baby gift ideas'),
