(460, 1, 'Canadian Exports Corp.', 'info@canadianexports.org', '1315 Jules-Poitras, Suite: 202, Montreal, Qc. - , Canada,', 'www.canadianexports.org', '+1-877-575-2022', '+1-514-331-4775', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Welcome to Canada&rsquo;s first and only, Export Promotion Tool . &ldquo;Canadian Exports&rdquo; is a publication that helps International importers source the products and services they need from Canada. We offer assistance and guidance throughout the import/export process. You are welcome to contact us at any step of the way. Our services are: 1. Identifying and checking out any Canadian businesses for you. 2. Helping you contact them. 3. Facilitating your negotiations with them. 4. Arranging business travels to meet with them. 5. Informing you about Trade Missions, Business Delegations, Trade Fairs, Payment Terms and much more. To receive &ldquo;Canadian Exports&rdquo; publication, contact the Canadian business council or chamber of commerce in your country. Or, follow the link &ldquo;Join our Mailing List&rdquo; above and we will e-mail it to you for free. Be sure to visit our website frequently as it is updated daily. Contact us for all your inquiries. About Us (What is Canadian Exports) . &ldquo;Canadian Exports&rdquo; is a publication that matches Canadian &amp; International businesses; * Helps them find each other. * Helps them meet. * Helps them conclude successful business transactions. It is issued by &ldquo;Canadian Exports Inc&rdquo;, a Canadian company located in Montreal &ndash; Canada. &ldquo;Canadian Exports Inc&rdquo; offers a wide range of export-related consulting services that cover the entire import/export process. Our services are: * Identifying and checking out any market and/or business for you. * Helping you contact them. * Facilitating your negotiations with them. * Arranging business travels to meet with them. * Informing you about Trade Missions, Business Delegations, Trade Fairs, Payment Terms and much more. Contact us for more information to grow your business.</p>', ''),
(461, 1, 'Page Aviation', 'adrian@adrianpage.com ', '95 Lawrence Rd., BERWICK, Nova Scotia, , ', 'www.adrianpage.com  ', '+1 (902) 538-7395 ', '+1 (902) 538-7395 ', '', '<p>Manufacture laser cut radio controled model airplane kits. Electric or glow power 80&quot; Super Cub: Wing span: 80 inch, Fuselage length 50 inch, Weight 5 1/2 to 6 1/2 pounds (depends on power system used, Wing loading: 13 to 15 oz./sq. foot, Kit price: $159.95, Can be converted to glow power Mini Electric Super Cub, Wing span: 40 inch, Fuselage length 26 inch, Weight: 16 oz, Wing area: 230 sq.&quot;, Wing loading: aprx.10 oz./sq. foot, Kit price: $67.95, Can be converted to glow power.</p>', ''),
(462, 1, 'Plasticity Inc. ', 'jvoisin@go-plasticity.com ', '4620 Hilltop St, PIERREFONDS, Quebec, , ', 'www.go-plasticity.com  ', '+1 (519) 502-5030 ', '+1 (514) 335-6010 ', '', '<p>Along with it\'s partner companies Plasticity S.r.l and Outil DIMCO Tool, Plasticity Inc. designs and manufactures plastic injection moulds and plastic blow moulds for the consumer, recreational, plumbing, packaging and automotive industries. Leading edge technology and old world craftmanship combine to give our customers the advantage of working with a tooling partner that can contribute to their competitiveness. Please visit our website for more details and contact information.</p>', ''),
(463, 1, 'Polaris Inflatable Boats (Canada) Ltd. ', 'polaris@polarisboats.com', '101-20583 Langley Bypass, LANGLEY, British Columbia, , ', 'www.polarisboats.com', '+1 (604) 534-5585', '+1 (604) 534-2329', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Here at Polaris Inflatable Boats we build new and make replacement parts for high quality watercraft. Whether you are looking for a durable river boat to charge rapids or are law enforcement agencies looking for a perfect rescue boat, we make exactly what you&rsquo;re looking for. Located in Canada, we are a custom boat builder.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We pride ourselves on using state of the art high quality materials; along with exceptional craftsmanship on everything we build. We have a full line of products to meet your needs and a custom unit can be designed and built to your individual requirements. Whether it is new boats, replacement parts or much needed repairs, we are your one stop shop.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Located in Canada, we are surrounded by many different sources of open water and understand the need for diverse products that can survive in unique environments. Riding tough rapids and rocky waters requires a strong inflatable boat. Our Aluminum inflatable boats can compensate and withstand rough surroundings while keeping passengers safe. We have many different sizes to accommodate tours, guiding, search &amp; rescue and many other commercial uses.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Fulfilling the needs of Law Enforcement agencies can be extremely challenging, especially on water. Here at Polaris Inflatable Boats we manufacture boats that are fit to keep the United States and Canada safe and sound. Whether it is foldable inflatable boats for discrete operations or aluminum inflatable boats made to patrol waters, we are there to help protect and serve.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our Canadian zodiac type style inflatable boats are built to order and your boat will be one of a kind. We specialize in custom accessorizing Polaris Ribs to meet your needs and expectations. Or, if you are looking for inflatable boat accessories, we have many available. Feel free to visit us or contact us for more information on the services and products we provide.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(464, 1, 'Portes Garex ', 'info@portesgarex.com ', '610, rue Principale, VAL-ALAIN, Quebec, , ', 'www.portesgarex.com ', '+1 (418) 744-3317 ', '+1 (418) 744-3443 ', '', '<p>Mission Portes Garex is attentive to the tiniest details in the choices it makes. We spare no effort in offering our customers quality products, professional service, and fast delivery. Our expertise in making steel and aluminum garage doors is recognized by industry specialists. A highly qualified workforce on both the production floor and in the sales office will guarantee you a product fully in line with your expectations. Company profile Portes Garex is always looking for and developing new technologies&mdash;a mark of leadership in a market with constantly changing needs. The garage doors we market through reputable specialized dealers result from the commitment of all our staff and business partners. Portes Garex is an industry frontrunner. We hope to be your first pick when choosing the garage door that best suits your needs. Portes Garex is ISO 9001-2000 certified.</p>', ''),
(465, 1, 'Reliable Food Service Equipment Inc. ', 'admin@restaurantequipmentdepot.com', '8-15 Connie Cres., CONCORD, Ontario, , ', 'www.restaurantequipmentdepot.com', '+1 (905) 738-6840', '+1 (416) 739-7271 ', '', '<p>The Restaurant Equipment Depot is made up of a group of companies that manufacture and distribute products for the local and export food service market since 1989. Our clients range from local restaurants and bakeries to nursing homes to theme parks. To enter the sites of each of the companies, please click on one of the links below:: P.V.A. Enterprises Inc. The product offering ranges from cooking equipment to refrigerated units to small wares. Go to site Reliable Food Service Equipment Inc. Reliable is a custom manufacturer of stainless steel products such as sinks, worktables, exhaust hoods, steam tables, dish tables, refrigerators and other custom-made products. Go to site Waterjetcutting.ca - NEW Introducing the Calypso Shark 612 Waterjet cutting machine, one of the very few waterjets in the market that has dual heads capable of cutting all alloys (Stainless Steel, Steel, Aluminum) Marble, Granite, carbon Fibre, Stone, Glass, Brass, Copper, Corian, Copper ...</p>', ''),
