(561, 1, 'Antica Hirpinia', 'info@anticahirpinia.it', 'Via Iannacchini, Benevento, International, Canada', 'http://www.anticahirpinia.it/', '82774730', '082533013', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The vineyards of Ancient Hirpinia, extended on over 300 acres of land, are plants on the sunny hills of Irpinia. The terrain is characterized by a structure of type clay-limestone and poor in organic matter, is rich in elements potassium and phosphates. These features, combined with an ideal microclimate, have made it possible for thousands of years now, a growing indigenous grapes, identifying wine production irpina renowned for making the highest quality.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
