(575, 1, 'K-sons Truck Accessories', 'ksonstruckaccessories@yahoo.ca', 'P.O. Box 89, DIXONVILLE, Alberta, Canada', 'www.ksonstruckaccessories.com', '(780) 971-2464', '(780) 971-2464', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%;\">K-Sons Truck Accessories is focused on providing high-quality service and customer satisfaction &ndash; we will do everything we can to meet your expectations.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">At K-Sons Truck Accessories we provide Canadian companies and individuals with heavy-duty bumpers and grill guards to protect their fleet and personal pickup trucks. Whether you are in the gas, mining, or ranching industry we have a bumper or grill guard to fit your needs. We have made it our commitment to our customers to find the best quality heavy-duty replacement bumpers and grill guards at the most affordable prices in Canada.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">We have now added diesel and gas performance parts to try and help with the rising prices of diesel and gas. From intakes to exhaust and everything in between, lift kits help with your ride on and off road. We also offer levelling kits, air bags or all out lift kits to help with towing and hauling.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">With a variety of offerings to choose from, we&rsquo;re sure you&rsquo;ll be happy working with us. Look around our website and if you have any comments or questions, please feel free to contact us.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', ''),
(576, 1, 'K-Sports Marine Inc.', 'john@ksportsmarine.com', '876 River Dr., KENORA, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ksportsmarine.com ', '(807) 467-4479', '(807) 468-7310', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 13.5pt;\">We offer a complete range of Yamaha ATV\'s, Yamaha Outboards and Yamaha Snowmobiles. Couple that with a complete line of Honda ATV\'s, Honda Outboards and Honda power equipment make KSport Marine an Ideal place to do business - but there is so much more!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 7.5pt 11.25pt 0in; line-height: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">We also carry and complete Boat line up including Crestliner, Sylvan and BRP Evinrude Outboards. Need a trailer to haul your toys around? We are pleased to offer Ezloader and Roll-IN - All are unique and offer tremendous value for the consumer.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 7.5pt 11.25pt 0in; line-height: 13.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Whatever your needs may be, you will feel at home with KSport Marine and we do look forward to earning your business.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<