(590, 1, 'K.N.Crowder Mfg', 'customerservice@kncrowder.com', '1220 Burloak Dr., BURLINGTON, Ontario, Canada', 'www.kncrowder.com', '(905) 822-3472', '(905) 822-8887', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 13.5pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">From the beginning we have produced a top quality product at a fair price that has stood the test of time.</span><span style=\"line-height: 13.5pt;\"> Customer satisfaction and pride in our diverse product line are still our top priorities today. There is no question that our company wouldn\'t be where it is today if it wasn\'t for the continuing support of our customers. We try to treat every customer the way that we like to be treated. We have always been a company that looks to develop long-term relationships with our customer. We want our customers to have the proper product for the application at the best possible price. A good deal only happens when both partners are satisfied. We have recently built a new building. Shop drawings, quotes, ordering, shipping, inventory control, purchasing, researching &amp; developing, communicating&hellip; and many more are all now done on computer.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#666666\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', ''),
