(1006, 1, 'Adler Steel Limited', 'mail@adlersteel.com', '510-150 Consumers Rd Unit 503, NORTH YORK, Ontario , Canada', 'www.adlersteel.com ', '(416) 498-5559', '(416) 498-9727', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The Adler Steel group is a privately-owned global Steel trading group, having world-wide operations and dealing with the complete range of Steel products.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our focus is to cater to the Steel and related product requirements of the Off-Shore energy, Tubular, speciality Plate, and Construction industries. The ability to offer personalized, comprehensive, and knowledge-based technical and commercial services to our customers is our strength. Our world-wide team consists of Steel professionals having extensive industry experience who ensure that our customers get exactly what they want, quickly.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our forthcoming production facility for Racks and Chords used in Off-Shore drilling platforms will fulfill the large gap between demand and supply in this sector. The full range of Seamless and Welded Tubulars, including OCTG Special Quality/Dimension Heavy Plates and Flat Rolled Coated Steel, are other areas of our specialization.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1007, 1, 'Admetrics Communications Inc', 'dtaras@telus.net', '909 Monashee Pl., KELOWNA, British Columbia, Caanada', '', '(250) 980-4201', '(866) 545-9366', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Unique applications:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Admetrics Call Tracking integrates call data analytics, in house telephone systems and TelCo partnerships to provide a truly complete, end-to-end solution.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Key / Major clients: Mr Rooter, Mr Electric, Domino\'s Pizza, Pizza Hut, RE/MAX, Royal LePage, Ford Dealerships<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Success stories: RE/MAX of Canada and several franchise companies have integrated Admetrics Call Tracking in all marketing initiatives.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Testimonial: &ldquo;We initially contacted Admetrics for a solution to a telecomm problem we had. Admetrics provided a superior solution with a cost savings of about 85%. Admetrics also helped us gain valuable insight into how well our advertising was working. We found that one yellow page publication generated significantly more call volume than others in our area. I would not undertake any advertising campaign without an Admetrics Call Tracking number.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1008, 1, 'Adrenalin Marine Ltd.', 'deana.brewer@adrenalinemarine.ca', '7481 Vantage Way, DELTA, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.adrenalinmarine.ca', '(604) 940-3897', '(604) 940-1227', '', '<p>We specialize in aluminum construction utilizing modern equipment, software, training and certification.We take great pride in building durable, high quality vessels to the highest industry standards.Our team is ready to meet with you to discuss your aluminum or steel project.</p>', ''),
(1009, 1, 'Advantage Communications Inc', 'info@advantagecall.com', '265 Brackley Point Rd., CHARLOTTETOWN, Prince Edward Island, Canada', 'www.advantagecall.com', '(902) 892-1585', '(902) 894-8479', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Advantage Communications launched in 1996 in Charlottetown, Prince Edward Island. Since its inception, with the help and support of our highly experienced senior leadership team, Advantage has grown to include 5 contact centres across Eastern Canada and in Jamaica.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">With 18 years of operational experience under our belts, we pride ourselves on being customer management experts with an affinity for technical support, all while boasting some of the highest net promoter scores in the telecom industry!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">And we carry that same philosophy forward in other verticals, such as, financial services, information technology, travel and tourism and more.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1010, 1, 'Aecon Minning Construction Services', 'ccoleman@lockerbiehole.com', '451 Elgin St, BRANTFORD,, Ontario, Canada', 'www.aecon.com ', '(519) 751-8000', '(519) 751-8018', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">For more than a century, Aecon and our predecessor companies have helped to build many of Canada\'s most famous landmarks &ndash; from the CN Tower and St. Lawrence Seaway, to the Vancouver Sky Train and Halifax Shipyards. In addition to these great landmarks, we\'ve also helped to build hundreds of factories, roads, sewers, theatres, book stores, power plants, arts centres, mine sites, offices, hotels and gas distribution networks &ndash; the smaller, but no less important projects that help to make Canada a great place to live.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">A Safe Working Environment<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">At Aecon, a safe job site is a productive one. Our company is committed to providing a safe working environment for every employee and partner with whom we work. On each site we operate, this means rigorous maintenance of our equipment and zealous enforcement of stringent workplace safety standards. As a result, not only is Aecon recognized as one of the Best Employers in Canada, but we also regularly earn a safety rating of more than 99% in national audits conducted by the Infrastructure Health and Safety Association.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1011, 1, 'Aerial Industries Inc.', 'info@aerialindustries.com', '10-145 Claireport Cres, ETOBICOKE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.aerialindustries.com', '(416) 675-3509', '(416) 675-1762', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Aerial Industries has been providing quality CNC turned and milled components and parts from our Toronto CNC machine shop since 2000. A family business, Aerial is owned and operated by a 30-year veteran of the metalworking industry and the son who followed him into the trade.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Together with our staff of skilled, dedicated machinists, we are committed to providing high-quality CNC machined parts and first-rate customer service at the right price.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Contact us today to discuss your Toronto CNC Machining needs.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Aerial Industries is a Toronto CNC machining &amp; manufacturing shop. ISO 9001 international certified, we produce custom, high-quality parts in our west-Toronto precision machining facility. We specialize in fast turnaround of small to medium batch sizes of 1 - 50,000 pieces.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We are committed to growing with our customers. Adaptable and quick, we&rsquo;re always ready to accommodate design changes and go the extra mile to ensure your satisfaction. With reliable, on-time delivery and competitive prices, we are your best choice for CNC machining in Toronto.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1012, 1, 'Aero Plastics Inc.', 'info@aeroplastics.ca', '91 Citation Dr. Units 1 - 4, CONCORD, Ontario, Canada', 'www.aeroplastics.ca ', '(905) 738-9010', '(905) 738-9175', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Welcome to aero plastics Inc.. Aero Plastics Inc. is proud to be a part of today\'s generation of manufacturing. The company brings along with it a new era of delivery scheduling. When timing and delivery are critical factors, Aero Plastics will fulfill our commitment to ship what you need... when you need it.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Every effort is made to ensure that all of our products are manufactured to the highest standards and delivered to you with our guarantee of superior workmanship and materials.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Aero Plastics caliber of mouldings will add new dimensions to your products and give you the Leading Edge.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">In an on going effort to raise the quality bar, Aero Plastics is registered to ISO 9001: 2000 standard.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Aero Plastics is proud to be a part of today\'s generation of manufacturing. Aero Plastics brings along with it a new era of delivery scheduling. When timing and delivery are critical factors, Aero Plastics will fulfill our commitment to ship what you need... when you need it.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1904, 1, 'Chemie Impex Trading', 'chempex@rogers.com', '56 Gold Hill Rd, BRAMPTON, ON, , ', 'www.sanghviforge.com', '+1 (647) 436-2182', '+1 (905) 497-0450', '', '<p>We are an import &amp; export organization. At present we are  marketing following products in and out of Canada, US and India 1. SS  Flanges 2. SS forging and large dia Tube Sheets/Flanges up to 60&quot; and  Rings 3. SS ferrules and Sanitary Fittings 4. SS Bright Bars and  Rods-Round, Hex and Threaded 5. SS Wires 6.Pneumatics Valves-Manifolds,  Needle and Bleed Valves We represent SANGHVI FORGING &amp; ENGINEERING  LTD, Vadodara-India. They manufacture and supply quality SS Forging and  SS flanges since 1996. Along with flanges we can supply SS ferrules,  Sanitary Fittings and Precise CNC Machined Components   Mohamed  Mehta-President</p>', ''),
(1014, 1, 'Agat Laboratories Ltd.', 'info@agatlabs.com', '2910 12 St NE, CALGARY,, Alberta, Canada', 'www.agatlabs.com ', '(403) 735-2005', '(403) 735-2771', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">AGAT Laboratories is a highly specialized, Canadian-based company that provides laboratory services worldwide. With over 30 years of experience, coast to coast locations and over 1,200 employees Canada-wide, AGAT Laboratories is the most geographically and technically diversified laboratory in Canada. Our scientists are highly skilled and specialized in the fields of chemistry, biochemistry, microbiology, geology, engineering and specialty analysis. Committed to local communities, AGAT Laboratories aims to maintain our mission statement in delivering &quot;Service Beyond Analysis&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">AGAT Laboratories&rsquo; operations encompass 12 scientific divisions to offer full-service solutions to multiple industry types within the Environmental, Energy, Mining, Industrial, Transportation, Agri-Food and Life Sciences sectors.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">AGAT Laboratories specializes in the following scientific areas:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Environmental Chemistry<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ultra-trace and Toxicology<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Agricultural Analysis<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Food Testing<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Geology and Petrology<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Reservoir Characterization<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Air Quality Monitoring<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Petroleum Testing Services<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Oilsands Analysis<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Routine Core<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mining Geochemistry<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Lubricants Testing Services<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">AGAT Laboratories&rsquo; network of laboratory locations provides full geographic coverage for the most cost-effective and timely analysis in Canada. We are proud to set the standard for the laboratory industry, pursuing creative, accurate and defensible solutions to your complex analytical requests.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Choose AGAT Laboratories and experience &ldquo;Service Beyond Analysis&rdquo; today.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1015, 1, 'Agra West Foods', 'agrawest@agrawest.com', '30 Hope St., SOURIS, Prince Edward Island, Canada', 'www.agrawest.com ', '(902) 687-1400', '(902) 687-1401', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We devote 100% of our time and resources to making the best dehydrated potato products. Our manufacturing facilities are located in key potato areas, which ensures that all of our products are manufactured from nature\'s best potatoes<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Potatoes are our specialty...that\'s all we do, and our guarantee to customers is that they are buying, using and serving the finest potato products available. We enjoy a close working relationship with our customers, and our employees are committed to delivering quality products with professional, friendly and accurate service. No customer is too small or too large. We serve the world over with ingredients for the industrial food and baking industries, and a full line of products for the food service industry. You can count on AgraWest Foods and Idaho Pacific quality products anywhere in the world<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Try all of our potato products - We know you\'ll enjoy them.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
