(1020, 1, 'Al Jewell Perfect Signs Ltd.', 'perfectsigns@bellnet.ca', '12 Barrie Blvd, ST THOMAS, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ajperfectsigns.com ', '(519) 631-8990', '(519) 631-0323', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Welcome to the all new Al Jewell Perfect Signs website. Inside, you will find a full gallery of all the different types of work we do, as well as testimonials from past clients, our history, and our company policies.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Al Jewell Perfect Signs has been a leader in both physical and digital design and production for over 40 years.</p>', ''),
(1021, 1, 'Amity Plastics Ltd.', 'amity@mcsnet.ca', 'Range Rd 252 Hwy 2, CLYDE, Alberta, Canada', 'amity@mcsnet.ca', '(780) 348-5355', '(780) 348-5275', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Amity Welding works mainly with the farming community along with dealers in the territory of Red Deer north in Alberta.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Amity Plastics works mainly in Alberta with contractors, construction companies, school divisions, Department of Highways as well as small businesses. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Amity Ag\'s main focus is the exporting of livestock to various countries.. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We are members of the CFIB&nbsp; and are pleased to offer warranties on our products. Our years of experience and friendly, knowledgeable staff ensure that your needs are met. We believe that a top quality product should be backed by top quality service.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1022, 1, 'Analytics Marketing Inc.', 'ejackson@AnalyticsMarketing.com', '3515 Fairmont Rd, NORTH VANCOUVER, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.AnalyticsMarketing.com ', '(604) 904-6554', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Analytics Marketing Inc. delivers revenues and glowing customer testimonials from western Canada.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">We take an analytical, project approach to help growing companies from the United States and Europe achieve their territory sales targets from western Canada. Depending on the objectives of our clients, we either recruit full-time local resources or provide experienced executives on contract.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Our extensive network of enterprise decision-making contacts in western Canada makes it possible to get results quickly. Our contract executives have at least 20 years of professional sales experience in the specific territory. Many are active university professors and Board members. All offer domain expertise and extensive professional networks.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">We work with senior management to develop and implement realistic territory plans. We insure that best practices in sales are implemented and maintained. Depending on the specific needs of our client, we fill and manage the opportunity pipeline, manage people or carry a bag.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">A typical client scenario might see one of our associates act as a Territory Manager for a day a week to establish a western Canada presence. When the activity exceeds 3 days/week, we recruit a full-time replacement and mentor them as they ramp up to productivity.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">References include Momentum Technologies, Nomadic Collaboration, Ikona Gear, Infowave Software, NextPhase Strategies, Stelix Technologies, eReservation Systems, Parasun Technologies and many others. We ask for a small monthly retainer, performance-based incentives and an equity stake in the venture. We will occasionally perform fundraising and team building tasks on contingency.&nbsp;</span></p>', ''),
(1023, 1, 'Apex Internet Marketing & Web Design', 'info@apexwebmarkeing.com', '306-1280 Finch Ave W , NORTH YORK, Ontario, Canada', 'www.apexwebmarketing.com ', '(416) 721-8434', '(647) 933-2933', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Since 2003, Apex Web Marketing has invested in building the most state-of-the-art, industry-leading Internet service centre for internet marketing, including web design, web hosting and website maintenance service in Toronto. Specialists in web marketing initiatives, we\'ve managed to combine the expertise of a diverse staff to provide our customers with a unique opportunity of advertising online. Our sales representatives don\'t just try to sell &quot;the next best thing&quot;, they work with you to determine where you want to take your company online and how we can help you get there. It\'s a personal approach that we think matters most when you\'re choosing to have a presence online.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We offer you with many options for web design, web hosting and internet marketing, because we believe that no company is equal to the next, and that every industry requires a different approach to succeeding online as the internet is becoming a very competitive yet lucrative possibility. Your online business requires professional, accurate and fast support and Apex\'s fully managed support delivers so your business can operate smoothly, without interruption. Our passion is to provide superior customer service. The deployment of your website is just the beginning in our relationship together. Our team will continue to monitor your growth and provide insight that is best suited for you. We pride ourselves in understanding the scalability needs of growing businesses and are fully committed to ensuring you achieve your growth objectives.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1024, 1, 'ADGA Group', 'services@adga.ca', '105-6700 De La Cote-de-Liesse Rd, SAINT-LAURENT, Quebec, Canada', 'www.adga.ca ', '(514) 878-4388', '(514) 861-6310', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Established in 1967, ADGA Group is a leading, privately owned, professional engineering consulting firm, providing a comprehensive range of professional and engineering services to all levels of government and the private sector. We are an international leader in concurrent engineering design in the defence and space industries.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The ADGA Group of Companies is headquartered in Ottawa, with offices in Calgary, Toronto, Montr&eacute;al, Halifax, Wavre (Belgium), London (United Kingdom), Leiden (The Netherlands), Darmstadt (Germany) and Frascatti (Italy).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our Group of Companies boasts industry-leading proficiencies in the areas of: engineering (systems, software, communications, aerospace, civil aviation and space systems); project management; management consulting; IT and software development and technical support; and is backed by a network of over 750 engineers, scientists, technologists and experienced professionals, who leverage their knowledge and expertise in order to deliver innovative solutions to our clients.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">ADGA&rsquo;s reputation is built on the breadth and depth of our domain knowledge, corporate experience, highly skilled employees and our commitment to excellence.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1025, 1, 'Aqua Bag', 'zen.canglobaltrade@gmail.com', '288D Marion St, WINNIPEG,, Manitoba, Canada', '', '(204) 771-6170', '(204) 231-9445', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Manufacturer of drinking water in Bio-Degradable, compostible 2 &amp; 3 gallon bags for First Nation Communities.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Manufacturer of 1 Litre Water Bags for Retail &amp; Food Service Industry. Private Label available. Spring Water &amp; RO Water Options.Supplier of Spring Water &amp; Flavoured Water in most sizes in either Branded or Private Label for North America and Asia. Can Supply Canada Wide as well as Internationally.&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
