(1061, 1, 'Behl Chemicals Inc.', 'behlchem@yahoo.ca', '52 Steeles Ave, MILTON, Ontario, Canada ', '', '(905) 878-1783', '(905) 878-1767', '', '<p>BCI is a full service provider of 800 different paints, coatings and cleaning products to residential, commercial and industrial users. BCI prides itself on its ability to service customers by efficiently matching specific color and product requirements at considerable savings. &nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1062, 1, 'Belgo Media Inc.', 'info@belgomedia.com', 'C.P. 524 Succ. St-Jacques , MONTREAL, Quebec, Canada', 'www.belgomedia.com ', '(514) 502-2580', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">If you are reading this, you probably have a Web goal, an idea, a vision, of how to improve your business using the Internet.&nbsp; Perhaps you have a Web site in dire need of redesign to incorporate additional function.&nbsp; Possibly, you are not sure what you need - you just know the Internet can benefit you in some way.&nbsp; We will make your Web goal a reality, even if you don&rsquo;t know what it is.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">That&rsquo;s what we do.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Just about anyone can create a Web site today, buy what we bring you is a professional marketing expertise, user-oriented original design - no templates - clear content experience and good programming practices.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Belgo Media Inc., is a turn-key one-stop shop for all your Internet needs.&nbsp; We provide professional consultation regarding your Web goals, and we have in-house resources and partners to help build your site from concept to final product.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Here\'s 30 reasons for having a Web site (pop-up window).<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1063, 1, 'BF SIMULATION', 'info@bfsimulation.com', '128 Des Fauvettes St, SAINT-COLOMBAN, Quebec, Canada', 'www.bfsimulation.com ', '(450) 592-6392', '(450) 592-6392', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our lines of business: BF Simulation is an engineering consulting and software development firm. We supply solutions to the metals and minerals, cement and composite materials industries. We design our products and solutions with you in mind. By understanding the aluminum and cement industries through over 30 years of experience, we can focus on the areas of concern in your business and quickly locate and optimize the elements that hinder your productivity. Our methodology, analytical depth, experience and client centered approach make us who we are. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">A Growing Company: We have expanded the scope of our business by moving this year into composite materials. Our expertise lies in the fields of 1) process control and optimization 2) composite structure designs and&nbsp;&nbsp; 3) materials characterization. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our Software: Our specialized yet simple to use software is designed for automatic quantitative mineralogical analysis of materials such as bauxite and cement. By providing a unique set of benefits that truly address the industry needs, our products are in an unrivaled market position. Explore the benefits of BauxQ and CemQuant - see for yourself why BF Simulation is emerging as a leader in computational phase analysis.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Engineering Tailored Solutions: Our tailor-made solutions make mineralogical analysis more simple and more accessible. We even help you get started, so that you can quickly make use of your investment. Through computation methods, you can take your process control to the next level. As a leader and visionary in computational quantitative mineralogical analysis, we have the technology to help you quantify what the competition can not. We understand that your raw materials vary in composition and morphology. That why both BauxQ and CemQuant share a flexible platform that lets us adapt the software to your specific needs. Accurate results, quickly, all the time. At home in R&amp;D, and unique for an industrial environment. Through constant innovation and leveraging unique technology, we have the capacity and knowledge to tailor make a solution that meets your specific needs. Explore the advantage of BF Simulation.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1064, 1, 'BGA Tax Specialists', 'bryan@taxspecialists.ca', '157 Meadowbrook Dr., ANCASTER, Ontario , Canada ', 'www.taxspecialists.ca ', '(905) 304-9014', '(905) 304-0762', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">BGA TAX SPECIALISTS provides value added tax advice to corporations, professionals and entrepreneurs in areas such as corporate tax compliance and planning, purchase and sale of businesses, succession, retirement and estate planning alternatives with an eye to tax minimization and wealth preservation.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our Principal, Bryan Allendorf CA, CBV, MBA, CFP, TEP, practices exclusively in the areas of TAXATION, FAMILY WEALTH PRESERVATION and BUSINESS VALUATION. Bryan is a recognized tax specialist with over 25 years of senior level tax experience including 21 years as a Tax Partner or Senior Tax Specialist with several Big Five firms serving national and international clients.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1065, 1, 'Bfofo Designs Inc.', 'service@bfofo.com', '31022 - 6389 - 120th St, DELTA, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.bfofo.com ', '(888) 920-0574', '(800) 589-2364', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We manufacture and wholesale imprinted clothing with quality dyes and foils. Each item bears a hang tag explaining the modern petroglyph or native artwork. We also produce pewter jewellery with similar designs, boxed with descriptive card.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1066, 1, 'BIAC BROADBAND', 'info@biacbroadband.com', '51 Main St N, MARKHAM,, Ontario, Canada', 'www.biacbroadband.com ', '(905) 887-7540', '(647) 722-3901', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">BIAC Broadband Internet Alliance Corporation is a federal company which was incorporated in 1999.&nbsp; It is employee owned and operated, led by 30+ year veterans of CATV, WAN and Data Center end to end engineering and operation.&nbsp; Through the years our team have innovated; creating hardware and software solutions for our clients.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Most notably is our invention of the RackLift &trade; which is now produced for other data center professionals.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Best-in-class network solutions and project management team Total end to end: hybrid fiber design, build, management<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Focused expertise: broadband industry and B2B marketplace<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Poised for growth: managerial and technical bench strength Reputation for quality: &ldquo;Engineered right on time the first time&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Insured, bondable, hands on talent you can depend on.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1067, 1, 'Big Chief Meat Snacks Inc', 'snacks@bigchiefmeatsnacks.com', '3900 52 Ave NE, CALGARY, Alberta, Canada', 'www.bigchiefmeatsnacks.com ', '(403) 264-2641', '(403) 262-9053', '', '<p>At Big Chief Meat Snacks Inc. our vision is to become the number one brand of convenient, ready-to-eat meat snacks in Canada. We will achieve our vision by providing consumers with high quality, nutritional meat snacks and promoting the importance of a protein balanced diet. We are committed to adhering to the highest quality standards in all of our manufacturing and quality assurance practices, as well as providing a safe and healthy work environment for our employees. We are dedicated to complete customer satisfaction by providing our quality meat snacks in various convenient locations and in a variety of popular flavors. In addition, we place a high value on corporate social responsibility, actively participating in the community, supporting local organizations and charities. &nbsp;We are a family owned and operated business in Calgary, Alberta that is very proud to be Canadian and support our fellow Canadians through employment, sponsorship, and businesses relationships. We also understand the importance of being environmentally conscious and have adopted sustainable practices wherever we are able. Through our devotion to quality, safety, variety, convenience, community, and environment, Big Chief Meat Snacks Inc. will continue to grow and be a positively recognized brand throughout Canada.</p>', ''),
(1068, 1, 'Big Foot Manufacturing Inc.', 'wayne@bigfoot-mfg.com', '3380 Ford Rd, TAPPEN, British Columbia, Canada ', 'www.bigfootloghomes.com ', '(250) 835-8885', '(250) 835-4732', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">For more than 20 years now Big Foot Log and Timber Homes has machined and handcrafted our homes in our 60,000 sq/ft plant in Salmon Arm, British Columbia, Canada. We have shipped more than 4000 homes to local and international markets in the United States, Canada, Europe and Asia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our high standards for quality and service have been well received in the market place. Big Foot Log and Timber Homes recently expanded our production to produce more than 500 homes per year.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Big Foot Log and Timber Homes can provide several standard plans for both our handcrafted and machined log homes as well as the capability to build fully customized homes to your plans.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Big Foot Log and Timber Homes is a member of the National Association of Home Builders, the International Log Builders\' Association and the British Columbia Log &amp; Timber Building Industry Association. Please contact us for more information about becoming a dealer for Big Foot Log and Timber Homes Inc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We invite potential dealers and homeowners to come and visit our facility in Salmon Arm, British Columbia, Canada. Or watch the video below to see our employees in action.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1069, 1, 'Bioriginal Food & Science Corp.', 'business@bioriginal.com', '102 Melville St, SASKATOON, Saskatchewan, Canada', 'www.bioriginal.com ', '(306) 975-1166', '(306) 242-3829', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Bioriginal is a global leader in delivering complete omega solutions to the Food and Nutraceutical industries. With over 20 years of global expertise in both plant and marine-based omegas, Bioriginal has carved out a niche by scientifically combining ingredients from all over the world, directly from the source, to create unique and efficacious solutions. Bioriginal is passionate about omegas and the health benefits they provide, discovering, anticipating trends and pioneering within the omega space since 1993. Bioriginal has developed proprietary methods and systems to provide customized turnkey solutions for its customers that help them compete in a highly competitive space. Bioriginal&rsquo;s headquarter is located in Saskatoon, Canada. Bioriginal Europe/Asia is located in Den Bommel, the Netherlands.</p>', ''),
(1070, 1, 'Bison Fire Protection Inc.', 'info@bisonfire.com', '35 Boys Rd - Grp. 582 - R.R.5, SPRINGFIELD, Manitoba, Canada', 'www.bisonfire.com ', '(204) 237-3473', '(204) 237-4744', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Bison Fire Protection has built a solid reputation on our commitment to superior products and services. We believe in providing education and training, as well as professional service, to ensure our customers are served as well as possible by the fire protection solutions we provide.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Established in 2001, Bison Fire Protection Inc. began as a fire extinguisher, and automatic suppression provider to grow into a full service company including fire alarm, and automatic sprinklers. In 2006 we added Thompson Extinguisher Service to our family, combining their more than 20 years of experience, with our entire catalogue of products and services. In 2010 we expanded to Regina Saskatchewan offering the same high quality products, and services our customers have come to expect. 2011 saw the acquisition of Protec Sprinklers, this addition has allowed us to move into automatic sprinkler design, contracting, and installation.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Most recently, we\'ve expanded our service region and entered northwest Ontario with our newest location in Kenora, open as of 2015. Visit our Location Page to see all of our locations, in each of th 4 cities.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">All Bison Fire Protection staff are factory trained and certified by each of our suppliers, as required by the fire code.&nbsp; Our Automatic Sprinkler Division provides Red Seal inspections, testing, and renovations to all types of sprinkler systems.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Bison Fire Protection Inc. is quickly becoming the recognized leader in fire alarm and emergency light products. Offering authorized Siemens Fire Alarm sales, service, inspections, verifications and product warranty. No matter the size of your project we can service your fire alarm needs.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our full service shops, in Winnipeg, Thompson, Regina as well as our newest addition in Kenora, are inspected by Transport Canada, and are certified by Warnock Hersey to service all manufacturers and types of extinguishers as well as both pre-engineered and engineered suppression systems.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1071, 1, 'BKD Aerospace Industries Inc.', 'info@bkdaerospace.com', '7-11771 Horseshoe Way, RICHMOND, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.bkdaerospace.com ', '(604) 247-2128', '(604) 214-9825', '', '<p>&nbsp;BKD\'s mission is to provide mobility products for any and every situation that requires assistance involving stairs, steep ramps, and vehicular transport: for travel (including airports, aircraft, and marine vessels), at home, in health-care facilities, and for ambulance and evacuation &mdash; in short, for any venue or situation where persons with reduced mobility need assistance climbing up and down stairs, or transferring to different levels or different modes of transportation.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Whether transporting persons up and down stairs and into and out of vehicles or aircraft, or transporting cargo, BKD\'s products are unique. BKD\'s staircliming devices do the lifting for you. All you have to do is guide the mechanism and use the controls on the device\'s handle &mdash; the stairclimber does the rest. As well, BKD\'s products afford mobility on flat surfaces, alleviating the need for transferring persons from wheelchairs to other rail-type stairclimbing systems.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Another advantage of BKD\'s product line is that, by safely and comfortably transporting persons up and down stairs using BKD\'s mobility devices, persons who would otherwise be involved in lifting are able to avoid musculoskeletal injuries. BKD\'s self-propelled devices do the lifting for you.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Based in Richmond, British Columbia, Canada, BKD can deliver stairclimber units worldwide, and can provide in-person training to purchasers of units internationally. In-person demonstrations of BKD\'s products can also be arranged.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>In addition, BKD Aerospace International provides a diverse range of products for the aerospace industry. As an agent for NAASCO, BKD supplies aircraft parts, and in association with JetBed, is a supplier of sofa beds for executive aircraft.</div>', ''),
(1072, 1, 'BL Plastics Inc.', 'sales@blplastics.com', '3-1136 Centre St Suite 92, THORNHILL, Ontario, Canada', 'www.blplastics.com ', '(416) 984-7131', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">BL Plastics is a distributor of plastic rods, tubes and pipes. We stock thousands of different materials and sizes to suit your individual needs.&nbsp; BL Plastics only carries the highest quality products at competitive prices.&nbsp; It is our mandate to provide exceptional service to our customers in order to help them achieve their goals. Whether for construction, maintenance, design, electrical, food processing, manufacturing or machining, BL Plastics will have you covered. A BL Plastics sales representative is ready for any quotes, stock checks or any plastics related questions you may have.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">BL Plastics facilities are equipped with FedEx Freight, FedEx Ground and UPS integrated software which enables us to ship your order out the same day. We have great discounts with these carriers that can benefit you through PPD shipping. We will handle all customs &amp; duties for cross border shipping, so you it feels like you ordered locally.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">BL Plastics understands how frustrating it can be to be told there&rsquo;s no stock available after getting a quote or placing an order.&nbsp; To avoid this, we use an online real-time inventory system that monitors our stock levels 24 hours a day 7 days a week. All products are electronically scanned, physically checked, and placed in their proper storing locations within our warehouse. This gives us the ability to provide our customers with real-time, accurate stock counts right away.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">BL Plastics has the ability to either send quotes through email or by telephone call back. However, we do prefer email quotes as we understand how busy your schedule is and how frustrating telephone calls can be. We send quotes to you so you can review them at your own time, and when you make the decision to purchase from us, just send us an email back with a purchase order and we&rsquo;ll handle the rest. Ordering has never been so easy.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1073, 1, 'Blue Streak Electronics Inc.', 'info@bsecorp.com', '30 Moyal Crt, CONCORD, Ontario , Canada ', 'www.bsecorp.com ', '(905) 669-4812', '(905) 669-5179', '', '<p>&nbsp;Blue Streak Electronics specializes in remanufactured automotive electronics. This is our focus and the foundation by which we are able to provide quality products and innovative solutions to an ever evolving and complex service industry.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1074, 1, 'BMR Express International', 'info@bmrexpress.com', '25 Sunforest Dr., BRAMPTON, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.bmrexpress.com ', '(905) 840-0500', '(905) 840-0540', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Created in 1996, BMR Express International is a Canadian-based air transportation logistics provider specializing in both time-definite and cost effective air cargo and charter services.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">With over 25 years of management experience in the air transportation industry, BMR Express has provided an efficient and personalized service to all of the world&rsquo;s major economically developed areas in North and South America, Europe, Asia, Africa, the Middle East and Oceania.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Through our network of international agents and carriers BMR Express provides a seamless, one call service tailored to each customer&rsquo;s needs. With highly trained cargo professionals in our international network, each one knows the culture, provides fluency in their language and is thoroughly familiar with local regulations concerning the importation and exportation of products and goods.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">For information on our rates and services please contact BMR Express at, +1 905 840 0500 or through our contact page<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1075, 1, 'BNG Global Foods', 'pablo.golan@bng-globalfoods.com', '645 du Vieux Moulin St, CARAQUET, New Brunswick, Canada', '', '(514) 502-5404', '(305) 647-2419', '', '<p>&nbsp;BNG GLOBAL FOODS is a Canadian company located on the Acadian shores of New Brunswick, specialized in exporting the following foods: 1) seafood -such us lobsters, snow-crabs, shrimps, scallops, salmon and herrings-, 2) berries -such as blueberries and cranberries-, 3) peat moss, and 4) maple-syrup, among others. &nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1076, 1, 'BoardSuite', 'info@boardsuitecorp.com', '330 Bay St, TORONTO, Ontario, Canada', 'www.boardsuitecorp.com ', '(647) 258-1670', '(866) 453-6939', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">All stakeholders (board of directors, officers, lawyers, accountants, shareholders) on boards have significant risks and responsibilities. BoardSuite was created to mitigate risk by providing directors and officers a simple yet powerful solution to address their responsibilities surrounding good governance and compliance.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Provided as a FREE SaaS-based service, BoardSuite enables executive leadership teams to securely and effectively manage their governance and compliance requirements, thus allowing them to devote more time towards helping their organizations improve overall business performance.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Award Winning Company:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">BoardSuite has received notable recognition within the online industry for its achievements. In March 2011, BoardSuite was selected as one of the Top 15 Companies to watch by AlwaysOn OnDemand. In July 2009, BoardSuite was chosen as one of Canada\'s leading Web 2.0 pioneers at the PICK20 Awards (the only national listing of Canada\'s up and coming Web 2.0 pioneers). In August 2009, BoardSuite was named by IDC (International Data Corporation) as one of Canada\'s Top Cloud Computing Solutions to Watch, calling it a &quot;disruptive innovation&quot; in the board portal industry.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1077, 1, 'Boitier Custom Metal', 'info@powersurvey.com', '7880 Rte Transcanadienne, SAINT-LAURENT, Quebec, Canada', 'www.custom-metalinc.com ', '(514) 333-8392', '(514) 333-8395', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">In today\'s market, versatility is important in order to respond to client demands.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">At Custom Metal housings, we are dedicated to responding to all your demands.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Custom Metal specializes in the fabrication of made-to-measure cabinets and housings; all to YOUR specifications.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We fabricate metal housings of all kinds and according to customer requirements; in steel, galvanized steel, aluminum or stainless steel.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
