(1205, 1, 'DCI Technologies Inc.', 'ted.skinner@dcitech.com', '31-4948 126 Ave SE, CALGARY, Alberta, Canada ', 'www.dcitech.com ', '(403) 720-4885', '(403) 720-3905', '', '<p>&nbsp;DCI Distributes and Manufactures industrial remote control products. DCI is Your preferred wholesale source for Wireless Telemetry Products and Custom Integration Services.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>DCI Technologies is a privately held Canadian Company dedicated to providing value added expertise in gathering, controlling, moving and analyzing data. &nbsp;The company has a well balanced technical and management background spanning electronics, industrial instrumentation, telecommunications, analog, and digital radio, as well as software and micro-controller development.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>DCI Technologies provides products and services that fit into three inter-related categories that revolve around moving and analyzing data. &nbsp;More specifically, Wide Area Networks are our forte, with a specialty in providing integration services to System Integrators, OEM\'s and industry service providers.</div>', ''),
(1206, 1, 'DDA Sports Marketing', 'info@ddasportsmarketing.com', '320, rue Pie-IX, TERREBONNE, Quebec, Canada ', 'www.ddasportsmarketing.com', '(514) 660-1727', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;DDA Sports Marketing is a company specializing in the design and sale of articles recognitions (trophies, cups, medals, plaques, corporate gifts), team uniforms, and custom corporate apparel and promotional items. Founded in 2011 DDA Sports Marketing has quickly become an important pillar in the field. DDA Sports Marketing offers the opportunity to make purchases online, by phone or at his studio located in Terrebonne. MISSION: DDA Sports Marketing is committed to providing high quality products that meet the highest requirements. We share the same passion. So it\'s a real pleasure to meet your desires to reward deserving people. We value the physical, artistic and social activities for young people. We are involved in several institutions and sports teams. In order to help us improve our services, do not hesitate to send us your comments. TESTIMONY At DDA SPORTS MARKETING , you are at the right place.&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1207, 1, 'Dearden Marine', 'deardenmarine@gmail.com', '1011 Venture Way, GIBSONS, British Columbia, Canada ', 'www.deardenmarine.com ', '(604) 886-8052', '(604) 210-9236', '', '<p>&nbsp;Dearden Marine has been creating custom aluminum boats, both power boats and sailboats since 1990 on British Columbia\'s beautiful Sunshine Coast on the west coast of Canada. Whether you are searching for a luxurious coastal yacht, a rugged offshore aluminum sailboat or even a tough little minitug, we can meet your needs, Full custom fabricating aluminum power boats and aluminum sailboats is our speciality.&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1208, 1, 'DF Barnes Fabrication', 'info@dfbarnes.com', '45 Pepperrell Rd, ST. JOHN\'S, Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada', 'www.dfgroup.ca ', '(709) 726-6820', '(709) 579-5055', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">To provide a wide range of personal and corporate services with a team of complimentary specialists, who through broad-based licensing, professional qualifications and technical expertise directly assist clients to achieve family and business goals.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We commit to ongoing &quot;face-to-face&quot; financial planning reviews to produce optimum results.&nbsp; We work with you to learn more about your personal and business goals in order to provide tailored and effective solutions.&nbsp; Our associates have access to diversified services, both locally and nationally.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1209, 1, 'DGM Inc.', 'ventes@dgm-seals.com', '751, rue Marion, JOLIETTE, Quebec, Canada', 'www.dgm-seals.com ', '(450) 752-1152', '(450) 752-1162', '', '<p>&nbsp;For nearly 25 years, companies Lapping DGM working closely with several North American businesses by providing mechanical seals adapted to their types of operations.&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1210, 1, 'DH Water Management', 'lorne@dhwatermgmt.com', '75 Lord Seaton Rd, NORTH YORK, Ontario, Canada', 'www.dhwatermgmt.com ', '(416) 616-0403', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">DH Water Management is the global leader in smart irrigation, drip irrigation, weather controlled ET and moisture sensing solutions for a sustainable future. Since 1991 we have led the way by developing solutions that help our customers optimize results.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sustainable productivity benefits not only business, but also the environment. By empowering our customers to use land, water and energy in more efficient and responsible ways, we help protect the world&rsquo;s natural resources.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Dedicated to implementing and supporting targeted solutions for our global customer base, DH Water Mgmt focuses on the following business lines.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1211, 1, 'Di-Corp', 'briancoston@di-corp.com', '360 - 800 - 6th Ave SW, Calgary, Alberta, Canada', 'www.di-corp.com ', '(403) 265-4401', '(403) 269-5540', '', '<p>&nbsp;Down to Earth Business</p>\r\n<div>At Di-Corp, we have proudly developed a reputation for meeting and exceeding the expectations of our customers since 1960. &nbsp;We build relationships that focus not only on down to earth customer service, but the capabilities and expertise of our staff as well.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Di-Corp is a leading distributor of specialty chemicals, parts and accessories serving the energy, mining, and drilling industries. Our marketing divisions focus on all aspects of your industrial project; Mineral Exploration, Drilling Fluid Supply, Cementing &amp; Stimulation, Mining, Research &amp; Development, Testing Equipment, and all Small Bore Drilling disciplines. &nbsp; Our geographic footprint, stretching coast-to-coast in Canada, the United States and around the world drives value for our customers and makes us your preferred supplier.</div>', ''),
(1212, 1, 'DJ\'s Lures', 'djevans@cablerocket.com', '4095 Byng Rd, PORT HARDY, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.djslures.com ', '(250) 949-9853', '(250) 949-9813', '', '<p>&nbsp;Our firm was established to develop lures to target sockeye and chum, the two species of salmon sportsman have trouble with. &nbsp;Along the way we designed some killer chinook and coho lures to round out our product line. &nbsp;Some of our Googly Eyes also work in the larger lakes in northern Canada. &nbsp;Anywhere you troll you can use our lures. &nbsp;We are in the process of providing flashers in various sizes and colour patterns to use with our products. &nbsp;We hope to provide one stop package deals for different salmon (or trout).&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1213, 1, 'DK-SPEC Inc.', 'info@dkspec.com', '1060, ch. Olivier, SAINT-NICOLAS, Quebec, Canada ', 'www.dkspec.com ', '(418) 831-3433', '(418) 831-0201', '', '<div>DK-SPEC has been a part of the forestry industry for many years. Through our vast experience we have come to recognize that, to reach success, we have to increase the durability, endurance and performance of all our tools and equipment.</div>\r\n<div>Thanks to our innovative research and development program, we are now able to achieve impressive results! We have learned how to combine innovative technologies with that of new generation materials, in order to offer what&rsquo;s best on the market: top performance.</div>\r\n<div>Our customer service is also a priority, thereby allowing us to build a reputation of excellence and enabling us to provide you with the professional services of our team of experts as well as state-of-the-art equipment.</div>\r\n<div>Contact us today. We will be pleased to provide you with any assistance you may require.</div>', ''),
(1214, 1, 'DLC Majorem inc.', 'dlalonde.dlc@gmail.com', '539 Le Moyne St, MONT-SAINT-HILAIRE, Quebec, Canada', '', '(450) 813-7274', '', '', '<p>Air Emissions Expert. Strategic planning for Emissions testing, regulatory negotiations.&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1215, 1, 'DM GLOBAL MARKETING', 'daniela@dmglobalmarketing.ca', '155 Darlington Terr., SHERWOOD PARK, Alberta, Canada ', 'www.dmglobalmarketing.ca ', '(780) 467-0101', '(780) 410-9669', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">DM Global Marketing started as an independent brokerage company after being in the agribusiness market since 2002, with the main goal to help our valuable customers finding the right product, and to our reliable suppliers to market their products in certain markets.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our Services:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Wide range of products of different origins.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Market reports<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Updated prices and competitive offers.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Logistic support.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Verification and support in fulfilment of contract terms.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1216, 1, 'DNI Web Design', 'dniwebdesign@sasktel.net', 'P.O. Box 895, CARROT RIVER, Saskatchewan, Canada', 'www.dniwebdesign.com ', '(306) 768-3020', '(306) 768-3027', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">DNI Web Design in the early years was founded DI Homepages Ltd. by Dawson Irvine; however we were just starting out and we needed a foot hold in the industry. In late 1999 DI Homepages Ltd. became known as INGEN Web Design and in May of 2000 we signed up our first client Prall Trucking Ltd. We developed a website that satisfied his needs and they were pleased with our work. Still needing a bigger foothold, in December 2000, with the help of a great aunt, the name of DNI Web Design came to light when she gave the CEO a sweater with a logo on it (as she worked at an advertising company), and the name and logo stuck. In 2004, the trademark of DNI Web Design took on the 3D look it has today.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">In the fall of 2001, we got one of the biggest clients we currently have, the Tri-Town Thunder from Carrot River. Still in school Dawson was approached by team executive (who happened to be his english teacher and his principle at the time) to create a website for the team. This project lead to two later clients, the North Saskatchewan Junior Hockey League (2002) and the Big River Timberkings (2005).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">In February of 2004, Dawson meet Jay Semko of the Northern Pikes at the Artful Dodger, where he went to see them play. Being a devoted fan who created a website about the Northern Pikes this help us get Jay Semko to allow us to help maintain his site, with a possible re-design of the site in the future. In April 2004 we got one of our largest clients to date, the Nipawin/Diamond North Credit Union. We sent in a proposal when we learned the current staff and executive were unpleased with their current web site and designer. We then meet with some of the personnel in charge of the website and it\'s content and created a design to meet their needs. We used the colours they wanted and did exactly what they want and so they were very pleased with our work.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1217, 1, 'Dockside Motel Inc.', 'docksidemotel@hotmail.com', '1 main street , BLACK DUCK COVE, Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada ', 'www.docksidemotel.nf.ca ', '(709) 877-2444', '(709) 877-9459', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Dockside Motel Inc. provides accomodations, food services and conference services to the general public. It is located near the Ferry Terminal connecting the Island of Newfoundland to Quebec and Southern Labrador. During the summer months it is frequented by tourists and other travellers. It is a popular stop on the way to the Quebec/Labrador mainland. We are involved with marketing the Viking Trail and the Quebec/Southern Labrador region.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1218, 1, 'DPC DP Consultants Inc.', 'tonyv@valcomp.com', '4-40 Winges Rd, WOODBRIDGE, Ontario, Cana', 'www.dpconsultants.ca ', '(905) 850-8949', '(905) 850-9115', '', '<p>&nbsp;We hope that you will enjoy your visit. As a value-added distributor, Valcomp prides itself on the quality of support we offer to you, our customers.</p>', ''),
(1219, 1, 'DRA Pharmedev Canada Inc', 'dra@pharmedev.com', '4815 Saint-Martin Blvd W, LAVAL, Quebec, Canada ', '', '(450) 687-6300', '(450) 687-6229', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Since 1974, we have provided consultation services to Canadian and foreign companies in Regulatory Affairs, Quality Control/Assurance, Research &amp; Development, Technology Transfer, Product Licencing to the Pharmaceutical, Medical Device and Cosmetic industries.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">International experience in North and South America, Europe, Middle East, India.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Expertise in OTC, Rx, solid and sterile dosage forms, Veterinary Drugs, Implant Devices. Principal activities include drug registration in Canada (new and generic), and devices, QC/QA for Canadian companies. Preparation of foreign companies for GMP audit (special experience in India). Membership in regulatory and scientific associations. Clientele 70% foreign.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1220, 1, 'DS Communications Group Ltd.', 'office@dscomgroup.ca', '720-999 Broadway W, VANCOUVER, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.dscomgroup.ca ', '(604) 734-5607', '(604) 730-0970', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">A boutique-style multilingual services provider specializing in major Asian languages to cater to translation, interpretation and multilingual communication needs.&nbsp;</span></p>', ''),
(1221, 1, 'Dubois Agrinovation Inc.', 'info@duboisag.com', '478, Notre-Dame, SAINT-REMI, Quebec, Canada', 'www.duboisag.com ', '(450) 454-3961', '(450) 454-6638', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Dubois Agrinovation&rsquo;s mission is to be the leader in advice and solutions for irrigation, plastic mulch film, floating row covers, greenhouse &amp; nursery equipement, vineyard &amp; orchard equipement and the effective use of plastic picking basket, harvest containers, and harvest bins.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">To find a solution adapted to your situation, listening to your needs is our fundamental approach. The advice, the expertise, and the quality of our service team bring an added value to the products offered.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We are always developing and searching for new technologies to improve the quality of your work and your profitability.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1222, 1, 'DV Hardwoods Inc.', 'viateur.girard@boisdv.ca', '131 Principale St, FASSETT, Quebec, Canada ', 'viateur.girard@boisdv.ca', '(819) 423-2338', '(819) 423-5102', '', '<p>&nbsp;ounded in 1992 thanks to the determination of its president and the support of two employees, DV Hardwoods has experienced continual growth and currently employs professionals from all aspects of the forestry and product transformation chain - &nbsp;sourcing, yard management, sawmill operations, kiln operations, grading and inventory management. &nbsp;This dynamic team is equally supported by a formidable administrative staff, human resource team and a diverse and knowledgeable marketing and sales team. &nbsp;DV\'s success can further be attributed to the partnership of two entrepreneurs with extensive experience in the forestry sector and an undeniable commitment to their team and their customers.</p>', ''),
(1223, 1, 'DW Environmental', 'dewalz@telusplanet.net', '116 Winchester Cres. SW, CALGARY, Alberta, Canada', '', '(403) 246-8025', '', '', '<p>DW Environmental specializes in assisting companies in developing environmental management programs and low carbon futures strategies while integrating these with the principles of sustainable development or the triple bottom line. DW Environmental services include environmental auditing, regulatory reviews, assessment of environmental responsibilities and assessing initiatives to reduce your carbon footprint.&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1224, 1, 'DXStorm.com Inc.', 'info@dxstorm.com', '824 Winston Churchill Blvd, OAKVILLE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.dxstorm.com ', '(905) 842-8262', '(905) 842-3255', '', '<p>&nbsp;DXStorm is a profitable E-Business engineer and service provider consolidating and leveraging the assets,<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">intellectual properties, and capabilities of the original DXStorm and an expanding number of acquired&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">and developing business units.</span></p>', ''),
(1225, 1, 'Dyad Infosys Limited', 'dave@dyad.ca', '110-5803 Yonge St, NORTH YORK, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.dyad.ca ', '(416) 512-7000', '(416) 512-7766', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">For over 35 years, DYAD has delivered professional software services to private and public sector clients in Canada and The United States. Our business is based on getting and maintaining long-term client relationships and on a sustained effort to keep current with the best and most productive software development tools in the industry.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">DYAD provides businesses with a partnership approach to systems developments. Your requirements and our approach to them ensure every opportunity to assess, re-assess and confirm the effectiveness of our software solutions.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">There are only two things you need to know about us. We always stand behind our product development and when you call us you are guaranteed that we will respond. When you call us, you do not have to go through an army of people to reach the person who can help you best. You get to the right person right away and never have to deal with anyone who is out of touch with your business needs. We pride ourselves on having maintained many of our clients for over a quarter of a century. This is unusual in such a dynamic industry but it is a measure of our commitment to service and our client loyalty.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1226, 1, 'DZD HARDWOOD INC', 'sdollinger@dzdhardwood.com', '450 Roland-Godard Blvd, SAINT-JÉRÔME, Quebec, Canada', 'www.dzdhardwood.com ', '(450) 431-1643', '(450) 431-3941', '', '<p>&nbsp;DZD hardwood is a family business, specializing in hardwood lumber handling drying and remanufacturing since 1983.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>DZD offers hardwood lumber in a variety of species, such as White Oak, Red Oak, Cherry, Soft Maple, Hard Maple, White Ash, Walnut, Beech, Basswood, Poplar and most other species native to North America.We have over 10 kilns and a drying capacity of over 520,000bft.</div>\r\n<div>DZD also has over 2,000,000bft of storage facility for kiln dried hardwood lumber.The container loading facility, with 4 container doors and sufficient space for loading and unloading trucks, is located under the same roof as the storage and grading facilities.</div>', ''),
(1227, 1, 'E-axis Inc.', 'info@e-axis.com', '254-30 Via Renzo Dr., RICHMOND HILL, Ontario, ', 'www.e-axis.com ', '(905) 513-1092', '(905) 513-1814', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">After more than 14 years of continuous evolution, keeping pace with technology, we&rsquo;ve developed a thorough, profound understanding for everything online, social and mobile. Every solution we deliver is focused on returning maximum value for client&rsquo;s investment.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our clients represent top Canadian and International companies where quality and innovation are paramount. Through various projects that include custom business applications, comprehensive web sites, micro-sites, mobile apps and games, augmented reality installations, and the next big thing, we&rsquo;ve delivered solid solutions that achieve measurable results.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We employ top level, experienced marketing and technology experts.&nbsp; From Mobile to Social, CMS systems to E-commerce we specialize in knowing precisely what technology will meet your needs, and then we implement that solution in an efficient manner to achieve your goals.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We find best channels to reach and engage your audience in the most effective way. Our strategies include helping you maximize Facebook, Twitter, Google+ and other tools for social engagement to help you build traffic and a loyal following.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1228, 1, 'E-CARGO INC', 'cargo@cargo-excess.com', '121-3700 Griffith St, SAINT-LAURENT, Quebec, Canada', 'www.cargo-excess.com ', '(514) 907-4766', '(514) 227-5131', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nous transportons les effets personnels et le cargo g&eacute;n&eacute;ral du Canada vers n\'importe quelle destination dans le monde. Exp&eacute;dier vos malles, bagages, colis sur Paris,Marseille, Nice, Londres, Sydney,Rennes, Nantes, Montpellier.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Transporter vos malles, exc&eacute;dent de bagages, de Montr&eacute;al, Toronto, Calgary, Vancouver vers, Rome,Perth, Bruxelles, Oslo, Geneve, Zurich. Transport de voiture de Montr&eacute;al, Toronto, Calgary. Transport de machines lourdes, d\'autobus, de petite voiture au Canada ou ailleurs dans le monde. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Exp&eacute;dier vos colis Montr&eacute;al- Nantes, Transport de bagages Toronto- Marseille-Transport d\'exc&eacute;dent bagage Canada France.Transport bagage petit prix pour la France, exp&eacute;dier moins cher par bateau ou avion.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Envoi moins chers &agrave; Montr&eacute;al, courrier International Canada, Transport Palette Montr&eacute;al, Toronto, Calgary, Edmonton, Courrier local, Service de livraison local, Transport de bagage moins cher Montr&eacute;al, Transport de colis, bagages &agrave; Toronto. Service rapide de transport de&nbsp; Bagages&nbsp; France-Qu&eacute;bec, Service express d\'exp&eacute;dition de colis, meuble, d&eacute;m&eacute;nagement international Montr&eacute;al. D&eacute;m&eacute;nagement international partielle, ou complete, demi-conteneur. Transport efffets personnels&nbsp; France-Qu&eacute;bec, Exp&eacute;dier effets personnels Montr&eacute;al - Paris, Marseille, Bordeaux, Lyon devis gratuit.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cargo Excess est une compagnie sp&eacute;cialis&eacute;e dans le transport international et offrant toute une gamme de services. Bas&eacute;s au Canada, nous avons un r&eacute;seau d\'agents &agrave; travers le monde qui nous assure des contacts dans toutes les villes du globe et nous permet de maintenir la qualit&eacute; du service &agrave; destination.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">As one of the leading freight forwarder and house goods moving specialists in Canada, Cargo Excess has the resources and the experience needed to ensure on-time, on-budget transport. Cargo Excess works only with the best freight companies in the world, leveraging our high business volume to obtain real cost savings for our clients.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Excess luggage shipping Montreal, Toronto, Calgary we can help, free quote available on site. Personal effect shipping to Sydney, London, Australia, International Moving in Canada. Personal effect customs clearance at Montreal airport. Small parcels shipping Montreal, Toronto, Calgary, Ship cars Montreal, Toronto, Mississauga, Easy shipping in France, Shipping, Excess luggages shipping in Canada, Toronto, Vanvouver. Relocation Montreal, Toronto, Vancouver.Excess baggaes shipping in Canada. Ship by air and sea Canada excess luggages, baggages, personal effect.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1229, 1, 'E-Mec Inc.', 'info@e-mec.com', '96 Salisbury Ave, BROCKVILLE, Ontario, Canada ', '', ' (613) 340-5255', '', '', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Manufacturer&rsquo;s Representative providing Electro-Mechanical Solutions for Industry. Specializing in the Defence, Security, and Medical markets. Services offered include;&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Precision Machining (AS9100)&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Aluminium dip and vacuum brazing&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Welding and fabrication (including ballistic steel)&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Structural bonding&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Sheet metal fabrication&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Custom stampings&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Laser cutting&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-famil