(1230, 1, 'E-W Metal Works (1993) Inc.', 'info@ewmetal.com', '1050 Crawford Ave., WINDSOR, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ewmetal.com ', '(519) 253-5229', '(519) 253-2006', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">E-W Metal Works is ISO 9001:2000 registered and certified by The Canadian Welding Bureau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our company provides job shop manufacturing services to the machine tool industry. The staff of E-W Metal Works strive to manufacture products that conform to our customers requirements, on time and within budget.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our mission is to provide complete manufacturing services that exceed the expectations of our customers through continual improvement and the implementation of new technology.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1231, 1, 'E & M Copper Products Inc.', 'sales@emcopper.ca', '349A Henry St, BRANTFORD, Ontario, Canada', 'www.emcopper.ca ', '(519) 753-7999', '(519) 753-7103', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">E&amp;M has been in the business of manufacturing high-quality copper components for the refrigeration, air conditioning, automotive, heating ventilation and plumbing industries for over 27 years.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Easily accessed just off the 403 highway, the company is situated in Brantford, Ontario and provides quality components for our clients in North America and Europe, operating from a 17,000 sq. ft. modern facility.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">E&amp;M&rsquo;s large tool inventory allows us to supply many parts without additional tooling charges. If new tooling is required, it is manufactured to meet your specific requirements. We also carry a large inventory of fittings for automotive industry application.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our experienced staff is available to work with you throughout the design phase of any project, to offer suggestions for cost savings and ease of manufacture of custom tubular products. We are able to supply complete assemblies of components and also bend aluminum &amp; stainless steel.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">E&amp;M carries a broad range of raw materials from capillary tubes to 1-5/8&Prime; O.D. copper tubing in stock at all times. We are able to process customer orders expediently, thereby reducing lead-time.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1232, 1, 'E.T.L Electronics', 'info@astus.ca', '2396 de la Province St, LONGUEUIL, Quebec, Canada', 'www.etlelectronique.com ', '(450) 442-7887', '(450) 442-0605', '', '<p>&nbsp;After 17 years in the market, we are among an elite few long-established companies in the world to offer fleet management solutions. ETL Electronics, the company behind our Astus products, started out as the largest manufacturer of electronic anti-auto theft products in Canada, with over 400,000 installed ignition interlock systems. Always innovative, the business established itself among the first to offer fleet management solutions. Now, our customer-base of several thousand companies is spread over 3 continents.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We have built our reputation on our robust and innovative product offerings. Many of our clients have endured unfortunate experiences with competing offerings, and have found a product that meets and exceeds their expectations in Astus.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>An Established Business</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We offer our employees a stimulating environment and we get back full commitment and dedication. Our turnover rate of near zero and our relationships with long-standing customers are ringing and reassuring evidence of the quality of our management.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Growth and sustainability of ETL Electronics is mainly based on:</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Dynamic R&amp;D department, always on the lookout for changes in the market</div>\r\n<div>Reliable and evolving solutions</div>\r\n<div>Development of powerful and comprehensive software</div>\r\n<div>Commitment to customer service quality</div>\r\n<div>Manufacturing of electronic modules, housings, wires, as well as programming and quality control are accomplished locally. Our subcontractors must meet our strict quality and performance requirements.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>This way of operating allows us great flexibility in the products we offer: we can customize the product you purchase to exactly suit your needs.</div>', ''),
(1233, 1, 'Eadex Tecnologies Inc.', 'mike@eadex.com', '20 Hodges Lane, HUNTSVILLE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.eadex.com ', '(705) 788-1194', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Eadex Technologies is a full service web development company committed to providing clients with dynamic applications that solve specific online business needs. Our business to business and business to consumer client base ranges from small entrepreneurial businesses, to mid-sized businesses, including the service industry, manufacturing, and retail sectors.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We are able to merge the requirements of your business such as branding, content management, lead generation, email marketing, e-commerce stores, search engine optimization/marketing, social media, administrative reporting, and many other web-based services into a comprehensive solution.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">At Eadex, we strive to become your web solutions provider, as well as participate as an integral part of your overall marketing and technology objectives.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our Mission: Serve our customers by delivering high quality products and services resulting in trusted long-term relationships.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1234, 1, 'Eagle Sportswear Inc.', 'info@eaglecanada.com', '313 Supertest Rd, NORTH YORK, Ontario, Canada', 'www.eaglecanada.com ', '(416) 650-5144', '(416) 650-5172', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Eagle Sportswear was established in Toronto in 1988 manufacturing sportswear.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our Management has over 45 years of combined experience manufacturing apparel which began in the South Pacific, Fiji Islands.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Today, the company manufactures and distributes performance sportswear, customized uniforms and promotional products across Canada and the United States to various industries.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Some Industry Clients:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Corporate Offices<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theme Parks<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Event Centres<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Retail Stores<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sports Organizations<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Government Institutions<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Major Brands Distributed:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;Skins, ACSkins, Active Cotton, The Lock, Eagle, Ash City, Debco,Trimark Sportswear, PVH, Forsyth, Calvin Klein, Ralph Lauren, JMJ, Nygard and Dickies.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our services include in-house manufacturing and embroidery for custom uniforms as well as on-site measuring where applicable.&nbsp; We also offer free consulting for uniform requirements, including samples, based on volume of business.&nbsp;&nbsp; In addition, for larger uniform programs, we offer unique proposals including staff rewards and volume rebates.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We are committed to providing the best quality products at competitive prices and complete customer service.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We thank you for this opportunity and look forward to hearing from you.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1235, 1, 'Eagle Steel Inc.', 'eaglesteeljf@bellnet.ca', '1870 Gage Crt, MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, Canada', 'www.eaglesteelinc.ca ', '(905) 672-7010', '(905) 672-7513', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Founded in 1972 by Kurt Kristensen, Eagle Steel has grown with its customers and is rooted in providing outstanding service as our #1 priority. Our attention to detail has promoted a long list of satisfied customers who return year after year for their next security or storage system.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">About eagle steel: For many decades, three generations of family have combined their experience and integrity into a business that has forged a solid reputation as the industry leader in mezzanine installation companies, wire mesh security partitions, guardrails and various warehouse security products. In addition, many valued employees, including management, installation crews and production, offer decades of expertise all working with the objective to provide a quality product from start to finish.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">As the manufacturer we can offer a prompt response to all inquiries regarding your specific material handling needs and without a middle man the costs to you are substantially lower. Our in-house advantage allows for great personal attention to our customers during the process from quotation, design, shipping and installation.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The standard of excellence for all our products can be identified by superior materials, certified welding, and designs that have been engineered to meet rigid industry standards. Each order is customized to meet your specific application and is expedited in the most efficient manner.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">You can count on Eagle Steel to continue leading the industry both in product and in providing a customer service relationship that is second to none.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1236, 1, 'ebackup Inc.', 'info@ebackupinc.com', '35 McTavish Place NE, CALGARY, Alberta, Canada ', 'www.ebackupinc.com ', '(403) 259-3620', '(403) 259-3628', '', '<p>&nbsp;KeepItSafe offers a new paradigm in online data backup and protection - one that lets our customers protect and access their data from any device in any location, as well as continuously protect their applications and systems. KeepItSafe has operations in major markets around the world, including North America, Europe, and Australasia.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>KeepItSafe parent company j2 Global, Inc. (NASDAQ: JCOM), is a leading provider of cloud services, helping improve business performance and efficiency for over 12 million customers worldwide. Our growing family of brands provides essential business tools such as online faxing, unified communications, hosted email services, email marketing, virtual phone systems, and online backup. j2 Global\'s network spans 49 countries over 6 continents.</div>', ''),
(1237, 1, 'ecarpetgallery', 'info@ecarpetgallery.com', '2251 Lapierre, lasalle, Quebec, Canada ', 'www.ecarpetgallery.com ', '(514) 272-8000', '(514) 272-8300', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Ecarpetgallery is the largest online retailer of a wide range of top quality hand-made oriental carpets and machine-made rugs. We deliver exquisite designs, elegance and unbeatable value directly to your door. Shop for authentic silk and wool rugs by color, size or style, including Aubousson, Chobi, Heriz, Sarabi, floral designs, geometric, medallion, cowhides, shags, sheepskins, and many more. With over 30,000 hand-made, traditional or modern carpets to choose from, you&rsquo;ll find the perfect rug for your home.&nbsp;</span></p>', ''),
(1238, 1, 'Echo Metal Products International Inc.', 'customerservice@echometal.ca', '150-10451 Shellbridge Way, RICHMOND, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.echometal.ca ', '(604) 709-9769', '(604) 708-9679', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Echo Metal manufactures and wholesales high quality metal products.We operate our own factory in China.Our factory staff of 100 consists of senior engineers, technicians and skilled workers.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">*About The Company and Its Products:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">15 years of International Business Experience .<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Incorporated in Canada<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Modern Manufacturing Centre in China;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Professional Customer Services Centre Located in Vancouver Canada;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Metal Products of the Highest Quality Guaranteed at Competitive Prices;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ability to Customize Metal Products as per Drawings or Samples;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Professional Quality Control to Meet or Exceed Required International Quality Standards;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Services to Customers in Canada ,Europe and U.S.A(via Eastbase Supplies Inc. Subsidiary);<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Flexible Payment Terms;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">On-time Delivery to Designated Destination;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">No Hidden Costs, What We Quote is What You Pay;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Convenient Purchasing, Place Your Orders Locally and We Will Do All the Rest;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">*A Wide Range of Products<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We supply metal products to a wide range of customers in forestry, automotive parts, off-highway construction, railroad, farm equipment, oil production.Our products include custom forging/casting metal products per drawings or samples, standard ASTM/NACM chains, rigging hardwares, trailer winches and winch bars, loadbinders, webbings, tie down straps, wire ropes and more metal products used in different industries.(See our products list in Home page)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The products are made of carbon steel, alloy steel, aluminium, bronze, copper and stainless steel.They are processed by forging, stamping, casting, machining and extrusion. Our professional and technical design EXPERTISE enables us to work with you to develop new custom products as per samples or drawings.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">*Competitive Prices<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Operating our own factory and serving international customers for more than 15 years enable us to maintain an excellent product line.Many of these products are made in our own factory in China, at the same time we are be able to source out products through our alliance with more than 50 qualified manufacturers;whatever the source, you can count on our deversified products meeting or exceeding Northern Amercian and International standards; you can also count on our competitive pricing and excellent customer service.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">*Excellent Quality Products<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We deliver excellent quality products.We achieve this by guaranteeing professional quality control.Our on- site professional engineers monitor the manufacturing process to ensure that the quality of all products meet the required standards.Our engineers inspect the quality, packing, marking for every shipment and issue inspection reports before we deliver the products to you.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">*Superior Customer Services<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">All of our staff are well-experienced in international trade.The operation system (Quotation process, order taking, production,quality control inspections,logistics and after-sale service) has been successfully operating for more than 15 years. Your importing quality metal products is as easy as your purchases in domestic market,you place the order locally and we will handle all the rest.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1239, 1, 'ECO Environmental Communication Options', 'inquiries@ecostrategy.ca', '400-19 Yorkville, TORONTO, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ecostrategy.ca ', '(416) 972-7401', '(416) 972-7434', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Environmental Communication Options (ECO) is a specialized communications firm with a unique insight into the environmental and energy landscape.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Through 30 years of experience, we have developed deep insight and understanding of the history, issues and culture in these sectors. Our unparalleled experience, professional network and industry knowledge provide us with an understanding of the elements related to your cause. We know how to reach your audience.<o:p></o:p></p>', '');
