(1240, 1, 'Edac Inc.', 'edac@edac.net', '161 Alden Rd Units 7 & 8, MARKHAM, Ontario, Canada', 'www.edac.net ', '(416) 754-3322', '(416) 754-3299', '', '<p>&nbsp;Edac Inc. is a Canadian success story. Established in 1966, Edac became a world leader in the Card Edge and Rack &amp; Panel industry. Many of our legacy designs are still in use today though over the years, we&rsquo;ve expanded our line to include one of the widest ranges of interconnect solutions in the world.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Headquartered in Markham, Ontario, Edac now has design and customer service centers worldwide, manufacturing facilities in China, and customer logistics centers in Canada, United States, UK, Taiwan and Hong Kong.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>The connector has evolved over the last 45 years and Edac has been one of the leaders in the industry&rsquo;s evolution. Edac offers a wide range of products including Card Edge, Rack and Panel, RJ45 &amp; Telecom Jacks, USB &amp; Firewire, Waterproof, PLCC Sockets, D-Sub, Pin Headers and custom cable assemblies.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Edac also has the ability to deliver custom connectors ranging from minor product variations to full custom solutions from concept to finished goods in less than 12 weeks and prototypes usually under 4 weeks.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We can also support low volume orders for many product variations which many of our competitors can not. We do this because our commitment is not only to your production needs but all your prototyping needs as well.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We have an extensive Global customer support system that includes dedicated inside sales service, highly trained field support, and a global distributor and representative network that can co-ordinate the timely delivery of Edac products to any factory in any country and proactively resolve any issues in a timely manner.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>At Edac, we are proud of our global Engineering Team. Based in North America, China and the UK, they travel the world to meet team&rsquo;s specialty is resolving electronic connector issues by designing cost-effective interconnect solutions that exceed the expectations of our customers.</div>', ''),
(1241, 1, 'Edge Design and Marketing', 'admin@edgedesign.ca', '230 Reuben Cres., KEMPTVILLE, Ontario, Canada ', '', '(613) 686-3177', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;Design and marketing firm located in Ottawa, Ontario. We specialize in internet and viral marketing, graphic design, web design, eCommerce, e-learning modules and online game creation. We pride ourselves on our creative, new ideas. &nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1242, 1, 'Edwards Door Systems Limited', 'bcrombeen@edwardsdoors.com', '147 Stronach Cres., LONDON, Ontario, Canada', 'www.edwardsdoors.com ', '(519) 659-0452', '(519) 659-9871', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We focus on identifying the needs of the marketplace and delivering quality products and services to our architectural clients and end users.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We specialize in promoting, detailing and providing technical specification expertise for custom designed products to the larger Architectural, Engineering and Design Firms, as well as School Boards, Hospitals, Casinos and Government Departments.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">From assistance with product selection through the timely completion of your project, &quot;You have come to the right source for your door system solutions!&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1243, 1, 'EEC Industries Ltd.', 'eec@eecind.com', '1237 Welch St., NORTH VANCOUVER,, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.eecind.com ', '(604) 986-5633', '(604) 986-2999', '', '<p>&nbsp;EEC Industries is the leading provider of architectural signs locally and around the world. From luxury hotels &amp; resorts to a variety of commercial, institutional and multi-unit residential projects, EEC Industries has the capability of meeting the needs of our customers\' signage requirements.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We specialise in crafting signage to client specifications or creating custom designs to meet specific requirements. EEC Industries offers diversity in products, all of which are created on site in our Vancouver facility. As a custom sign company, we have the capability to manufacture signs in all types of materials, using advanced methods and equipment. Decades of experience enables us to adapt and implement the very latest techniques in production &amp; finishing.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our core values of craftsmanship, service and attention to detail have set us apart since our inception in 1973.</div>', ''),
(1244, 1, 'EFES TILE INC.', 'info@efestile.com', '1100 South Service Rd, STONEY CREEK,, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.efestile.com ', '(905) 643-5277', '(905) 643-5275', '', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">EFES Tile is an importer and dealer of natural stone tile, porcelain tile, and mosaic tile. Locally owned and operated, we offer an extensive selection of tiles and mosaics with products for everyone&rsquo;s taste and budget. Line Building Supplies Wholesaler-Distributors.</span></p>', ''),
(1245, 1, 'EGS Electrical Group Canada Ltd.', 'info@egscanada.com', '99 Union St, ELMIRA, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.egscanada.com ', '(519) 669-9222', '(519) 669-6389', '', '<p>&nbsp;As a global manufacturer of electrical products for commercial, industrial, hazardous and adverse environments, Appleton Group offers the industry&rsquo;s best known and most highly regarded brands. From the latest innovations to familiar products that have led the industry for decades, the brands of Appleton Group offer durability, safety, quality, easy installation and global availability.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Appleton Group, formerly known as EGS Electrical Group, brings together the world&rsquo;s most recognized brands: Appleton, ATX, O-Z/Gedney, SolaHD, EasyHeat, Nelson Heat Trace, Nelson Firestop, McGill and Nutsteel. We are a trusted, global supplier of steel boxes and fittings, heat tracing cables, power supplies, explosionproof controls, floor warming systems, industrial lighting and much more.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>For product selection, quality, ease of installation and reliability in use, count on Appleton Group to supply the familiar products that have led the industry for decades&mdash;as well as the innovations that will drive new opportunities in the decades to come.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Stretching back as far as 1847, the companies that make up Appleton Group are all pioneers in their respective fields. Today, they stand for a heritage of proven quality and an enduring commitment to innovation. Backed by the resources of Emerson, they are ready to supply and support all the electrical solutions you need.&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1246, 1, 'EHA Engineering Ltd.', 'a.hayden@EHAengineering.com', 'P.O. Box 2711 Stn B, RICHMOND HILL, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ehaengineering.com ', '(416) 460-3048', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;EHA Engineering Ltd is a group of Consulting Engineers in the fields of hydrometallurgy and mineral &nbsp;processing. &nbsp;Experience gained on many &nbsp;projects &nbsp;include the processing of ores and materials for the &nbsp;recovery of arsenic, beryllium, bismuth, cobalt, &nbsp;copper, &nbsp;diamonds, gold, graphite, lead, magnesium, &nbsp;molybdenum, &nbsp;nickel, platinum/palladium, rare earths, &nbsp;rhenium, silver, &nbsp;strontium, tungsten, uranium, &nbsp;vanadium, and zinc.</p>', ''),
(1247, 1, 'EHT Design', 'info@ehtdesign.com', '109 Miranda Ave, YORK, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ehtdesign.com ', '(416) 256-2722', '(416) 256-4329', '', '<p>&nbsp;EHT Design is a Canadian leading specialist in premium quality cowhide rugs and leather carpets.</p>\r\n<div>We also offer custom upholstery services and custom furniture for the residential and hospitality sectors. EHT Design is a Canadian-owned company in business since 2004.</div>\r\n<div>Quality and excellence is what put EHT Design above others in the market. Our stock is hand-picked from hundreds of hides, going one by one and choosing only the best in quality and design with the purpose of offering you a wide range of the very best quality hides and rugs. Through our e-commerce website we offer excellent customer service and deliver all over Canada, USA, Europe &amp; the Caribbean.</div>', ''),
(1248, 1, 'Eidap Inc.', 'info@eidap.com', '14 Chippewa Rd, SHERWOOD PARK, Alberta, Canada', 'www.eidap.com ', '(780) 467-2707', '(866) 467-5160', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">In the nearly 15 years that EIDAP Inc. has been involved in the relatively new market of Electronic Identification, our company has established itself as the largest supplier of microchips for use in companion animals in Canada. Animal and owner information is stored in the EIDAP Animal Registry, which is available 24 hours per day - 7 days per week &ndash; 365 days per year, making it very simple to reunite a lost pet with its owner as quickly as possible.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">In addition to servicing the companion animal market, EIDAP Inc. works with researchers across North America by providing identification devices and custom scanners to accommodate their unique requirements.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">EIDAP&rsquo;s reliable technology and expertise provides a secure system, able to respond to a dynamic marketplace, both now and in the future.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1249, 1, 'EIP Manufacturing Inc.', 'eip@eipmfg.ca', '965 Cecelia St, PEMBROKE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.eipmfg.ca ', '(613) 735-8095', '(613) 735-2961', '', '<p>&nbsp;EIP Mfg, formerly known as Eddy Industrial Products, was founded in 1957 as a division of the Eddy Match Company. The function of this division was to develop and manufacture highly specialized machinery for the match industry and to service the associated companies in the Eddy Match group.</p>\r\n<div>When Eddy Match ceased production in 1998, the Eddy Industrial Products division was purchased by two local businessmen, Michael and Tim Harrington, who recognized the company\'s potential for growth.</div>\r\n<div>Eddy Industrial Products became EIP Mfg in September 1999, and moved to its current location on Cecelia Street in July 2000. Within 12 months of the move, EIP doubled its machining capacity and increased its work force by 70 per cent. EIP Mfg is now a certified ISO 9000:2000 company with a broad customer base including the aerospace, automotive, and steel cabinet industries.</div>\r\n<div>Today, EIP Mfg is a custom precision machine shop, specializing in the design, development and manufacture of custom tooling and associated components. Future business to include production machining and inspection.</div>', ''),
(1250, 1, 'Ek\'eau services', 'ekeau@videotron.ca', 'C.P. 55007, REPENTIGNY, Quebec, Canada ', 'www.services-ekeau.com ', '(450) 841-1177', '(450) 585-4498', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ekeau supplies a range of watercoolers at work, friends of the Environment!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Friends of the environment, because unlike traditional watercoolers with bottle of 18 liters, Ekeau\'s watercoolers use a filter system. Two major advantages: No pollution with plastics, No bottle to buy, No handle.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ekeau also supplies a range of coffee machines at work, friends of the environment!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our choice of machines are always guided by the ecological aspect, we ban by examples polluting machines that use containers or plastic bucket. We favor the bulk coffee.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The team members Ekeau have developed experience in nearly 30 years in OEM products for the home environment.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">They developed product concepts for chains of distributors (Europe, Africa, North America).The main objective of today\'s team is working on products, friends of our environment. Technicians and installers of machinery Ekeau Service have extensive experience and thousands installations.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1251, 1, 'ek pass Corp.', 'contact@ekpass.com', '6-64 Riel Dr., ST. ALBERT, Alberta, Canada', 'www.ekpass.com ', '(780) 459-5850', '(780) 459-0711', '', '<p>&nbsp;Heavy Equipment Operator Training on Over 100 Manufacturer&rsquo;s Equipment in Over 170 Locations</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>EKpass is a seasoned, internationally recognized, professional heavy equipment operator and safety training organization. We&rsquo;re dedicated to enhancing performance, productivity, safety in the workplace, employee morale, and profitability.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>EKpass is a registered vendor with NATO and the United Nations.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Worldwide, EKpass serves many industries and sectors: mining, industrial, military, forestry, city, county, municipal, railroad, agricultural, petrochemical, manufacturing, construction, pipeline, water and sewer, the oil patch, and many more. We customize training programs and materials to accommodate most categories.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We maintain close relationships with leading manufacturers and equipment suppliers, keeping close tabs on developments in the equipment industry. Training is conducted in our clients&rsquo; operations. Engaging classroom instruction and discussion is combined with &ldquo;hands-on&rdquo; experience, using machines on our clients&rsquo; job sites. Operators learn on the machines they use on the job, a method proven to give a strong and enduring learning experience.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our proven model of heavy equipment operator instruction is interpersonal, interactive, and participative.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>EKpass takes pride in our growing list of clients; time after time, our knowledge, service, professionalism and integrity are what brings them in &ndash; and brings them back.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Find out what we can do for you &ndash; contact us now for a preliminary consultation at no obligation!</div>', ''),
(1252, 1, 'ELAM ltee', 'info@elam.qc.ca', '2352 Duvernay St, MONTREAL, Quebec, Canada', 'www.elam.ca ', '(514) 395-1948', '(514) 395-2321', '', '<p>&nbsp;ELAM, language school for business people, acts as a leader in the field of second language education for the business.</p>', ''),
(1253, 1, 'Elastic Path Software Inc.', 'marketing@elasticpath.com', '300-455 Granville St, VANCOUVER, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.elasticpath.com', '(604) 408-8078', '(604) 408-8079', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We help businesses maximize revenue from their goods, services, and content with solutions that empower companies to create outstanding customer experiences that drive engagement and conversion. Elastic Path technology brings this functionality to multiple touchpoints &ndash; websites, apps, APIs, and more &ndash; while generating a single view of the customer.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Elastic Path powers digital customer experiences for over 200 global enterprise customers, and supports them with over 130 dedicated employees in North America, the UK, and around the world. For four consecutive years, we earned a spot on the PROFIT 100 ranking of the fastest-growing companies in Canada.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Elastic Path is covered in the most important analyst reports and market evaluations, including the Gartner&reg; CRM Vendor Guide, Gartner&reg; Hype Cycle&trade; For Digital Marketing, and the Forrester&reg; Market Overview for Digital Commerce Solutions.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Technologists from interface developers to the CTO love Elastic Path because no other enterprise solution is more scalable, flexible, and easier to integrate with customer touchpoints and other enterprise applications. Our products, including Elastic Path Commerce and Elastic Path for Adobe Marketing Cloud, are built on an open-source Java foundation, and feature great documentation &ndash; increasing productivity and reducing total cost of ownership.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1254, 1, 'Embassy Flavours Ltd.', 'sales@embassyflavours.com', '2-5 Intermodal Dr, BRAMPTON, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.embassyflavours.com ', '(905) 789-3200', '(905) 789-3201', '', '<p>&nbsp;At Embassy Flavours we combine creativity and science to provide our customers with the very best innovative flavours and bakery ingredients available. &nbsp;Whether you need a specific flavour, customized bakery base, functional ingredient or a completely integrated signature bakery product &ndash; Embassy delivers!</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We have an on-site flavour lab and full bakery test kitchen staffed with certified flavourists, food scientists and bakery specialists. &nbsp;We formulate, test and manufacture a wide range of flavours and bakery ingredients ensuring that taste, quality and performance are built into every product. We take pride in addressing your needs quickly so you can take advantage of changing food trends and customer opportunities.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our versatile manufacturing plant is BRC certified, nut-free and Kosher certified. &nbsp;Our Quality Assurance team ensures that the highest standards are met by bake-testing every batch of bakery ingredients, and all of our flavours are tested through sensory panel and organoleptic evaluation.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Embassy Flavours has the experts and the expertise you need to make your products a success. &nbsp;Contact us at info@embassyflavours.comif you would like to speak to someone about your customized flavour or bakery needs.</div>', ''),
(1255, 1, 'Emego Trading Co Ltd', 'ftin@emego.ca', '7373, rue Cordner, LASALLE, Quebec, Canada', '', '(514) 365-0202', '(514) 366-9031', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Footwear Wholesaler-Distributors</span></p>', ''),
