(1257, 1, 'Enable Interconnect Inc', 'solutions@enableconnect.com', '716 Colonel Sam Dr., Oshawa, Ontario, Canada', 'www.enableconnect.com ', '(905) 579-2316', '(905) 579-9991', '', '<p>Enable specializes in cable assemblies, wire harnesses, panel assemblies and box builds. &nbsp;We provide electro-mechanical design, manufacturing, parts and services for high-reliability industrial, commercial, aerospace and defense applications. &nbsp;If you have a power or signal interconnectivity requirement, we have the solution! &nbsp;Our team of professionals are here to provide you with the best quality and service the industry has to offer. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><br />\r\n</span></div>', ''),
(1258, 1, 'Enable Interconnect Inc', 'solutions@enableconnect.com', '716 Colonel Sam Dr., Oshawa, Ontario, Canada', 'www.enableconnect.com ', '(905) 579-2316', '(905) 579-9991', '', '<p>Enable specializes in cable assemblies, wire harnesses, panel assemblies and box builds. &nbsp;We provide electro-mechanical design, manufacturing, parts and services for high-reliability industrial, commercial, aerospace and defense applications. &nbsp;If you have a power or signal interconnectivity requirement, we have the solution! &nbsp;Our team of professionals are here to provide you with the best quality and service the industry has to offer. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><br />\r\n</span></div>', ''),
(1259, 1, 'Enchpro Chemicals Corp.', 'sales@enchprochem.com', '55-8 Glen Watford Dr. , SCARBOROUGH, Ontario, Canada', 'www.enchprochem.com ', '(416) 637-6907', '(416) 637-5327', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Enchpro Chemicals Corp. is a professional and experienced global chemical distributor in food additives and pharmaceutical industry. Enchpro provides creative sourcing solutions, quality product alternatives and&nbsp; customer service as a worldwide. Our extensive product knowledge and industry experience support our commitment to provide creative sourcing solutions and value-added options for your business.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We invite you to become familiar with Enchpro Chemicals Corp., which is a progressive and growing specialty healty and funtional products distributor. We make specialty high quality product for the food, cosmetics, healthy care markets. We have been known for innovation, agility, growth and socially responsible business practices. Our reputation has earned us appreciation awards from the excellent relationships with our clients around the world. Growing from a basic chemical distributor, we now provide amino acid, Vitamins and Plant extractions. We has continued to provide additional diversified value-added services and products throughout the years to meet our customers\' requirements, so they can succeed in a rapidly changing world.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">All of us at Enchpro Chemicals are committed to service and quality. Customers can rely on Enchpro\'s products, whether under private brand or the Enchpro label, and be assured of expert technical support and quick responses. Our mission is to continue to create sustainable partnerships worldwide by providing innovative and competitive sourcing solutions. Our success is based on the ethics and ingenuity of our team. We create an environment that promotes growth for our employees, partners and community. We thank all of our customers and suppliers for their support and growth. As a customer driven corporation, it is our goal to provide the best and most cost effective product available anywhere in the world. Enchpro Chemicals Corp. is your Right Chemical Source.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1260, 1, 'Engineering Dynamics Limited', 'robin@dynamicaqs.com', '137 Pick Rd, CARLETON PLACE, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.dynamicaqs.com ', '(613) 257-5450', '(613) 257-7397', '', '<p>&nbsp;In 2012 Dynamic Air Quality Solutions celebrated the thirtieth anniversary of the first one-inch polarized-media electronic air cleaner. &nbsp;It was thirty years ago that the first polarized-media electronic air cleaner, produced under our &quot;Dynamic Air Cleaner&quot; brand, was introduced. &nbsp;Since that time, Dynamic Air Quality Solutions has manufactured IAQ products for several OEMs and contracting network groups.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Dynamic Air Cleaners utilize active&ndash;field, non-ionizing polarized-media technology. &nbsp;While Dynamic has pioneered and perfected its application to air cleaning in general HVAC applications, the basic principals have been around for a long time. In fact, the word &ldquo;electricity&rdquo; comes from the Greek word for amber, elekton. &nbsp;It was observed that dust particles would hop onto amber after it had been rubbed. &nbsp;That magical force was called electricity. &nbsp;The first electrically-enhanced air filters date back to 1930 and combine elements of both passive and electrostatic filtration. As with most high-efficiency filtration products, polarized media had its roots in industrial applications. Although there have been a number of different configurations since then, all are based on charging, or polarizing, fibers in a media and particles in the air in order to generate an electric force between the fibers and particles. While the principle has been around for many decades, it has only been in recent years that the technology has been fully understood to maximize effectiveness and to provide consistent, reliable performance.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>In 1982, two university professors from Carleton University in Ontario, Canada developed a polarized media design for a residential application that provided a simple means of replacing dirty media. They started Engineering Dynamics, Ltd. (EDL) and began manufacturing 1&rdquo; and 2&rdquo; polarized-media air cleaners, room console units and overhead ceiling-mount units, all under the Dynamic brand. All of the polarized-media air cleaners on the market today can be traced back to beginnings at EDL, although subsequent patents and refinements have created discernable differences in the product designs and features.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>In 1993, EDL was acquired by Environmental Dynamics Group, one of EDL&rsquo;s largest distributors. &nbsp;The companies are now known as Dynamic Air Quality Solutions. &nbsp;The primary manufacturing remains in Carleton Place, Ontario, while sales and engineering are based in the Princeton, New Jersey headquarters. &nbsp; While EDL&rsquo;s initial focus was primarily residential, Dynamic has also worked to address the clear need for improved air quality and energy savings in commercial and industrial applications. This has resulted in a focus on technology enhancements, new configurations, and a complete line of commercial products that now dominate in some categories, with healthcare and energy retrofits being the two largest business segments.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Dynamic has doubled sales every few years, invests heavily in research and product development and has a variety of patents in the field.</div>', ''),
(1261, 1, 'EOA Scientific Systems, Inc.', 'generalinfo@eoascientific.com', '11A Parkhill Rd, HALIFAX, Nova Scotia, Canada', 'www.eoascientific.com ', '(902) 477-1908', '(902) 477-6834', '', '<p>&nbsp;EOA Scientific Systems and ScienceSchoolHouse have served the educational community for 14 years, designing, developing, and distributing interactive multimedia science software. The core library that we distribute was developed by us, and is continually enhanced and expanded. We also sell high quality software developed by other companies.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We have been developing our own products since 1992, and have also developed products under contract for various clients. The products we develop and sell consist of the best truly interactive and multimedia educational content possible, and satisfy U.S. and Canadian national, state and provincial learning standards for middle, high school and early university science topics. Educators across North America and internationally have endorsed the excellence and comprehensiveness of EOA products.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>But don\'t take our word for it. Visit our products page to find out more about Discover! Science, view samples and obtain a trial subscription to our online library.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1262, 1, 'EODC Inc.', 'info@eodc.ca', '1377 Triole St, GLOUCESTER, Ontario, Canada', 'www.eodc.ca ', '(613) 748-5549', '(613) 748-1293', '', '<p>&nbsp;EODC (Engineering Office Deisenroth Canada) Engineering, Development and Licencing Incorporated (EODC Inc.) is the exclusive Canadian representative of IBD Deisenroth Engineering of Lohmar, Germany. IBD is a world-class company with more than 30 years experience in research and development of advanced high-tech survivability systems.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Since 2001, EODC has manufactured and delivered combat-tested add-on armour (AoA) and protection kits that continue to protect members of the Canadian Armed Forces from improvised explosive devices (IEDs), land mines and enemy fire.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We know Canadian armoured vehicle requirements. We provide quality products and services, on time and on budget.</div>', ''),
(1263, 1, 'EP Medical Power', 'inquiry.medicalpower@eaglepicher.com', '13136 82A Ave, SURREY, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.eaglepicher.com ', '(604) 543-4350', '(604) 597-0814', '', '<p>&nbsp;EaglePicher Technologies is an industry leader in integrated power solutions. Demands on technology call for batteries and devices that are both smaller and lighter, yet deliver more energy while increasing safety. In response to these demands, we are providing the newest technology innovations which support our customers from concept to final production.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>In the span of 169 years, we have created, innovated, and customized solutions for a multitude of defense, aerospace, commercial, and medical customers. Our research and development capabilities are unsurpassed. With a team consisting of over 250 astute scientists and accomplished engineers, combined with our state-of-the-art equipment and facilities, EaglePicher is creating energy storage solutions to meet our customers\' specific and specialized power needs. At EaglePicher, we ensure the right power is always available. Whether it is EaglePicher&rsquo;s cutting-edge research in hybrid technologies or ground-breaking innovation modernization in the oil and gas industries, you can look to the experts at EaglePicher for the solution.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1264, 1, 'EP - Engineered Pump Systems Ltd.', 'epsl@telus.net', '1635 Industrial Ave, PORT COQUITLAM, British Columbia, Canada', '', '(604) 552-7900', '(604) 552-7901', '', '<p>&nbsp;Engineered Pump Systems Ltd. was incorporated in 1982, with the primary markets being municipal, industrial and building trades. Sales and support staff total 12 people. Average sales, 4.0 million.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Engineered Pump Systems Ltd. specializes in the supply and manufacture of water and wastewater conveyance, treatment and disposal products (submersible pumps, air blowers, rotating screens, valves, controls, etc.). Equipment can be supplied in complete factory built packages or as components for on site installations.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Engineered Pump Systems Ltd. has built a reputation as a trusted provider of knowledge and quality products, backed up by over a decade of excellent customer service. &nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1265, 1, 'Epurair Inc.', 'info@epurair.com', '149 J.-A.-Bombardier Bureau 2, BOUCHERVILLE, Quebec, Canada', '', '(450) 464-6416', '(450) 464-8111', '', '<p>&nbsp;Epurair est un des plus importants manufacturiers de produits de qualit&eacute; de l&rsquo;air au Qu&eacute;bec. Chaque jour, le personnel de Epurair met au point de nouveaux produits renversants. L\'ing&eacute;niosit&eacute; et la qualit&eacute; sont au coeur des produits que nous fabriquons.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Nos professionnels de la sant&eacute; travaillent de concert avec notre d&eacute;partement d&rsquo;ing&eacute;nierie afin d\'incorporer les plus r&eacute;centes technologies dans le domaine de la qualit&eacute; de l\'air. Cette synergie nous permet d\'innover tout en am&eacute;liorant la sant&eacute; de nos clients.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Nous fabriquons les produits suivants;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&Eacute;changeur d&rsquo;air r&eacute;cup&eacute;rateur de chaleur ultra performant.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&Eacute;changeur d&rsquo;air et purificateur d&rsquo;air central combin&eacute;.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Purificateurs d&rsquo;air central et portatif.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Syst&egrave;mes de filtration d&rsquo;air 99% pour chauffage &agrave; air chaud.&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1266, 1, 'Équipements Boisbriand Inc.', 'equipementsboisbriand@hotmail.com', '226, rue Turgeon, SAINTE-THÉRÈSE, Quebec, Canada', '', '(450) 435-3237', '(450) 435-4054', '', '<p>&nbsp;We buy, sell, trade, rent, recondition heavy duty equipment as:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Excavators<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span>Make:<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span>Caterpillar&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Motor graders<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span>Komatsu&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Bulls<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span>John Deere&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Wheels loaders<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span>Volvo&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Skidders<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">	</span>Hitachi&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Etc.... Etc....&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We recondition the equipment to be ready to work.&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1267, 1, 'ER Plus Risk Management Group Inc.', 'info@erplus.com', '230-11120 Horseshoe Way, RICHMOND, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.erplus.com ', '(604) 275-9070', '(604) 275-9074', '', '<p>&nbsp;ER Plus Risk Management Group Inc. &ndash; Is committed to saving lives, reducing accidents, protecting equipment and property, and helping businesses save money. ER Plus Risk Management Group Inc. has three sectors that can change your company&rsquo;s culture.</p>', ''),
(1268, 1, 'ERE Information Security Auditors', 'ronl@ere-security.ca', '10 Parsons Crt. 1st Floor, THORNHILL, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ere-security.ca ', '(905) 764-3246', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">ERE Information Security Auditors: ERE provides extensive knowledge transfer<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">ERE IT security compliance auditors are information security compliance verification auditors. As an IT security auditor in Canada, we serve large and medium organizations across Canada, US, and Europe since 2000. The ERE IT security compliance auditing team has built client loyalty based upon the expertise of our certified security experts and upon our impartiality - ERE Security sells no hardware or software whatsoever.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our IT security audit methodology encompasses cyber security auditing one time snapshots, 7 24 IT security auditing, and 7 24 security compliance audits. As an extension of 24 x 7 IT security monitoring we provide managed security services.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">As a managed security service provider or MSSP our managed security services include operations for advanced firewalls, IDS, vulnerability scanning, and complete SIEM or Security and Event Management services.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1269, 1, 'Esdale Printing Co. Ltd.', 'info@esdaleprinting.com', '207 De Baets St, WINNIPEG, Manitoba, Canada', 'www.esdaleprinting.com ', '(204) 957-4900', '(204) 957-4909', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">To place an order or get help with a new project, enter our online Customer Service Center. To download useful software and find helpful information, search our Resources &amp; Support area. To learn more about us, browse through our Company Information section<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">An easy-to-use pulldown menu, search engine, and link to our contact form appear on each page. As well, feel free to consult the site map at any time if you\'re having trouble locating a particular item. If there\'s anything Esdale Printing in Winnipeg can do to improve our site, please let us know.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1270, 1, 'Esmond Manufacturing', 'mohan.gopal@teknion.com', '195 Nantucket Blvd, SCARBOROUGH, Ontario, Canada ', '', '(416) 759-3573', '(416) 759-0488', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;\">Semiconductor and Other Electronic Component Manufacturing</span></p>', ''),
(1271, 1, 'ET Industries Inc.', 'info@etindustries.com', '2-210 Willmott St, COBOURG, Ontario, Canada', 'www.etindustries.com ', '(888) 801-0700', '888-801-0700', '', '<p>&nbsp;ET Industries designs, manufactures, and distributes innovative kitchen and bath products. &nbsp;In business for over 20 years, we are proud of our attention to quality, detail, and customer service.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our business began with importing and distributing the renowned Siroflex product line &ndash; including the Amazing Acrobatic Sprayer &ndash; a market leader in sprayers and swivel aerators. &nbsp;Since then, we have designed and added other kitchen and bath products such as the Sinktastic sink stopper, the ThunderHead showerhead and our newest item, the Acrobat flexible sprayer.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our products can be found in selected home shows and catalogues in Canada and the United States. The Amazing Acrobatic Sprayer is distributed by WalMart USA. &nbsp;Sinktastics are available in most Bed, Bath and Beyond stores. &nbsp;For full availability in your area, please contact us.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We are always looking for motivated salespeople for any of our product lines.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Based in Toronto, Canada, ET Industries has been manufacturing its own designs since 1981, primarily in the kitchen and bath category. Introducing original, and innovative products at the rate of about one every six months is the mandate of the company.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>The mainstay of ET Industries business is the line of market-leading Amazing Acrobatic Sprayers &ndash; faucet sprayers and swivel aerators for the kitchen faucet, bathroom faucet, and laundry tub faucet, in a range of both economy and deluxe models.</div>', ''),
(1272, 1, 'ETP Metal Products Mfg. Ltd.', 'sales@etpmetals.com', '237 Toryork Dr., NORTH YORK, Ontario, Canada', 'www.etpmetals.com ', '(416) 741-9859', '(416) 741-1090', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">When we formed our company over 13 years ago, we decided to never settle and never compromise. Following our mission to create the best low-maintenance solutions for outdoor living, we have since become a premier choice for builders, architects and homeowners across North America.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">A proud Canadian manufacturer, ETP strives to marry form and functionality in each product we offer. By offering unlimited color options and a wide range of customizable features, we&rsquo;ve sought to create robust, high-quality aluminum products with more lasting visual appeal than their poor-quality plastic counterparts. And combined with our excellent dealer base and substantial warranties, we&rsquo;re proud to be known as a full-service manufacturer that builders and homeowner can rely on.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our family has been in the railing business since the mid 70&rsquo;s. We&rsquo;ve taken that experience at applied to creating ETP metals in 2001 in an effort to become the leader in low maintenance outdoor living solutions.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We began with our railing system and columns, and evolved most recently in to offering low maintenance aluminum decking and our industry leading and robust aluminum pergola structures.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1273, 1, 'Euler Hermes Canada', 'louis.plante@eulerhermes.com', '2810-1155 Rene-Levesque Blvd W, MONTREAL, Quebec, Canada', 'www.eulerhermes.ca ', '(514) 876-9656', '(514) 876-9658', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Euler Hermes offers services for both domestic and export business trade transactions, protecting clients against commercial and political risk in more than 200 countries and territories worldwide. We also provide services to help companies of all sizes outsource their debt collection, risk management and credit management information needs.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Euler Hermes Canada has historically advanced its products through a direct sales force. In addition, EH Canada has an expansive distribution network of brokers and third party alliances represented by over 50 specialty and P&amp;C producers.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1274, 1, 'Euro-Pharm International Canada Inc.', 'info@euro-pharm.com', '9400 Langelier Blvd, SAINT-LEONARD, Quebec, Canada', 'www.euro-pharm.com ', '(514) 323-8757', '(514) 323-6325', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Founded in 1996, EURO-PHARM has grown rapidly and offers a diversified pharmaceutical product line for adults and children.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Based in Montreal, EURO-PHARM develops, manufactures and distributes high-quality innovative products. It offers an impressive product line, including calcium, iron, potassium and vitamin supplements, analgesics and laxatives for adults, as well as vitamins and acetaminophen for children.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">EURO-PHARM\'s dedicated professionals are the foundation of its success. Our expanding team includes highly-qualified scientific, marketing and sales professionals. Our departments of research and regulatory affairs, quality control/quality assurance, and operations are committed to meeting and exceeding the highest industry standards.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Recruited for their proven experience in the pharmaceutical industry, our staff members are dedicated to a shared goal of continued excellence.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We would like to thank our customers, suppliers and employees, and we are looking forward to continued success.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1275, 1, 'Evalulab Inc', 'info@evalulab.com', '206-5475 Pare St, MONT-ROYAL, Quebec, Canada ', 'www.evalulab.com/en ', '(514) 343-0001', '(514) 343-9996', '', '<p>&nbsp;Evalulab specializes in Tolerance, Efficacy, and Consumer Preference testing for personal care and natural health products. Our aim is to help manufacturers and marketing firms to predict and boost the success potential of their products and to substantiate their marketing claims with reliable data.&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1276, 1, 'Everdry Forest Products Ltd', 'info@everdry.ca', '67 Tradewind Dr, OAKVILLE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.everdry.ca ', '(905) 842-6411', '(905) 842-9076', '', '<p>&nbsp;DryVac treatments and application systems have been developed to improve the durability of wood through enhanced water repellency.</p>\r\n<div>Products include DryVac 1010, a solvent based water repellent wood preservative developed for the door and window industry, and DryVac 1030, a water based treatment that confers excellent water repellency with minimal grain raising.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>The DryVac double vacuum system enables the millwork manufacturer to control both the quantity of treatment and the depth of penetration, depending on wood species and vulnerability to outdoor exposure. When you use our product, your customers will know your wood has been treated from the inside out!</div>', ''),
(1277, 1, 'Evonik Cyro Canada Inc.', 'janet.oneail@evonik.com', '101-180 Attwell Dr., Etobicoke, Ontario, Canada', 'www.acrylite.net ', '(905) 677-1388', '(905) 677-3871', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Evonik Industries is a worldwide manufacturer of PMMA products sold under the ACRYLITE&reg; trademark in the Americas and under the PLEXIGLAS&reg; trademark in the European, Asian, African and Australian continents.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Designers, fabricators, architects, engineers and end-users have come to rely on ACRYLITE&reg; sheet products to meet their unique challenges in a broad range of markets including P-O-P displays, store fixtures, conservation glazing, architectural interior, furniture, greenhouses, aircraft glazing and security applications.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1278, 1, 'eWerks Inc', 'inquiries@ewerksinc.com', '2186 Mountain Grove Ave Box 420, BURLINGTON, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.ewerksinc.com ', '(905) 319-7756', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Since 1998 eWerks Inc has provided product design and technical support services to our valued customers.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Babbage\'s Differential Engine<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We bring extensive experience with microcontroller integration, prototype development, PCB layout, manufacturing, and agency certifications to your project. Our technical know-how and industry partners will help get your shiny new idea to market. Small or large we welcome all inquiries.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">eWerks Inc specializes in designing with Microchip products. Visit the Microchip web site for more information by clicking the Microchip logo below<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1279, 1, 'Exact Furniture Limited', 'jimf@exactfurniture.com', '1-33 Alex Ave, WOODBRIDGE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.exactfurniture.com ', '(905) 856-8887', '(905) 856-6344', '', '<p>Exact Furniture is a manufacturer and distributor of high quality furniture products that are attractively designed and competitively priced. Our product line includes podiums, lecterns, Plasma TV stands, A/V carts, projector and multi-media carts for the videoconferencing, and A/V equipment for education and training markets. We also do custom designs and store fixture work, which includes custom mill work for store fixtures and educational markets.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Exact Furniture manufactures a wide range of furniture related to the audio visual market. &nbsp; Our major product lines are Podiums, &nbsp;Tables, &nbsp;Credenzas (including rack carts), &nbsp;Videoconferencing carts, &nbsp;Desks and &nbsp;Custom furniture. &nbsp;We sell to several end markets with a major emphasis on educational, corporate and government markets. &nbsp;The experience we have gained meeting the high standards of these institutions has allowed Exact Furniture to become a leader in developing contemporary furniture that enhances productivity.</p>\r\n<p>We strongly believe in supporting our dealer network across North America and strive to provide the best customer service in the industry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><br />\r\n</span></div>', ''),
(1280, 1, 'Eyedro Green Solutions Inc.', 'info@eyedro.com', '100-151 Charles St W, KITCHENER, Ontario, Canada', 'www.eyedro.com ', '(226) 499-0944', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;Eyedro Green Solutions Inc. is a designer and manufacturer of electronics and web-based services, with&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">a focus on electricity monitoring and analysis. Our goal is to make electricity monitoring affordable,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">understandable, and accessible to everyone &#150; from light industrial all the way through to home-owners. &nbsp;</span></p>', ''),
