(1410, 1, 'Hub International HKMB Limited', 'hkmb@hubinternational.com', '900-595 Bay St, Toronto, Ontario, Canada', 'www.hubinternational.com/ontario/ ', '(416) 597-0008', '(416) 597-2313', '', '<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;\">HUB International Limited is a leading North American insurance brokerage and the largest middle market commercial insurance broker in Canada. It provides a broad array of property and casualty, life and health, employee benefits, reinsurance, investment and risk management products and services. HUB International is structured around large regional &ldquo;hubs&rdquo; with satellite offices strategically located throughout Canada and the U.S. HUB International HKMB is one such &ldquo;hub&rdquo;.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;\">When it comes to risk management, risk optimization and insurance, HUB HKMB clients know they will receive expert strategic guidance and the most current information.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;\">HUB HKMB provides seamless, multi-line service extending to every major commercial centre in the world. HUB HKMB&rsquo;s experience in the international arena allows us to handle placements of all sizes quickly and efficiently.</span></p>', ''),
(1411, 1, 'HVNetworks', 'info@bpr.ca', '1200, rue Saint-Jacques Bureau 604 , MONTRÉAL, Quebec, Canada', 'www.hvninc.com ', '(514) 569-8834', '(514) 847-0012', '', '<p>&nbsp;Soliman Trading of Montreal Inc. was established in 1983 as a trading company and operates under &lsquo;HVNetworks&rsquo;.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>In 1990, the company diversified into engineering and contracting.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>The sale of High Voltage equipment continues to be one major activity. This activity expanded to cover customers across Canada. Representation agreements have been signed with major manufacturers across the globe.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our engineering activities encompass research and development in the areas of Rural Electrification and High Voltage substations.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Positive results support the execution of many feasibility studies in South America, Africa, Asia and Europe.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Contracting is conducted in cooperation with other Canadian companies, as well as the transfer of technology to our international customers.</div>', ''),
(1412, 1, 'Hy-Grade Precast Concrete Ltd.', 'dg@hygradeprecast.com', '2411 First St Louth, ST CATHARINES, Ontario, ', 'www.hygradeprecast.com ', '(905) 684-8568', '(905) 684-8560', '', '<p>&nbsp;Manufacturer of standard and custom precast concrete elements for the transportation, utility and commercial construction markets.&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1413, 1, 'Hybrid Building Logistics Inc.', 'tony.virdo@hybridbldg.com', '3611 Erindale Station Rd, MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.hybridbldg.com ', '(905) 279-7100', '(905) 279-7110', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We specialize in custom built shelters, electrical installations, and custom steel structures.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We have the knowledge and experience to provide an array of turnkey product solutions and extended service options.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our service extends beyond manufacturing shelters; our customer service options include offering solutions for power distribution, load balancing, climate control, equipment installation and integration.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our delivery options include both pre-assembled, or assembled on site, for both ground or roof-top shelters. Shelter top mounted lifting lugs provide for easy lifting to the shelter\'s final location.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1414, 1, 'HYTEK PLASTIC SALES INC.', 'levans@hytekplastics.com', '2175A TESTON RD., MAPLE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.hytekplastics.com ', '(905) 832-7977', '(905) 832-7978', '', '<p>Hytek Plastic Sales Inc. is a Manufacturer / Master Distributor of:</p>\r\n<p>Chemkor Industrial Pipe</p>\r\n<p>Chemkor Plastic Pressure Fittings</p>\r\n<p>Chemkor Plastic Valves</p>', ''),
(1415, 1, 'I-D Foods Corporation', 'info@idfoods.com', '1800 Autoroute Laval, LAVAL, Quebec, Canada', 'www.idfoods.com ', '(450) 687-2680', '(450) 682-4797', '', '<p>&nbsp;I-D FOODS operates a unique network throughout the country, including offices and warehouses in most major cities and a national trucking system. Key Account Managers, a retail sales force and layout specialists serve more than 10,000 customers all backed up by a state of the art information system.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>In 1948 Imported Delicacies (the precursor to I-D) reversed the post war movement of food parcels to Europe by importing European specialties to Canada. Philip Issenman purchased the company from Henry Gamer In 1971.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>From 1975 to 1987 Issenman then acquired the specialty food division of Rose &amp; Laflamme, the R.H. Melville Company in Vancouver and Superior Foods in Winnipeg, changing the company&rsquo;s name to I-D FOODS CORPORATION In 1977. The period between 1988 and 1990 gave birth to branches in Halifax, Ottawa and Quebec City.</div>', ''),
(1416, 1, 'I-MED Pharma Inc.', 'info@imedpharma.com', '1601 St Regis Blvd, DOLLARD-DES-ORMEAUX, Quebec, Canada', 'www.imedpharma.com ', '(514) 685-8118', '(514) 685-8998', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">I-MED Pharma Inc., a Montreal-based biotechnology company and Biocia Inc., a New Jersey-based biotechnology company announced today the Health Canada approval for their fourth generation preservative-free, multi-dose, viscoadaptive eye drop, i-drop&reg; PUR Gel for treating ocular surface disorders (OSD) such as dry eye disease (DED). This product already received a CE mark earlier this year.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Viscoadaptive eye drops are topical solutions that exhibit both cohesive and dispersive behaviours depending on the shear energy in the solution. At low shear rates the solution exhibits cohesive behaviour (enhanced viscosity for lubrication, protection and prevention of evaporation of the tear film) and at higher shear rates it may exhibit dispersive behaviour (enhanced elasticity for optimal patient comfort and longer residence time requiring fewer applications during the day and/or night).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The i-drop&reg; commercial line of products are the only current commercially available viscoadaptive solutions. The newly approved i-drop&reg; PUR Gel, 0.30% viscoadaptive hyaluronan, will be available in a simple to use, preservative-free multi-dose 10 mL bottle which dispenses sterile eye drops from the first to the last drop.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ilan Hofmann, Ph.D., President of both I-MED and Biocia commented: &ldquo;this latest approval will continue to strengthen I-MED&rsquo;s commercial footprint in the Canadian OSD market which is projected to be growing &gt;13% per year with state-of-the-art Products that are superior to others commonly marketed in Canada.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Wes Domareki, MBA, Chairman of the Board of Biocia Inc. commented: &ldquo;i-drop&reg; PUR Gel represents the culmination of years of successful research and development which is now being offered to suitable licensing partners on a worldwide basis moving forward&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1417, 1, 'i3 International Inc.', 'bob@i3international.com', '16-780 Birchmount Rd, SCARBOROUGH, Ontario, Canada', 'www.i3international.com ', '(416) 261-2266', '(888) 222-0559', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">i3\'s simple formula for success has not changed much over the years - hard work and a strong desire to provide personalized, quality service. This philosophy continues to be our driving force today. By remaining true to our core values, I have watched our company grow into a cutting-edge organization that strives to improve technology with the distinctive needs of our customer base in mind.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">As a company, we are equally committed to providing a comfortable livelihood for our employees and giving back to our community. One of our primary strengths is that, despite our rapid growth, we have managed to maintain a strong sense of family in our everyday working environment. That is, the family-centered atmosphere that characterized the business at its inception still very much defines the company today.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Clients continue to be drawn to i3 not only because of our innovative products and quality services, but also because of our rich, &quot;family-like&quot; working environment. This distinguishing trait is something that owners and employees alike work hard to maintain.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1418, 1, 'Iafrate Machine Works Ltd.', 'waltoft@iafratemachine.com', '1150 Beaverdams Rd, THOROLD, Ontario, Canada', 'www.iafratemachine.com ', '(905) 227-6141', '(905) 227-7147', '', '<p>&nbsp;With more than 35 years of solid practical experience, IMW&rsquo;s custom machine shop in Thorold, Ontario utilizes CNC turning and milling machines, grinding, induction bending, induction brazing and other manufacturing methods to turn out top quality machined parts and forgings for our automotive, oil and gas, aerospace, chemical, alternative energy, forging and machinery clients &ndash; all at competitive prices.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>CNC is a versatile system that allows you to control the motion of tools and parts through computer programs that use numeric data. CNC Turning Centres, Vertical &amp; Horizontal</div>\r\n<div>Machining Centers give the capability to perform essentially any machining operation at the highest accuracy and repeatability. With focused and sustained growth, IMW has evolved to expand our facility to its current 60,000 square feet.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>IMW should be regarded as your complete source &ndash; a full service facility that offers a total system for parts, production and tooling manufacturing. IMW strives to maintain absolute quality and reliability.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We are especially aware of the needs to respond quickly to customers&rsquo; requests for quotations and to establish appropriate delivery lead times to comply with scheduled due dates.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our vision is to exceed our customer&rsquo;s expectations in Quality, Delivery, Continuous Improvement and Customer Service.</div>', ''),
(1419, 1, 'Ian Martin Limited', 'ashworth@ianmartin.com', '203-275 Slater St, OTTAWA, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ianmartin.com ', '(613) 237-0155', '(613) 237-2070', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">At the Ian Martin Group, we believe amazing achievements are made when innovative people connect. Advances in technology and social media have opened up the world to the idea that we are all connected.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">What we do is connect the right people to the right circumstances, at the right time. We do it by understanding that all business works only because of people, and that business to business is really just a fancy way of saying person to person during business hours.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We may not be scientists, engineers, developers or inventors. But we know a lot of people who are, and we&rsquo;d like to know you. Think about it: the human possibility of people connected together around meaningful work. Our role is simply to make the links, and to find for each a place to flourish.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1420, 1, 'IBC International Bar Coding', 'info@ibcworld.net', '1940 Barnes St, PENTICTON, British Columbia, ', 'www.ibcworld.net ', '(250) 493-3201', '(250) 493-3257', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">International Bar Coding Systems &amp; Consulting Inc. (IBC) is a full service solution provider for inventory management, Point-of-Sale, SMB and enterprise computing. IBC provides the technical know-how and experience to update outdated and legacy computing up to the requirements of modern business. By providing optimal computing power per dollar, IBC helps integrate your current computing into a modern fully functioning Point-of-Sale (POS) and computing solution that provides seamless integration between head office, work-stations, POS terminals and even mobile computing and tablets. Utilizing rugged peripherals and unmatched computing customization, IBC helps optimize productivity in a cost effective reliable manner.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">With over 20 years&rsquo; of experience, IBC&rsquo;s solutions are utilized by SMB&rsquo;s, Fortune 500 companies, and government agencies all across North America. With Government contracting solutions provided to the USA and Canada; IBC&rsquo;s unique solutions are in operation 365 days of the year by Municipalities, Provincial and State Governments, and Federal Agencies.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1421, 1, 'IBEX Pharmaceuticals Inc.', 'info@ibex.ca', '100-5485 Pare St, MONT-ROYAL, Quebec, Canada ', 'www.ibex.ca/', '(514) 344-4004', '(514) 344-8827', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">IBEX markets a line of recombinant high-purity proprietary enzymes (heparinases and chondroitinases) from Flavobacterium heparinum.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">IBEX also produces a series of arthritis assays which are used by leading pharmaceutical companies for research purposes.</p>', ''),
(1422, 1, 'IC Axon Inc.', 'rallard@icaxon.com', '650-3575 Saint-Laurent Blvd, MONTRÉAL, Quebec, Canada', 'www.icaxon.com ', '(514) 274-4400', '(514) 274-4012', '', '<p>&nbsp;Working in partnership, your training and marketing departments will have access to a dedicated team of creative and instructional designers, medical illustrators, programmers, project management specialists, and one of the largest teams of in-house medical content experts in the industry.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our expertise navigating the medical, legal, regulatory, and sales environments allows us to help our clients quickly and efficiently develop healthcare training programs across a variety of therapeutic areas.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>A wide range of learning solutions</div>\r\n<div>for digital delivery, live training, or print</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Impactful sales training is our top priority. We partner with our clients to create learning programs that drive sales performance, deepen knowledge, and change behaviors.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our comprehensive blended curricula reflect a flexible approach, while strategic case-based approaches, advanced pull-through learning tactics, and comprehensive virtual preceptorship programs drive learner engagement.</div>', ''),
(1423, 1, 'IC Controls', 'sales@iccontrols.com', '29 Centennial Rd, ORANGEVILLE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.iccontrols.com ', '(519) 941-8161', '(519) 941-8164', '', '<p>&nbsp;IC Controls has been a proven and trusted manufacturer of Water Analysis Equipment for over 30 years. Specializing in pH, ORP (Oxidation Reduction Potential), Conductivity, Chlorine, ppm Dissolved Oxygen and ppb Dissolved Oxygen. Our products offer high quality, proven performance, and are manufactured to your specific application need, with the ability to select from various options.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>The rugged design and simple maintenance of our products allows for exceptional performance in tough and demanding applications. Our products are known for their reliability and accuracy which is crucial to ensuring that our customers are able to avoid risk and meet regulatory compliance through effective water quality management. We strive to meet your needs and expectations, offering flexible and on-time delivery, a knowledgeable and caring production team, and products that surpass your expectations. All products are backed by our technical experts to ensure quality, durability, trouble-free performance, and outstanding technical support.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>IC Controls is the Canadian National Distributor of &ldquo;Orion Process Products&rdquo; by Thermo Fisher Scientific since 1981. Sales, Stock, Service and Warranty all available in Canada.&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1424, 1, 'ID Fusion Software', 'info@idfusion.com', '401 Provencher Blvd, WINNIPEG, Manitoba, Canada', 'www.idfusion.com ', '(204) 237-6147', '(204) 231-4942', '', '<p>&nbsp;Our approach to software development sets us apart from most other technology companies. We don&rsquo;t just build isolated systems for individual issues. Instead, we take a look at every aspect of what our clients need, examining existing systems and learning as much as we can about their current - and even future - problems. Then we build a solution that works seamlessly within its environment and provides a great user experience.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We deliver world class solutions from a small city at the centre of North America - and we always want to do better work. We give our employees the resources they need to master their craft, and opportunities to really put that knowledge and experience to work. We want our employees to understand how their work fits into a larger picture - and these things together provide tremendous advantages to both our employees and our clients.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We are an Aboriginal / Metis company, and that identity is important to us. Giving back to our community is important to us, and over the years we&rsquo;ve contributed to - and helped to build and grow - many programs and opportunities for Aboriginal youth in Manitoba who are interested in pursuing careers in IT.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We&rsquo;re not just software developers. We understand how our work and our expertise can fit into the larger picture of how - and why - our clients run their businesses. And our solutions reflect that deep understanding by delivering well-rounded and totally customized systems that are as flexible and intuitive as our clients need them to be.</div>', ''),
(1425, 1, 'idcaps inc', 'azimuddin@idcaps.ca', '1658 Sir Monty\'s Dr, MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, Canada', '', '(416) 619-0565', '(866) 431-8248', '', '<p>&nbsp;Administrative Management and General Management Consulting Services</p>', ''),
(1426, 1, 'IDG Technologies Inc.', 'paul@idgtechnologies.com', '64 Grey Alder Ave, RICHMOND HILL, Ontario, Canada', 'www.idgtechnologies.com ', '(647) 932-3278', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;The Internet not only has changed the way in which your subscribers get their information, it has changed their attitude towards the way in which they wish to communicate with you regarding their subscriptions.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>In the age of instant communication and information overload, many publishers are finding that the response rates to traditional subscription drives and renewal efforts are declining. Readers have less time to respond to direct mail solicitations, which are in danger of being dismissed as junk mail.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>webCirc is a proven, multi-lingual capable and truly Internet-based subscription management system. It provides your subscribers with password protected real-time access to their subscription information for purposes of renewals, new subscription requests or address changes, on-line and in real-time, thereby greatly increasing customer satisfaction and your circulation staff\'s productivity.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>More importantly, it allows you the publisher, to increase response levels and reduce the ever-increasing costs associated with subscription renewal and acquisition by tens of thousands of dollars per year or more!&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1427, 1, 'IEC HOLDEN INC', 'info@iecholden.com', '8180 De La Côte-de-Liesse Rd, SAINT-LAURENT, Quebec, Canada', 'www.iecholden.com ', '(514) 735-4371', '(514) 342-3944', '', '<p>&nbsp;Manufacturers of large motors and generators and components thereof for the transportation, industrial and power generation sectors. &nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1428, 1, 'IEC International', 'clayton@ieccorporate.com', '4829 Maplegrove St, VICTORIA, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.ieccorporate.com ', '(250) 658-0179', '(250) 658-4709', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">IEC INTERNATIONAL is a privately owned Consulting-Research-Development company with offices in Victoria and Comox, British Columbia, CANADA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Since 1988 owners and staff have contributed significantly towards international developments in the environmental (R.A.R, S.P.E.A, remediation, assessment, monitoring), fisheries, and aquaculture sectors. Our expertise is wide ranging and also covers the fields of:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">environmental project and business development and management;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">technology development and utilization;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">food and seafood processing, marketing, and value added product development;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">fisheries and aquaculture facilitation, technology, policy, market development, and monitoring; and,<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">education-training.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We are very proud of our record of the successful completion of well over 620 projects in 16 countries covering over 30 species during the last 25 years. CELEBRATED 25 SUCCESSFUL YEARS IN 2013.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1429, 1, 'iFact inc.', 'info@ifact-consult.com', '436 Strathcona Rd, MONT-ROYAL, Quebec, Canadaa', 'www.ifact-consult.com ', '(514) 735-9892', '(514) 736-2773', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Fact Management has been founded in 1995 with the objective to provide international advisory and management services for clients in mainly three industry sectors: finance/banking, high tech and public sector.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">With iFact you choose a team of senior executives with numerous years of experience in high-level management positions in their respective fields with a track record spanning work in large multi-national firms as well as with small and medium-sized firms.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our core team is based in Montreal, Canada, supported by a network of partners assuring an important presence across North America and Europe. We have also started our expansion across Asia with partners in Japan and Hong Kong.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1430, 1, 'IFC (CANADA) INC', 'gcarrigan@yourwastepartners.com', '104-48 Alliance Blvd, BARRIE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ifccanada.ca ', '(705) 797-8355', '(705) 797-8356', '', '<div>In 1981, the IFC Group became the first company in Canada to rent &amp; lease waste compactors &amp; balers direct to end-users. Over the years, we have acquired the largest compactor rental portfolio in the country. Today, we specialize in offering unique finance, sales &amp; operational support programs that assists our many marketing Partners to effectively distribute their lines of waste handling equipment. &nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1431, 1, 'Igeco International Inc.', 'igeco@igeco-international.com', '2500-1155 Rene-Levesque Blvd W, MONTREAL, Quebec, Canada', 'www.igeco-international.com ', '(514) 448-2600', '(514) 819-9848', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&#8203;Headquartered in Montreal, Canada, Igeco International Inc. provides, in collaboration with its network of partners, business development and consulting services in the following fields:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Consulting: Through its consulting division, Igeco International Inc. offers a variety of services to small and medium size Canadian enterprises, among which identifying business opportunities, marketing, matching trade partners, international expansion, sourcing and distribution logistics, implementing eCommerce solutions, and selection of integrated IT/communication solutions. The company also offers sourcing services for some foreign partners. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">International Trade and Investments: Igeco International Inc.&rsquo;s international trade and investments division works with select partners in importing/exporting physical goods and services. We have representation agreements with Canadian firms as their exporters, and also have agency and distribution agreements, representing some leading foreign companies in Canada for their goods and services. The company also has some investments in other enterprises.&#8203;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Software Implementation and Training: Igeco International Inc. offers Software implementation, localization, and customization services for some vertical applications, including corporate services software solutions and selected CRM systems. The company also develops and adapts training programs to meet the requirements of its clients.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1432, 1, 'Igloo Building Supplies Group', 'frank.marocco@igloo.ca', '21421, 111 Ave NW, EDMONTON, Alberta, Canada', 'www.igloo.ca ', '(780) 451-0600', '(780) 455-6356', '', '<p>&nbsp;Igloo Building Supplies Group Ltd. prides our self on our quality expertise and service. We provide premium building supply streams to our loyal customers. We offer Traditional Stick Built - for those builders that want to put their own elbow grease into the project, Panel Systems - have your home designed and built in wall panel sections and delivered to your site. If you require assistance we can refer you to a team of expert framers with experience installing our wall panels. We are constantly striving to achieve a high level of customer satisfaction by offering a variety of services to help you build your dream home, using the latest technology, offering a team of trained experts, and great customer service to follow through. Igloo Building Supplies Group Ltd. has been in the business of helping home builders achieve their dream for over 60 years. We are a Builders Best Resource.</p>', ''),
(1433, 1, 'IHI Planning Ltd.', 'info@ihi.ca', '1096 10th Ave W, VANCOUVER, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.ihi.ca ', '(604) 733-5400', '(604) 734-8300', '', '<p>&nbsp;IHI International has the exclusive rights to a revolutionary customized modular technology (except for Canada) that is bringing the power of the computer to the construction industry. IHI is ready to begin marketing, manufacturing and constructing hi-rise and low-rise residential and commercial insulated steel and concrete structures for the countries worldwide where patents were issued. The IHI System proves that buildings can be affordable, safe and durable without compromising quality.</p>', ''),
(1434, 1, 'IHS', 'ehs-sustainability@ihs.com', '401-155 Gordone, NORTH YORK, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ihs.com/ehs-sustainability ', '(800) 289-6116', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;IHS equips you with the expertise, software and content to effectively manage environmental, health and safety (EHS) and sustainability performance. The largest companies in the world publicly report business sustainability, from water consumption and supply-chain stability to greenhouse gas emissions and safety performance. Though this data doesn&rsquo;t apply directly to finances, it can give shareholders leading indicators of mid- to long-term financial performance. With our EHS solutions, you gain a disciplined approach to managing this information and can learn proven best-in-class processes to drive greater operational efficiencies.</p>', ''),
(1435, 1, 'IIE Solutions', 'service@iiesolutions.com', '851 Colonia Dr., LADYSMITH, British Columbia, Canada ', 'www.iiesolutions.com ', '(250) 245-0110', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our focus since our creation in 1996 is to master and stay at the fore-front of the rapidly-evolving Internet technologies to help you define and build your Internet, Intranet and Extranet website solutions.Website Design, Content Development, ASP.NET Applications, DotNetNuke CMS, Ecommerce, Blogs &amp; Wordpress, Social Community Websites, and more...<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Search Engine Marketing (SEM), Pay Per Click Marketing (PPC), HD Web Video Campaigns, Viral Marketing (Facebook, Twitter, YouTube,etc..), Logo Development, Skins &amp; Template Design, and Cascading Style Sheets (CSS) which are developed for continuity for both web and print production.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HD Video Productions for Internet specializing in promotional videos &amp; commercials, educational &amp; training videos and event videography, Video Promotions, Video SEO, Google Search, YouTube Promotions, Video Blogs - Vblog, Viral Video Marketing Campaigns. Services also include videography &amp; filming and a range of post-production services such as video editing, motion graphics, DVD authoring, and CD &amp; DVD duplication.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Domain Name Registration, Website Hosting including ASP.NET, DOTNETNUKE (Professional CMS), PHP, WORDPRESS (Personal CMS), Shared &amp; Dedicated Servers, SSL Certificates, IceWarp Email Hosting, 24/7 Support.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1436, 1, 'IIS International Internet Systems Inc.', 'naoko@iis-int.com', '604-1255 Main St, VANCOUVER, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.iis-int.com ', '(604) 602-1455', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;IIS is an association of talented professionals dedicated to connecting suppliers and buyers around the world.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We specialize in helping companies and corporations bridge the tremendous cultural, linguistic and regulatory gaps in today\'s global marketplace.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Introduce your brand to new international consumers</div>\r\n<div>Find eager new buyers to build your bottom line</div>\r\n<div>Extend your network into global markets</div>\r\n<div>When you don\'t speak the language, or understand the local customs or regulatory framework, commercial success is almost impossible.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>With international language and trading solutions, global marketing and multi-media services, we can help.</div>', ''),
