(1439, 1, 'ILPS', 'ilps@msn.com', '10304C, 120th St, SURREY, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.ilps.com', '(604) 588-0880', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">International Loss Prevention Systems (ILPS) is an innovator in the Loss Prevention industry. From our early days as a manufacturer and designer of Electronic Article Surveillance systems to where we are now, a full service retail and commercial Loss Prevention solutions provider ILPS remains on the forefront of technology in order to assist our clients with their Loss Prevention needs. Working within the niche market of Retail and Commercial Loss Prevention allows ILPS to focus our attention and efforts into constantly finding solutions that are both innovative yet affordable for any business.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Discover how ILPS saves every type of business (from the smallest to the largest) millions of dollars in losses due to shoplifting, employee theft, vendor theft, fraud, liability, and other criminal acts.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1440, 1, 'Iluma International Ltd.', 'diana@ilumaint.com', '15 - 14215 - 82 St NW, EDMONTON, Alberta, Canada', 'www.ilumaint.com ', '(780) 702-6805', '(888) 761-8328', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thank you for visiting our website. Diana created this website to help promote wealth building through real estate. This is accomplished by providing complete realtor services, educational seminars, networking events, personal mentoring and much more.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">For many people buying their own home is the most important and biggest single investment they&rsquo;ll make &ndash; it&rsquo;s also one of the easiest to understand in regards to return on investment. Not only can you experience the pride which comes from home ownership as a tangible asset, but you can also measure the return on investment as the price of your home increases in relation to other investment vehicles.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">In a market where many consider stocks and shares complex and risky and many who are experiencing dwindling pension expectations, perhaps it is unsurprising to see an emerging trend in investing in real estate. However, there are some mine-fields to negotiate when considering buying property especially when transacted from distance. That&rsquo;s where Iluma International can help.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Diana brings an impressive array of experience and training in financial management, business building and real estate investments. Adding to her industrial finance degree earned in her native China and the graduate program in Finance from McGill University in Montreal, Ms. Chu became a Licensed Real Estate agent in 2009. As an agent of Home &amp; Gardens Real Estate of Edmonton she has been able to successfully council clients from across Canada as well as the United States and Mainland China.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Whether you are considering making your first home purchase, starting an investment strategy or are a veteran investor, you will find our friendly professional services help you realize success in real estate. Iluma International can call on a team of highly experienced Edmonton Real Estate professionals who can guide you through the intricacies of your real estate purchase.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1441, 1, 'IM Consulting', 'michael@imconsulting.ca', '300 Widgeon Way, GLOUCESTER, Ontario, Canada', 'www.imconsulting.ca ', '(613) 715-1130', '(613) 822-1864', '', '<p>&nbsp;IM Consulting is an Integrator Product Suites offered to Canadian Federal Government through the NMSO&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>IM Consulting has the expertise to implement a researched solution that will meet the unique requirements of our customer\'s policies and procedures. We will insure adherence to SLAs for security, retention, longevity, authenticity, accessibility and recoverability in disaster. IM Consulting will provide the greenest innovative products and online services that will serve datacenters for government departments and agencies for years to come.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>IM Consulting provides InContinuum Cloud Services an innovative provider of cloud computing software that controls and automates your virtualized managed services and associated SLAs.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>IM Consulting is composed of dedicated Green IT Storage and Networking Professionals with the depth and knowledge to be a tremendous asset to meet tomorrow&rsquo;s business challenges. The world&rsquo;s ecological issues, impact our decisions to look forward as opposed to looking in the rear view mirror&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our green consultants are among some of the finest and have adopted the need for change as tomorrow will not look like yesterday. Traditional data storage paths will not be sustainable as we moved from the industrial age to the information age. IM Consulting provides green innovative strategies to address the future which is now.&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1442, 1, 'Image Gear Inc.', 'service@imagegearinc.com', '103-358 Dufferin St, TORONTO, Ontario, Canada', 'www.imagegearinc.com ', '(416) 923-7432', '(416) 923-1874', '', '<p>&nbsp;With over thirty years experience importing equipment into Canada for film and video production, as well as collaborating in the design and manufacture of some very specialized tools, Image Gear Inc. continues to provide sales, service and rental support to a wide variety of videographers and filmmakers across the country.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Recently specializing in on-camera accessories such as Matte Boxes, Filters, Follow Focus, Zoom Controls, Optical Adapters, Wireless Control and Monitoring, the company continues to source new products and adapt conventional gear for use with the latest digital technologies.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Relationships with clients and suppliers. The strength of Image Gear over the years has always been the relationships with clients and suppliers. As new technologies expand the horizons of todays storytellers and equipment evolves to meet those needs, Image Gear hopes to be a conduit in both directions, with experiences that will be beneficial to all.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Right Place, Right Time, Right Price. Our focus is on the production equipment needs of our clients. Whether it\'s a special piece of equipment or a common tool used everyday we endeavour to get it in the right place at the right time for the right price.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Your Purchasing Department. We can serve as your purchasing department, working with you on an annual basis to schedule equipment acquisitions. By planning ahead, combining purchases with others and using economical shipping methods, the cost of production equipment can be significantly reduced.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We Get the Gear. Of course, the nature of the motion picture and television industry dictates that very often there is little time to get the gear. It is this reality that Image Gear has tremendous experience in dealing with. We look forward to working with you.</div>', ''),
(1443, 1, 'Inbox Advertising Inc.', 'info@inbox-advertising.com', '133 Waterloo Ave, NORTH YORK, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.inbox-advertising.com ', '(416) 636-5638', '(416) 636-1550', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">At Inbox Advertising, it\'s all about Email Marketing Services. We assist Agencies, Marketers and Internet Publishers, by performing all of the complex tasks associated with email campaign set up, deployment, tracking, reporting and list &amp; data management. In a nutshell, you have a list or database of permission-based recipients and an email marketing message that you need to send...we will take care of the rest.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We enable you to effectively communicate with your audience, assess your messages\' performance, reduce your marketing costs and hone your marketing strategies, all without the expense of hiring any IT staff or purchasing and managing software or hardware.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Since 2001, we have been developing a host of unique and sophisticated software solutions, which we use in performing our services. At Inbox, we are very client centric in how we operate, especially when it comes to our commitment to expanding our range of services. We are dedicated to providing new and useful tools and technologies ahead of our industry (usually a couple of years), which gives our clients a definite edge.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">If we do not offer a service that you need, tell us and we\'ll see what we can do about building it...for free. We only charge you for using it. It is this type of customized development and sheer dedication to our clients\' requirements, which separates Inbox Advertising from all other email vendors.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our core strengths revolve around our stellar service, superior technology (\'ahead of the leading edge\') and affordable pricing. We work for you as your outsourced Email Technology Specialists, ensuring that each email marketing program is professionally managed and executed.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1444, 1, 'Incom Manufacturing Group Ltd.', 'distributor@incomdirect.com', '1259 Sandhill Dr., ANCASTER, Ontario, Canada', 'www.incomdirect.com   ', '(905) 648-6811', '(905) 648-7188', '', '<p>&nbsp;INCOM manufactures specialty adhesive tape and identification signage products for the safety and compliance markets.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We provide a wide array of stock and custom products including anti-slip tape, aisle marking tape, floor demarcation, reflective tape, barricade tape, abatement tape, pipe identification, safety signs and tags.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our products are available globally through a wide array of stocking distributors. Most orders ship next day from our locations in the US and Canada.</div>', ''),
(1445, 1, 'IO Industries Inc', 'info2@ioindustries.com', '12-1510 Woodcock St, LONDON, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ioindustries.com ', '(519) 663-9570', '(519) 663-9571', '', '<p>&nbsp;IO Industries Inc., London, ON, Canada (est. 1991), designs and manufactures digital video cameras and digital video recorders for applications in machine vision, testing, medical, scientific, broadcast and cinema.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our Flare&trade; family of video cameras are useful for high-resolution inspection and high-speed capture. These cameras use advanced CMOS sensors with global shuttering and high dynamic range.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our DVR Express&reg; Core family of digital video recorders provide SSD-direct, uncompressed recording for most popular video interfaces.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our world-wide sales and distribution network consists of experienced professionals, expert in all aspects of video technology, who will work closely with a customer to develop a vision system that targets the needs of the customer. The highest quality technical support is guaranteed.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>IO Industries is committed to developing innovative vision hardware and software products for the most demanding computer vision applications. &nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1446, 1, 'Ionbond Inc.', 'jason.turchin@ionbond.com', '10-1315 Industrial Rd, CAMBRIDGE, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ionbond.com', '(519) 653-0610', '(519) 653-2634', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ionbond provides highest performance PVD, CVD and PACVD wear protection, low friction and decorative coatings as well as coating equipment. With 38 service centers in 17 countries in Europe, North America and Asia Ionbond has one of the largest networks in the world. The company has been involved in this market for over 40 years and offers the broadest set of coating technologies in the industry. Our expertise goes far beyond our industry-leading CVD coating services and equipment with extensive coating portfolios based on PVD and PACVD technologies as well. Ionbond is operationally headquartered in Olten, Switzerland and has over 900 employees worldwide.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our focus at Ionbond is to provide both high quality standard coating portfolios for the cutting, molding and forming tool market and to offer customized solutions for our customers making OEM components. Ionbond is eager to take on difficult and specialized coating applications and to put in the time and energy required to meet such custom coating requirements. We work with our customers in very close cooperation to ensure the coatings meet all the critical requirements. In doing so Ionbond gains a deep understanding into the very specific requirements of several demanding markets such as aerospace, medical, automotive components, and high-end decorative. In such applications it is imperative to have the highest level of quality control throughout the coating process. To this end we put a large emphasis on product quality and invest significant resources towards quality certifications such as ISO 9001, ISO 13485, TS 16949 and AS 9100.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Flexibility, innovation, and integrity are at the heart of our business at Ionbond. Our qualified coating specialists around the world are ready to help with your coating requirements today.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1447, 1, 'IPAC', 'ntl@ipac.ca', '401-1075 Bay St, TORONTO, Ontario, Canada', 'www.ipac.ca ', '(416) 924-8787', '(416) 924-4992', '', '<p>The Institute of Public Administration of Canada (IPAC), founded in 1947, is a dynamic association of public servants, academics, and others interested in public administration. Anchored by our regional groups, we&rsquo;re a membership-based organization that creates knowledge networks and leads public administration research in Canada. Since the early 1990s, IPAC has been a major player in exporting successful Canadian public sector expertise around the world.</p>', ''),
(1448, 1, 'Ipac Chemicals Ltd.', 'info@ipachem.net', '1620 75th Ave W, VANCOUVER, British Columbia, Canada', 'www.ipachem.net ', '(604) 261-3019', '(604) 261-1655', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Founded in 1987, IPAC provides customized, engineered solutions for water treatment, dust control, wastewater, industrial cleaning and sanitation. We offer a number of proprietary water treatment formulations to prevent corrosion, scale, deposit and biological fouling in steam boilers, chillers, open recirculating cooling water systems, and other industrial process equipment. Ultimately, the goal is to enhance the efficiency of your process while extending the lifespan of your equipment. Other products include specialty chemicals to improve air quality and environmental safety, industrial cleaners and degreasers for transportation and food processing plants, and flocculants and coagulants for wastewater, all ISO 9001:2008 and 14001:2004 certified.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Since 1976 Power Chemicals has provided custom-engineered chemical solutions and technical service for the pulp and paper, mining, coal, primary metals, bulk terminals and solid wood industries. The focus of our team of scientists and engineers is to provide technically innovative economical solutions for our customers in process improvements and efficiencies, as well as environmental and occupational health and safety improvements. Our proprietary knowledge and technology in dust suppressants, scale inhibitors, fireside additives, combustion catalysts, anti-freeze agents, hydrogen sulphide scavengers, pulping enzymes, and liquid and dry polymers provide us with the means to help our customers.&nbsp; All our products are ISO 9001:2008 and 14001:2004 certified<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We\'re proud members of the Building Owners and Managers Association, and have helped many of our customers with BOMA Canada\'s \'Go Green\' certification. Our company has a proactive Health and Safety program and Emergency Response Plan in place, not just for our own benefit, but for our clients\' use as well.<o:p></o:p></p>', '');
