(1628, 1, 'VSK Machining', 'info@vskmachining.com', '3480 McNicoll Ave Unit 3-4, SCARBOROUGH, Ontario, Canada ', 'vskmachining.com ', '(416) 335-5997', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;We&rsquo;re committed to providing you with the highest level of service, so you&rsquo;ll always choose us for your Design and Manufacturing&#8203; needs.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our Mission&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>At VSK Machining we thrive to provide leadership in the Manufacturing world by delivering outstanding value, continuous innovation and excellence in customer satisfaction. We believe in achieving our goal by embracing the simple concept of pay less and expect more.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>VSK Machining has long committed to being the best in design and manufacturing in North America. Based in Toronto, Ontario and servicing both Canada and the United States, we have provided parts, prototypes, assemblies and sub-assemblies for the military, automotive, aerospace, food, energy and mining sectors since 1999. We have been profoundly driven by customer satisfaction providing manufacturing needs from small and large components and from custom pieces to mass quantity orders.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;Copyright &copy; VSK Machining&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Starting as a small business with screw machines we have grown to gain the capability to place care towards a product from the design and planning, through manufacturing to the final work.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We have top CAD designers that are able to work closely with you and your team to create what your imagination dictates. Using our CAD drawing, we can move forward with our testing and prototyping phase prepping for manufacturing.</div>\r\n<div>We have t</div>\r\n<div>Our large network of suppliers has given us the advantage of providing our customers with extended services, such as:</div>\r\n<div>- Heat treating - Grinding - Welding - Anodizing - Powder coating&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1629, 1, 'VTL TRANSPORT', 'douimet@vtltransport.com', '208-1221 32 Ave TATIO, LACHINE, Quebec, Canada ', 'www.vtltransport.com ', '(514) 631-6669', '(514) 631-2694', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">With over a decade of experience in the transportation industry, VTL Group has developed a solid position and reputation around the world. We offer transportation and distribution services from continent to continent with dedicated personnel, quality and comprehensive services, modern facilities and state of the art rolling stock.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">VTL offers more than just &ldquo;transportation from A to B&rdquo;. In fact, our comprehensive services include the following divisions:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">VTL V-TRANS: Logistic Services<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">VTL TRANSPORT: Transportation Services<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">NAUTICA: International Freight and Forwarding<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">VTL appreciates and respects the trust of our customers. We attribute our reputation and success to the professionalism and availability of our qualified staff. Our commitment is to provide the best quality service possible in the transportation industry. In today&rsquo;s competitive market, we strive to deliver nothing but the best: exactly what our customers expect and deserve.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">VTL is very proud in its achievements over the past decade. You, our customers, have contributed largely to our success and we will always consider it a privilege to offer you our full array of services.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1630, 1, 'VTR Inc', 'sales@bowlfeeders.com', '4-745 South Service Rd, STONEY CREEK, Ontario, Canada', 'www.bowlfeeders.com ', '(905) 643-7300', '(905) 643-7708', '', '<p>&nbsp;VTR Inc. (Vibratory Tooling &amp; Repair Inc.) is an industry-leader in automated parts feeding systems. VTR Inc. is a supplier of Storage Hopper Units or Bulk Storage Devices, Vibratory Inline Feeder Units, Vibratory Bowl Feeder Units, Various Types of Escapement Devices (Blow Feeds, Cross Shuttles, Pick and Places), Rotary (Centrifugal) Feeder Bowls &amp; the recently established Step Feeder product line.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>VTR Inc. offers all these components as individual acquisitions or they can be procured as an option on a fully automated system. VTR Inc. is truly your &ldquo;one-stop&rdquo; shopping destination for all your parts feeding needs. With attentive Project Management staff and 3D Solidworks Design in-house, VTR Inc. is truly unmatched in capabilities by any competitor.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Take some time to view our website and look over some past projects that are running efficiently in a wide array of industries today. We offer many forms of information and multi-media content that can only begin to introduce you, to what we do and how well we do it, every time.</div>', ''),
(1631, 1, 'Vue-Craft Products Ltd.', 'pkg@vuecraft.com', '15 Colville Rd., NORTH YORK, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.vuecraft.com ', '(416) 789-7163', '(416) 781-0487', '', '<p>&nbsp;Vue-Craft has been in the transparent PVC packaging business for over 50 years. We specialize in producing plastic PVC packaging, custom fitted to any type of product, in addition to carrying a full line of packaging, in a wide assortment of shapes and sizes. Clearly, our perspective has always been and still is to offer our customers quality packaging, quickly and economically.</p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Because we manufacture what we sell, our inventory is deep and wide. Because you buy directly from our factory, you save. Place an order and we can ship it to you anywhere - immediately.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>And if we don\'t have in-stock items just right for your merchandise, we\'ll custom make even small runs to your specifications!</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Selection, service, satisfaction - that\'s what we\'ve built our business on.</div>', ''),
(1632, 1, 'Vulcan Electric', 'kathy@chargers.ca', '205B Konrad Cres., MARKHAM, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.chargers.ca ', '(905) 513-1550', '(905) 513-1557', '', '<p>&nbsp;Whether you&rsquo;re on this site researching Standby Chargers for navigation or institutional use, Motive/Industrial Chargers for fork lifts, scissor lifts, golf carts or floor sweepers or Automotive/Battery Shop Chargers you can count on one thing. The performance and reliability of all Vulcan chargers is an historical certainty.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>Since 1896, Vulcan Electric Inc. has been synonymous with reliable battery charging power systems. Back then, we made batteries that supplied the energy for many of the electric-car prototypes that were prevalent at the time. By 1926, we were manufacturing battery chargers and we have been ever since.</div>\r\n<div>Without question, Canadian made Vulcan battery chargers are the hardest working and most reliable on the market. We use heavy-duty copper wire in our transformers instead of aluminium because it provides superior heat transfer, conductivity and reliability. To further enhance longevity, our stud type diodes are heavier and our steel is thicker. Check the History section for amazing true stories about the indestructibility of Vulcan chargers.</div>', ''),
(1633, 1, 'VWR International', 'canada_callcenter@vwr.com', '8567 Dalton Rd, MONT-ROYAL, Quebec, Canada ', 'www.vwrcanlab.com ', '(514) 344-3525', '(514) 344-0133', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">VWR International, LLC, is a global laboratory supply and distribution company.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">VWR Collection: Delivering the highest standards of quality, performance, and service, the VWR Collection represents the right products, at the right price, when you need them &ndash; with the name you trust...<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Clearance Sale: Take advantage of drastically reduced pricing on hundreds of products...<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Current Promotions: Looking for special offers, promotions, or samples from VWR? Don\'t miss your chance to take advantage of these great offers today!<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1634, 1, 'W Communication', 'info@wcommunication.com', '150-210 Lee St, QUEBEC, Quebec, Canada', 'www.wcommunication.com ', '(418) 622-9266', '(418) 622-9213', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The intelligent promotional Article<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">With us, ideas prevail, not objects! We create with a strategic and conceptual mind so as to generate a deep commitment toward your brand. We offer eye-catching concepts, supported by unique and unmatched reproduction processes, and we select, with a keen sense of aesthetics, products consistent with your goals. That&rsquo;s creative intelligence!!!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">W Communication makes you shine with intelligence and creativity<o:p></o:p></p>', '');
