(1702, 1, 'YaGotta.ca', 'yagottabob@gmail.com', '5014 55 Ave, CAMROSE, Alberta, Canada', 'www.yagotta.ca ', '(780) 240-2501', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Just search our list of the most popular destinations Ya\'Gotta go to in western Canada, to find adventure, culture and history. Before planning adventure travel in Western Canada, visit the Ya\'Gotta Western Canadian Adventure Travel Guide!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Keep up-to-date with Ya\'Gotta &amp; visit our main Ya\'Gotta Edmonton Network Blog. The Blogroll will point you to our other blogs for Calgary, Vancouver, Central Alberta and Canadian Rocky Mountains. Now we\'ve added a companion Ya\'Gotta Travel Blog and you can follow us on Twitter @yagottabob and our Facebook page.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ya\'Gotta has information for young and middle-aged adults, with Ya\'Gotta feature articles that will provide you travel planning information about the adventure tourism destinations you know about! Ya\'Gotta has pages about the Canadian Rocky Mountain destinations of (Banff, Lake Louise and, Jasper). If you\'re planning to visit the Canadian north, we also have articles about Dawson City, Whitehorse and Yellowknife. Teachers, kids and and teens will also find Ya\'Gotta useful, for finding out about the Canadian outdoors!<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ya\'Gotta specializes in those fantastic out-of-the-way destinations to visit in British Columbia, Alberta, Saskatchewan and Manitoba. Ya\'Gotta can also help you find the right adventure travel destination in Cananda\'s north in the Yukon, Northwest Territories and Nunavut.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Because with adventure travel Ya\'Gotta start somewhere and we have feature articles about the western Canadian tourism gateway cities of Edmonton, Calgary, Regina, Vancouver, Victoria and Winnipeg.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ya\'Gotta can also help you find out about things to see, in western Canada. Every summer, our most popular pages are our listings of aboriginal powwows and folk music festivals will help you to find the best festivals to attend. If live folk music is what you\'re looking for, we\'ll help you find great performers to see and venues to go to, with our roots (eg. folk, country, bluegrass) music pages.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ya\'Gotta also has a collection of articles about things to do in western Canada as well as topical environmental issues. If you plan to trek, in the outdoors, your health is very important...Visit our Ya\'Gotta Be Healthy page to buy organic, gluten free &amp; environmentally friendly products.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">If you operate an adventure travel business we can help you to sell your outdoors products and services and if you operate a destination marketing organization, adventure travel business, travel club, related event, let Ya\'Gotta Communications &amp; Marketing Get Your Message &quot;out&quot;!<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1703, 1, 'YCS Inc.', 'jkincler@ycs.net', '5568 King Edward Ave, CÔTE SAINT-LUC, Quebec, Canada', '', '(514) 737-5434', '(514) 737-5495', '', '<p>&nbsp;The Yamatech group was established in 1982 with the founding of Yamatech Scientific Inc. which is now the holding company for the Yamatech group of companies and divisions. Our core business in the 80\'s and 90\'s was computer networking and data communications. Presently we put together international consortia for international projects in the fileds of technology, telecommunication infrastructures, sustainable development and construction. We act as project initiators and managers and offer project management services globally.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>Financial assistance in developing countries is possible, depending on circumstances. &nbsp;</div>', ''),
(1704, 1, 'Yeadon Fabric Structures Ltd.', 'info@yeadondomes.com', '201-128 Woolwich St, GUELPH, Ontario, Canada', 'www.yeadondomes.com ', '(519) 821-9301', '(519) 821-9010', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">With over 25 years experience, YeadonTM is the industry leading producer of state-of-the-art air structures.&nbsp; We provide the most cost effective fabric structure domes for sports and recreation, warehousing, military and construction usage.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our custom designed air supported domes are easy to maintain.&nbsp; Every YeadonTM air dome incorporates the latest innovations in design, anchoring, mechanical and electrical systems to provide the ultimate in efficiency, safety and comfort for your air structure.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Our commitment to service doesn\'t stop after installation.&nbsp; Every YeadonTM air supported dome is backed by Yeadon&rsquo;sTM outstanding technical support for the life of the structure.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1705, 1, 'Yellow Bird Paper Greetings Inc', 'info@yellowbirdgreetings.com', '2930 Lonsdale Ave, NORTH VANCOUVER, British Columbia, Canada ', 'www.yellowbirdgreetings.com ', '(604) 980-8215', '(604) 980-8217', '', '<div>At Yellow Bird Paper Greetings, a chi-chi concoction of girlish glamour, vintage imagery and witty sayings, culminate in a stationery collection that is high on style and serious sass.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Inspired by her children, world travels, and her own childhood, Charmaine Carlson uses both past and present experiences as her muse. Reaching into the past, she unearths nostalgic images, color palettes, typefaces and styles, which she then magically reinterprets in refreshingly modern ways.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>With an inclination toward the creative arts, Charmaine earned a degree in Fashion Design and Marketing, and spent 10 plus years working in the business before the corporate culture began to have her yearning for freer pastures.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>An infatuation with paper led to the creation of Yellow Bird Paper Greetings in 2002. Originally supplying a handful of North American retailers with handmade, hand-embellished greeting cards, that were celebrated for their combination of sass and sophistication, the demand for these chi-chi concoctions was exceptional. Not one to stand on her laurels, Charmaine channeled her creative talents and in 2004 launched an all new printed collection which consisted of 16 greeting cards. This launch ultimately led to the Yellow Bird Paper Greetings global recognition and the collection, as it stands today, of 1000 plus items.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Yellow Bird Paper Greetings hasn\'t flown too far from its\' beginnings. All of our products continue to be manufactured in North America. Using only the highest quality papers. We believe it\'s best to manufacture high-quality greeting cards and stationery products that benefit our friends, neighbors and the earth. In short, we strive to offer great products, great designs and great price points, all while still being mindful of the environment. Nestled in the foot hills of North Vancouver, British Columbia Yellow Bird Paper Greetings is still headed by its founder Charmaine Carlson. Anyone visiting the office should be prepared to be greeted with licks and wags from Charmaine\'s yellow lab Ruby who is a permanent fixture in the office and never let\'s Charmaine get too far from her gaze.</div>', ''),
(1706, 1, 'Yfactor Inc.', 'info@yfactor.com', '1100-151 Yonge St, TORONTO, Ontario, Canada', 'www.yfactor.com ', '(416) 977-9724', '(416) 642-1959', '', '<p>&nbsp;Why do we do what we do? At Yfactor our core purpose is to strengthen the social fabric of societies by helping communities grow.</p>\r\n<div>How do we do this? Yfactor is Canada\'s leading specialist in marketing for communities with a focus on strategy, technology and design.</div>\r\n<div>Where do we do this? Our client base is concentrated in Ontario and extends to both the west and east coast of Canada as well as south to many communities in the United States.</div>\r\n<div>Yfactor is a thought-leader in marketing and technology solutions for the economic development and tourism sectors. We also support the non-profit and for-profit sectors.</div>\r\n<div>The Yfactor &quot;Y&quot; represents the intersection of strategy, design and technology, which defines the work that we do. We use this 3-pronged approach to create innovative and practical marketing and technology solutions that deliver real results to our clients.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Yfactor was formed in 1997 with a forward thinking vision of helping customers achieve their business objectives by combining technology with strategy and creativity. Yfactor has used this vision to become a North American thought-leader, respected for our marketing and technology solutions.</div>\r\n<div>We have worked with more than 200 clients across 13 states and provinces. With over 4000 projects completed, we have developed a proven methodology for delivering integrated solutions to our clients. That being said, each project is unique, and we continue to get excited about every new opportunity!</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1707, 1, 'YG Enterprise Ltd.', 'ygerber@rogers.com', '38 Moraine Ridge Dr., RICHMOND HILL, Ontario, Canada', '', '(416) 998-6070', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;Computer software and hardware consulting. Database design and data modeling. Database development. Datawarehousing.</p>', ''),
(1708, 1, 'YHC Cassette Industrial Ltd.', 'info@yhcdirect.com', '16 Wyndemere Crt, MARKHAM, Ontario, Canada ', 'www.yhcdirect.com ', '(416) 817-6603', '(905) 201-7399', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We are CD and DVD Duplicator and Custom T-Shirt Printing Company in Markham, Ontario, Canada.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We provide CD duplication, DVD duplication with direct full color CD/ DVD logo printing and packaging services.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We also provide custom T-Shirt Printing with no minimum quantity. We can put your custom logo/design onto the T-shirt/ Apparel/ Uniform/ other clothing of your choice.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We also offer a complete line of blank media, CDR, DVDR, VHS video cassette tape, 3.5&quot; 2HD floppy diskette, business card CDs, and mini CDs/DVDs, CD case, DVD case, video tape library case, calendar case, speaker, mouse phone, CD label, envelope, sleeve, pouch and accessories.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Any size of order are welcome. We will make sure that we will provide every client the best products and the best services with the best price. Please contact us for more information.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1709, 1, 'YieldPoint', 'andrew@yieldpoint.com', '170-1407 John Counter Blvd, KINGSTON,, Ontario, Canada', 'www.yieldpoint.com ', '(613) 531-4722', '(888) 282-5784', '', '<p>&nbsp;YieldPoint, its owner Dr. Andrew Hyett, its employees and contractors would like to thank all the clients and contacts that have contributed to making this a very interesting and the most successful year so far for the company. We now count more friends and contacts than ever and we were honoured to count new clients in Australia, South Africa, Tanzania, Mali, Sweden, Spain, Peru, Mexico and of course the US and at home here in Canada. We also received renewed attention from most of our existing customers and shipped products to many of them. Our digital instrumentation has reached maturity and our d_EXTO multipoint borehole extensometer has become the best solution on the market, as indicated by numerous users and by fast growing sales volume and orders sizes. Our data logging offering now offers extended battery life and integrated RF and Ethernet solutions including Power Over Ethernet for simplistic deployment configurations. Our fibre optics solutions have generated very interesting data and have received attention from a worldwide community of experts.</p>\r\n<div>We look forward to continued growth for us and all in the mining and civil industries and to many projects that will contribute to improving safety in the mines.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We wish you a happy holiday season and all the best for 2015!</div>', ''),
