(1757, 1, 'Yezitronix Group Automation & Ctrl. Ind. Inc', 'info@yezitronix.com', '6333 Saint-Francois Rd, SAINT-LAURENT, Quebec, Canada', 'www.yezitronix.com ', '(514) 856-0101', '(514) 620-3606', '', '<p>&nbsp;YEZITRONIX Group Inc. (YGI) is internationally recognized by ultrasound system builder giants worldwide as a state of the art provider of medical phantoms technology.</p>\r\n<div>YEZITRONIX Group Inc. has elevated the competition few steps further by developing an advanced Multi-Component Tissue Mimicking Phantom construct.</div>\r\n<div>The material of the new Phantom technology not only generates correct 3D morphology for human tissues and mimics ultrasound imaging properties, &nbsp;but also generates the tissue&rsquo;s mechanical properties for needle piercing applications.</div>', ''),
