(2045, 266, 'GlenKebl Inc.', 'tamara.kebuladze@glenkebl.com', NULL, 'www.glenkebl.com', '+14168993061', '', 'We are committed to help Canadian SME sector to reach their short and long term goals associated with International trade and Marketing.   \r\nWe offer a range of global business solutions to help SMEs succeed in international markets including, new product and business development, market research, feasibility studies, market analysis and selection, market entry strategy, international lead generation and partner search, brand development, overseas marketing and promotion, public relations, product launch and trade show support services.', 'If you are looking for answers on the following questions: \r\n•	What are characteristic of you target market? \r\n•	How competitors approach the market?\r\n•	What is the best promotional strategy to use on given market?\r\n•	How should one adopt brand book, existing, marketing materials, or even product or service?\r\n\r\n•	How complex are international transactions- What means of payment/ financial interaction is widely used in target market?\r\n•	Will it be better to use local business representative or directly enter the market?\r\n•	What documents will be needed to fulfill clients exporting needs\r\n•	What is like local Taxation system? How it affects export pricing?\r\n•	Who can be our client’s local partner?\r\n•	What are external risks and how to avoid them?\r\nWe are here to advise, coach and outsource your activities.', 'export; international marketing; market research; partner search; business development; investment opportunities'),
(2046, 267, 'Canada Essay Writing', 'molly.abram@outlook.com', NULL, 'http://canadaessaywriting.com/', '647-256-6723', '', 'Canada Essay Writing provides highly professional writing service for students in the Canada. ', 'Canada Essay Writing offers top notch academic papers on all subject to students studying in different universities. Our writers who have a specialization in the subject field can work on any citation formats (APA, MLA, Chicago, etc.) and include every source they use on the Works cited page. We assure 100% Plagiarism-free content and on time report delivery before the deadline. Our service offered include, writing essays, assignments, research papers, coursework, dissertation, term paper and journals.', 'Buy essays, custom essays, write my essay, do my homework, term paper help, dissertation writing, course work, research paper help, book review, '),
