(26, 1, 'Larsen & Shaw Limited', 'sales@larsenhinge.com', 'P.O. Box 1420, WALKERTON, Ontario, , ', 'www.larsenhinge.com', '+1 (519) 881-1320', '+1 (519) 881-3593', '', '<p>A leading North American manufacturer of top quality custom and standard continuous/piano hinges, architectural hinges, butt/strap/tee/lift off/stop/spring hinges, and metal stampings (brackets/braces) used in enclosure/cabinet/tool box, appliance, vehicle hardware, industrial/agricultural/transportation equipment, furniture and architectural hardware industries. We are The Hinge People&reg;, ISO Quality Management certified, following LEAN manufacturing principles, enabling us to focus on our customers&rsquo; requirements to be responsive with short lead times, on time delivery , high quality and competitive pricing. Our products are available in steel, stainless, aluminum, galvanized and brass materials, in a variety of finishes, using our in-house plating and tooling capabilities. Larsen &amp; Shaw, a family owned business since 1919, has grown to a leadership position by combining technology with a skilled and dedicated work force.</p>', ''),
(27, 1, 'Chemie Impex Trading', 'chempex@rogers.com', '56 Gold Hill Rd, BRAMPTON, ON, , ', 'www.sanghviforge.com', '+1 (647) 436-2182', '+1 (905) 497-0450', '', '<p>We are an import &amp; export organization. At present we are marketing following products in and out of Canada, US and India 1. SS Flanges 2. SS forging and large dia Tube Sheets/Flanges up to 60&quot; and Rings 3. SS ferrules and Sanitary Fittings 4. SS Bright Bars and Rods-Round, Hex and Threaded 5. SS Wires 6.Pneumatics Valves-Manifolds, Needle and Bleed Valves We represent SANGHVI FORGING &amp; ENGINEERING LTD, Vadodara-India. They manufacture and supply quality SS Forging and SS flanges since 1996. Along with flanges we can supply SS ferrules, Sanitary Fittings and Precise CNC Machined Components   Mohamed Mehta-President</p>', ''),
(28, 1, 'Wilshire Works Inc.', 'info@wilshireworks.com', '17 Wilshier Blvd., BRACEBRIDGE, Ontario, , ', 'www.wilshireworks.com', '+1 (705) 706-0227 ', '+1 (705) 646-2922', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\">Wilshire Works Inc. - Who Are We? Wilshire Works Inc. is a Canadian-based healthcare product manufacturing company that provides infection control solutions benefiting hospitals and long term care facilities worldwide. We develop products based on workplace needs shared by frontline healthcare staff and create commercially viable solutions using CAD design, modeling and prototyping techniques. As a business we can compete worldwide through the utilization of state-of-the-art automatic PLC controlled manufacturing equipment. Wilshire Works Inc. takes great pride in our quality products and attention to customer service. Our product development team is always up for new design challenges with commercial potential. Please contact us if you have a good idea that we can help you commercialize. Wilshire Works welcomes good ideas from frontline healthcare staff and offers royalty based remuneration.</p>', ''),
