(39, 1, 'Catalina Enterprises Ltd.', 'info@catalinaltd.com', '1935-11th Ave., VERNON, British Columbia, , ', 'www.catalinaltd.com ', '+1 (250) 558-3909', '+1 (250) 558-3914 ', '', '<p>A manufacturer of private label bath and body personal care  products, operating out of a 40,000 sq foot plant. With a solid  foundation of proprietary formulas, we are prepared to  manufacture and/or tailor formulas to create complete product  lines or individual products to compliment any existing lines.  Also available to do product filling.</p>', ''),
(40, 1, 'Ontario Drive & Gear Limited', 'sales@odg.com', '220 Bergey Crt., NEW HAMBURG, Ontario, , ', 'www.argoatv.com', '+1 (519) 662-2840', '+1 (519) 662-2421', '', '<p>Ontario Drive &amp; Gear Limited is the manufacturer of the ARGO, an amphibious, multi-purpose, all terrain vehicle. Using the ARGO\'s design, our facility also manufactures platforms for various  robotic vehicles (ie. minesweepers). ODG introduced the Centaur  in January 2000 to address the industrial/commercial market.  ODG\'s GEAR DIVISION specializes in custom design of flexible  shaft couplings and industrial gearboxes for manufacture in our  fully equipped machine shop.</p>', ''),
(41, 1, 'Cormer Group Industries Inc.', 'acorner@cormeraerospace.com', '33 Bentall St, WINNIPEG, Manitoba, , ', 'www.cormeraerospace.com', '+1 (204) 987-6400 ', '+1 (204) 987-6419', '', '<p>CNC custom production machining facility. High-precision machining utilizing machining centres and lathes for the  manufacture of Airframe and Aircraft Structural Components and  for the manufacture of components for Defence Industries. In  house LPI / Anodize / Paint for Major Aerospace Assemblies.  AS9100 and NADCAP Approved</p>', ''),
(42, 1, 'Omni Graphics Ltd.', 'omnimail@omnigraph.com', '2-12760 Bathgate Way, RICHMOND, British Columbia, , ', 'www.omnigraph.com', '+1 (604) 276-9717 ', '+1 (604) 276-2514 ', '', '<p>Omni Graphics Ltd. is one of Canada\'s premier quick turn and prototyping circuit board facilities. Since incorporating in 1985, Omni has consistently lead the local market in new developments and services. Printed Circuit Board manufacturers typically were offering completion of orders within a 4 to 6 week time frame. Omni Graphics made a commitment to offer much quicker and more flexible delivery schedules. This service has brought about a partnership with the industry that it has relied upon to rapidly develop today\'s newest technologies.</p>', ''),
(43, 1, 'Atelier Landry', 'atelierlandry@nb.aibn.com', '2515, route 205, Saint -FranÃ§ois-De-Madawaska - NB, , ', 'www.atelierlandry.com', '+1 (506) 992-2272 ', '+1 (506) 992-3808 ', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">With 30 years of experience we distinguish ourselves by the quality of our hardwood products. We manufacture moldings and we do mass production of custom pieces. Brief, we specialize in many different areas and are always open to new ideas. In 2007, we\'ve added new line of products, which includes rolling pins, cutting boards, bread boxes and a variety of other items. Our priority is to offer our clients high quality products at competitive prices.</p>', ''),
(44, 1, 'Microhard Systems Inc.', 'info@microhardcorp.com', '17 - 2135 - 32nd Ave NE, CALGARY, Alberta, , ', 'www.microhardcorp.com', '+1 (403) 248-0028', '+1 (403) 248-2762', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">About Microhard Systems Inc.   Microhard Systems Inc. specializes in the design and manufacture of long range robust wireless data equipment. Our continuous innovation and unparalleled product performance has earned us a trusted name in the wireless industry. Microhard provides OEM level products, packaged products, and ready to install systems for wireless Data and Voice for industrial, and military, and government clients. We serve a variety of customers ranging from radio integrators to multibillion-dollar defense contractors.</p>', ''),
(45, 1, 'Steam Sauna', 'sales@steam-sauna.com ', '13-153 Bridgeland Ave., NORTH YORK, Ontario, , ', 'www.steam-sauna.com ', '+1 (416) 787-1711', '+1 (416) 785-9388 ', '', '<p>Welcome to the World of Wellness and Relaxation Steam Sauna has been providing top quality steam generators for virtually every commercial and residential application for over 30 years. Steam Sauna&rsquo;s leading design, development and product lifestyle improvement programs have resulted in the most complete line of steam bath products for your club or home. For those seeking the finest dry sauna experience, we offer our unique Serena series cedar log sauna rooms. Custom pre-cut kits from 2 x 4 western cedar planks, our saunas are quick and easy to assemble requiring no nails or glue. Because of their thickness, no insulation or vapor barrier is needed. If you are considering a commercial or residential steam unit or a cedar log dry sauna, we invite you to check out our products on this web site. Each Steam Sauna product is manufactured, assembled and tested to exacting specifications, ensuring the highest quality, efficiency and ease of use.</p>', ''),
(47, 1, 'Action Forms Inc.', 'bob@actionforms.ca', 'P.O. Box 760,, St George Brant - , Ontario, Canada, ', 'www.actionforms.ca', '+1 (519) 448-4377 ', '+1 (519) 448-4375', '', '<p>Manufacture computer forms . Transportation forms and supplies, Business forms, Sell shipping supplies and office supplies</p>', ''),
(48, 1, 'Nett Technologies Inc.', 'sales@nett.ca', 'P.O. Box: 27143,, Toronto â€“ Ontario,, , ', 'www.nett.ca', '+1 (905) 672-5453', '+1 (905) 672-5949', '', '<p>Nett Technologies is an environmental company specializing in exhaust pollution control products for internal combustion engines. We manufacture catalytic converters, catalytic mufflers, diesel filters, and other emission controls for diesel, LPG, natural gas and gasoline engines. Our major markets are materials handling, construction, underground mining, urban buses, trucks, and stationary applications. Specialized lines of products are available for OEM and aftermarket applications.</p>', ''),
(49, 1, 'Pure Canadian Products Inc.', 'jameskim@cdnproducts.com', '1701-555 Austin Ave, COQUITLAM, British Columbia, , ', 'www.cdnproducts.com', '+1 (604) 771-0324', '+1 (604) 771-0324 ', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\">Pure Canadian Products Inc. specializes in serving the global market with high quality health food supplements and all-natural health products. We are fully committed to: Providing the purest Canadian health products. Our goal is to use 100% Canadian ingredients and develop products in a controlled Canadian manufacturing process. When buying from us, you will be satisfied with the quality of our products processed and manufactured in Canada. Any products not produced in Canada will be stated on our packaging. Sharing our products with our community. The message we want to share with all our customers is, &ldquo;Be well with Pure Canadian Products.&rdquo; To provide affordable health solutions for our customers, our products are offered at competitive prices. For seniors and people with physical disabilities, we have developed a special discount policy.</p>', ''),
(50, 1, 'Scintrex Limited', 'scintrex@scintrexltd.com', '222 Snidercroft Rd., CONCORD, Ontario, , ', 'www.scintrexltd.com', '+1 (905) 669-2280', '+1 (905) 669-0648 ', '', '<p>Scintrex Limited of Concord, Ontario, Canada, is a developer and manufacturer of scientific instruments for earth science and environmental markets. Our instruments allow for precise measurements of geophysical data for exploration and monitoring in petroleum, mineral, ground water and academic applications . In addition, Scintrex provides airborne and ground based geophysical exploration services for the mining and petroleum industries. The origins of Scintrex Limited date back to the year 1946 when the company, then known as Sharpe Instruments Ltd., first manufactured a number of fine mechanical and opto-mechanical measuring devices. By the mid-1950\'s, the product line had expanded to include electronic and electromechanical devices, primarily for use in mineral exploration as well as a quartz-element gravimeter.</p>', ''),
