(53, 1, 'Design & Integration Inc.', 'sales@designintegration.com', '132 Jardin Drive, Vaughn, Ontario, , ', 'www.designintegration.com', '+1 (905) 669-8497', '+1 (905) 669-3607 ', '', '<p>\r\n\n<meta content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" />\r\n\n<meta content=\"PowerPoint.Slide\" name=\"ProgId\" />\r\n\n<meta content=\"Microsoft PowerPoint 12\" name=\"Generator\" />\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black; font-style: italic;\">For the past 17 years, Design &amp; Integration Inc. has been producing highly specialized machinery equipment supporting various field of the industry such as the steel warehousing handling, the photographic and printing industries, glass laminator machines and handling systems, custom conveyance of all kind, presses and lifting devices and many exotic machinery of all kinds. Our company provides the services form conceptual idea to a final turnkey client site installation. </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\"> </span></p>\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black; font-style: italic;\">Our company posses a strong engineering and manufacturing expertise in many specialized fields of endeavor to satisfy our client needs. We have a proven track record of successful project in design and full process integration.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\"> </span></p>\r\n\n</p>', ''),
(397, 1, 'Crown Construction Equipment ', 'info@crownequip.com', 'P.O. Box 234, Station â€œLâ€, WINNIPEG, Manitoba, , ', 'www.crownequip.com', '+1 (204) 885-5800', '+1 (204) 885-7557', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Crown Construction Equipment manufactures a full line of contractor size Mortar and Concrete Mixers, Concrete Screeds, and Buggies and Mobile Glycol Heaters designed for ground thawing and concrete curing applications.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We started with a simple philosophy; Build quality products at a competitive price and good things will happen. They have! Crown has grown by leaps and bounds by introducing new product lines, providing superior customer support and always working to improve our existing products.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We would like to thank all of our loyal customers for their support. We hope that you find your visit to our site informative and enjoyable. We are always open to your comments and suggestions so please send us your feedback. Thank you for visiting our website.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(422, 1, 'Applied Physics Specialties, L-3 Wescam', 'aps@apphysic.com', '17 Prince Andrew Place, NORTH YORK - Ontario, , ', 'www.wescam.com', '+1 (416) 445-1870 ', '+1 (416) 445-7977 ', '', '<p>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\r\n<meta name=\"ProgId\" content=\"PowerPoint.Slide\">\r\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Microsoft PowerPoint 12\">  </meta>\r\n</meta>\r\n</meta>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">APS is a fully integrated optical shop. We have mechanical design, mechanical fabrication, optical fabrication, optical coating and assembly facilities. Our main product is multiple field of view lenses for the IR and visible we also manufacture glass aspheric </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">lense</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\"> using high quality generators and computer controlled polishing machines.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">Wescam</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\"> will change the </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">way you see the world by capturing visual information from moving platforms and by transmitting images and data in real time to strategic command centres for interpretation, and to production facilities for live broadcast.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">A world leader in the provision of visual information systems, </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">Wescam</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\"> delivers exceptional value in precision optics, </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">gyrostabilization</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">, digital and analog transmission and reception, and custom-fitted system integration. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">Wescam&rsquo;s</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\"> visual information systems are used by the most discriminating customers around the world including armed forces; federal and local law enforcement agencies; broadcasters of news, entertainment and sports; and NASA. Using our systems, these customers are able to capture, process, transmit and interpret integrated images and data.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(423, 1, 'Captec Americas Inc. ', 'sales@captecamericas.com', '675 Queen Str. S., KITCHENER - Ontario, , ', 'www.captecamericas.com', '+1 (519) 576-3336', '+1 (519) 576-3992', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Your Technology Partner<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;Manufacturer of industrial computers and providers of custom industrial computing solutions for difficult environments<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Leading-edge products, solid engineering expertise and a comprehensive operational and logistical support - that\'s what our customers expect when they choose a Captec industrial PC. Our customers trust in the skill and experience of Captec\'s team of engineers and technicians to deliver the most appropriate solution for their applications - on time, cost-efficient, and meeting the highest quality requirements.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>We meet your every requirement</strong><o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(1923, 1, 'ABCO Group', 'mikea@abcogroup.ca', '1280 Eglinton Ave E, MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, Canada', 'www.abcogroup.ca ', '(905) 629-2291', '(905) 629-2432', '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Since 1987, The ABCO  Group has provided office furniture and moving solutions to thousands of  Ontario businesses. With locations in Toronto, Mississauga, Concord,  Pickering, Barrie and Kitchener, The ABCO Group offers over 160,000  square feet of new and pre-owned office furniture deals. The ABCO Group  can also assist your business in many related areas, such as corporate  relocation and moving services, refurbishing of existing furniture and  servicing and repairing of almost all brands of office furniture. We  also offer the benefits of a custom furniture division, a full service  repainting shop and we can help re-design your space with computer  assisted drawings.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">In 2009, The ABCO Group  acquired Addmore Office Furniture to become Ontario&rsquo;s largest  independent office furniture retailer. With a strong focus on the  ability to display quality new and pre-owned office furniture in a  relaxed and inviting atmosphere, The ABCO Group has become a preferred  supplier for most of Ontario&rsquo;s leading companies. The ABCO Group  understands that the competitive nature of business in today&rsquo;s economic  climate can create challenges for companies of all sizes. Through  strategic alliances with our suppliers, The ABCO Group offers a wide  range of new office furniture at very competitive prices, as well as  re-markets the region&rsquo;s largest selection of quality, pre-owned office  furniture that allows companies to save money on one of the most  important requirements for successful businesses.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether your business  needs to grow or move, The ABCO Group offers the services to assist in  any transition. With a dedicated team of Consultants and the personnel  and equipment to execute, we are truly &ldquo;big enough to manage and small  enough to care!&rdquo; Drop into any of The ABCO Group&rsquo;s six locations today  and see what&rsquo;s in store for you.</p>', ''),
