, , ', 'www.fpitx.com', '+1 (902) 752-0989', '+1 (902) 755-3262', '', '<p>Manufacture heavy open die forgings. Formerly known as TrentonWorks Forge. Manufacture shafts, rings, discs, cylinders and blocks in carbon and alloy grades. Forgings up to 45,000 kg are made on the largest open die forging press in Canada. Quality system registered to ISO 9001:2000  Nova Forge Corp. manufactures open die forgings for a broad range of industries. Products include: shafts, rings, discs, ylinders,blocks and blind cylinders. The plant has complete capabilities for heat treatment and machine shop work.  Nova Forge Corp. produces hydroelectric and generator shafts, heat exchanger tubesheets, pressure vessel components, eccentric shafts, pulp and paper shafts, cement mill shafts, gas compressor barrels, electric motor shafts, oil field pressure control components, cylinders for hydraulic presses, fanshafts and ship shafting.  Nova Forge specializes in custom forgings. Our products are  shipped around the world from the ice-free port of Halifax,  Nova Scotia.</p>', ''),
