(289, 1, 'CorActive High Tech Inc.', 'michel.careau@coractive.com ', '121-2700 Jean-Perrin St, QUÃ‰BEC, Quebec, , ', 'www.coractive.com', '+1 (418) 845-2466 ', '+1 (418) 845-2609', '', '<p>\r\n\n<meta content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" />\r\n\n<meta content=\"PowerPoint.Slide\" name=\"ProgId\" />\r\n\n<meta content=\"Microsoft PowerPoint 12\" name=\"Generator\" />\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">The only constant in today&rsquo;s business world is change. Globalization is creating ferocious competition in every market. This new reality is forcing companies to resort to new creative solutions. How can your company innovate? What can you do to beat the competition? How can you come out on top? Who can help you&nbsp;&nbsp; bring&nbsp; your concepts to the next level?</span></p>\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">If your company designs and manufactures optical systems, we believe </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">CorActive</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\"> is the partner who can help you reach your goals.</span></p>\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">CorActive</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\"> manufactures Specialty Optical Fibers for applications in the telecommunications, remote sensing, strategic defence, security, industrial machining and medical industries.</span></p>\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">CorActive</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\"> produces a wide range of specialty products, including rare-earth-doped, double-clad , Mid-IR, UV sensitive, fiber bundles and attenuating Fibers. </span></p>\r\n\n<span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black; font-weight: bold;\">CorActive</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\"> has the know-how and expertise to produce customized fibers for any application. We devote a team of specialists to your project, and once the fiber has been developed, our state-of-the-art automation systems go into full-scale production mode just for you. </span></p>', ''),
