(59, 1, 'AGI EnviroTank', 'info@envirotank.com', 'P.O. Box 879, BIGGAR, Saskatchewan, , ', 'www.envirotank.com', '+1 (306) 948-5262 ', '+1 (306) 948-5263 ', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A.G.I. is a leading manufacturer of steel storage tank  We design and build  environmentally safe tanks for use in every major industry-oil and gas, mining, transportation, construction, waste management, bulk and retail storage and service, and more.  A.G.I. is committed to giving our customers affordable solutions to all their containment needs. If there is a better way to design a tank or delivery system to fit your requirements... we will find it.    Custom Manufacturing A.G.I. manufactures a complete range of tank sizes and designs. In partnership with experienced petroleum contractors we are able to, supply all the necessary components, including pumps, dispensers, bollards, spill containers, and electrical accessories. Our product are built to API, G55, ULC or UL standards. And because every industry-and every customer-has their own needs, A.G.I. customizes our product to suit your application.</p>', ''),
(60, 1, 'CL Activewear', 'sales@clactivewear.com', '8529 Lafrenaie St, SAINT-LÃ‰ONARD, Quebec, , ', 'www.CLactivewear.com', '+1 (514) 374-6566 ', '+1 (514) 374-6510', '', '<p>CL Activewear is a private company, established in 1989 to design and manufacture clothing for three specific markets; the sports team market, the promotional apparel market (a corporate clientele) and the private label market. From its head office in Montreal, the firm can easily increase its production capacity to meet additional market requirements by setting up new production lines. Its hallmarks are creativity, the quality of its clothing and its high capacity to adapt to each customer&rsquo;s needs and requirements. Another asset is the company&rsquo;s ability to consistently deliver its product within a very short time frame (a few weeks).   The company specializes in a new technology, dye sublimation, which involves printing a customer&rsquo;s colors, logos and patterns directly into a cloth&rsquo;s fibre. Although clothing styles vary according to each customer, the firm&rsquo;s specialty is jackets (summer-winter), jerseys (tods-men-women), pants, shorts, leotards, swimsuits and other specialty garments</p>', ''),
(61, 1, 'Libart Enclosure Systems Ltd ', 'sales10@libart.com ', '110-7391 Vantage Way, DELTA, British Columbia, , ', 'www.libart.com  ', '+1 (604) 952-5150', '+1 (604) 648-9919', '', '<p>LIBART ENCLOSURE SYSTEMS is an innovative design, manufacturing and marketing company that provides architectural solutions to residential and commercial building owners looking for unique swimming pool and patio structures. Libart has North American and European customers through its distribution network.  LIBART brings you modern, aesthetic designs that allow natural light in while sheltering you from the weather and harmful UV rays. Our European designs have been in use in residential and commercial buildings from Northern Europe to the Mediterranean for the past 16 years. Libart has a widespread network of national and international distributors that assures satisfaction to its many customers.   Libart delivers and assembles:  Unique designs for specific needs and projects;  Competitive and innovative solutions;  A wide range of complementing products;  New systems and designs utilizing the latest materials and technologies.</p>', ''),
(62, 1, 'Corporation Scientifique Claisse Inc. ', 'info@claisse.com ', 'Parc Technologique, 350, rue Franquet, Suite 45, QUÃ‰BEC, QuÃ©bec, , ', 'www.claisse.com  ', '+1 (418) 656-6453', '+1 (418) 656-1169', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\">World leader and the first in its field in the development of analytical fusion techniques, instrumentation and fine chemistry science, Corporation Scientifique Claisse (or Claisse) is world-renowned for its outstanding achievements in the development of inorganic sample preparation by fusion for XRF, AA, ICP and wet chemistry analysis. As the leader, Claisse has opened new technical and economic frontiers for ceramic, cement, steel, aluminum, glass, oil, polymers, mining and other industries. Taking these questions and more into consideration, the Claisse team works with you to find the best solutions for all of your expectations and needs. How to prepare your samples? How to get the best analytical results ever? Which fusion instrument best suits your needs? What flux is the most convenient for your applications? Claisse...&quot;The First and Finest in Fusion&quot;</p>', ''),
(63, 1, 'H.D. Brown Enterprises Ltd. ', 'info@hdbrown.com ', 'P.O. Box 190, ST GEORGE BRANT, Ontario, , ', 'www.hdbrown.com  ', '+1 (519) 448-1381', '+1 (519) 448-3159', '', '<p>Hugh Douglas Brown owned a furniture manufacturing company that made, among other things, oak bars for automobile roof racks. When the contract was almost cancelled, Hugh turned the potential loss into an opportunity.   It was when the national retailer who sold the racks couldn&rsquo;t find a supplier to make the cotton straps usedto fasten the racks to car roofs that Hugh realized with the right set-up it would be easy to make the straps.   The customer would be serviced, the contract would be saved, and the product - the only one of its kind at the time - would continue to reach the market.   In 1971 H.D. Brown Enterprises Ltd. began operations as a small cut and sew business with two staff working out of a factory in St. George, Ontario. Over the years the furniture business was sold and H.D. Brown began importing products on a subcontractor basis.</p>', ''),
(64, 1, 'Finecast Limited ', 'info@finecast.ca ', '208 Migneron St, SAINT-LAURENT, QuÃ©bec, , ', 'www.finecast.ca  ', '+1 (514) 331-0322', '+1 (514) 331-0261', '', '<p>FINECAST Limited provides custom manufacturing of small to medium size high precision dies, tools, fixtures and gauges and has  extensive expertise in specialized machining of small, highly  complex components of various alloys, such as Kovar,Titanium,  Inconel, Invar, Aluminum and materials such as Ceramics,Graphite  and Plastics.  FINECAST has been supplying the semiconductor, aerospace, military, medical and telecommunication industries with high quality products since 1974. During these years FINECAST has earned the  reputation as a Quality Supplier in the industry and has been  recognized as such by many multinational companies for  outstanding performance in quality, service and reliability.  Certification : ISO 9001:2000 Certificate No. 412/97 SGS Canada Inc.</p>', ''),
(65, 1, 'Hodgson Custom Rolling Inc. ', 'hodgson@hodgsoncustomrolling.com ', '5580 Kalar Rd, NIAGARA FALLS, Ontario, , ', 'www.hodgsoncustomrolling.com ', '+1 (905) 356-8132', '+1 (905) 356-6025', '', '<p>Hodgson Custom Rolling Inc. provides the manufacturing expertise, and equipment to process our customer\'s heavy steel plate  further. We roll, flatten, bend, and form our customer\'s material to whatever their specifications and/or product might be.  Hodgson specializes in customized rolling of heavy wall large  and small diameter pipe; forming and flattening of steel plate for primary steel industry; pressbrake steel plate from 1/4&quot;  to 14&quot; thick; rolling to 7&quot; thick plate. Products include: rings, gear blanks, heavy weldments, ladles furnaces, pressure vessel components, platework, angle rolling rolling of steel tubing, steel pipes of varied dimensions and  thicknesses, flanges support ribs, spiral stair stringers,  formed trunion pads cones, cylinders, drums, steel shells, steel casings etc.</p>', ''),
(66, 1, 'Leading Edge Automation Inc. ', 'office@leadingedgeautomation.com ', '8-160 Matheson Blvd E, MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, , ', 'www.leadingedgeautomation.com ', '+1 (905) 712-9451', '+1 (905) 712-9460', '', '<p>Leading Edge Automation is a drives control and industrial automation company that provides state-of-the-art products and services to a wide range of industries and demanding applications. We are also a major authorized distributor for the versatile Parker SSD Drives product line.  In addition to our strong engineering and product offerings, we are able to provide complete turnkey solutions to our customers. Machinery rebuilds, equipment relocation, and electrical contracting services are provided by our sister company Captec Electric Ltd.  As a result of many years of successfully working with various OEM&rsquo;s, our engineering and service staff have gained significant experience in a wide variety of industrial applications. Let us put this experience to work for you so that you can see for yourself why Leading Edge Automation is consistently invited back to provide our customers with quality products and services.</p>', ''),
