(105, 1, 'CVDS Inc. ', 'sales@cvds.com ', '117 Brunswick Blvd., POINTE-CLAIRE, Quebec, , ', 'www.cvds.com  ', '+1 (514) 426-7879', '+1 (514) 426-3511', '', '<p>CVDS Inc. is a design-oriented company specializing in the development and manufacture of a wide range of electronic products, such as digital voice recorders, telecommunication equipment, automated merchandising and transaction systems, surveillance equipment, high-reliability switching power supplies, and custom air traffic control applications.   Founded in 1972, CVDS had its start on the design of an automatic message accounting system and rail yard communication systems for CP Rail (formerly CNCP Canadian National Canadian Pacific). CVDS created a reputation for designing dependable products using the latest technologies. We have the expertise and versatility to respond to diverse product requirements for any application, and are constantly involved in a variety of research and development projects.</p>', ''),
(106, 1, 'Madentec Limited ', 'sales@madentec.com ', '4664, 99th St NW, EDMONTON, Alberta, , ', 'www.madentec.com ', '+1 (780) 450-8926', '+1 (780) 988-6182', '', '<p>Madentec Limited is a leading supplier of assistive technology for people with physical disabilities. Products include solutions for accessing and controlling a computer or communication device 100% hands-free by using Tracker products as well as an alternate keyboard or scanning access through the Discover product line. These products are ideally suited to people with severe physical disabilities, including: quadriplegia, cerebral palsy, multiple sclerosis, ALS and muscular dystrophy.</p>', ''),
(107, 1, 'ReflectoSphere Division ', 'peterrowe@execulink.com ', 'Unit 2 - 135 St. David Street South, Fergus â€“ Ontario, , ', 'www.reflectosphere.com  ', '+1 (519) 843-2138', '+1 (519) 843-2712', '', '<p>The ReflectoSphere Division of our firm specializes in the development, manufacture and sale of a wide range of Retro-Reflective Products, which include Coatings, Printing Inks, Tape and Sheeting.  Our advanced line of finished product formulations is based upon the use of Highest Optical Quality Hemispherically-Aluminized High Index Glass Microspheres, which we also market under the name ReflectoSpheres.     ReflectoSphere is committed to providing a safer nighttime environment through increased visibility after dark and under conditions of low light .  A unique line of Reflective Finished Products brings to the end user, highly-durable, cost-effective applications which provide equal reflectivity from any combined light source and viewing angle.</p>', ''),
(108, 1, 'NaturoSources', 'naturosources@yahoo.ca ', '2447, rue des CyprÃ¨s, SHERBROOKE, Quebec, , ', 'www.naturosources.com', '+1 (819) 820-9773 ', '+1 (819) 820-9773', '', '<p>Naturosources is a Canadian business specialized in the production and the comercialisation of 100% natural aromatic ingredients. Our line of products includ: - Aromatic and medicinal plants  - High quality Essential oils 100% pure and natural obtained by steam distillation. Our Essential oils and botanicaly and biochemically well defined. (Checked by our laboratory partner)  - 100% natural floral water ( hydrolats): Lavender, Oregano, Rosemary, Orange flower, Rose damasca, Thym,... - 100 % natural and pur Carrier Oils cold pressed (Argane oil, Apricot oil, cactus oil...) - 100% natural Moroccan lava clay (Ghassoul) for spa and beauty institution.  The production sites are located in morocco where the raw materials are collected and processed in place. In Canada NaturoSources activities cover distribution and comercialisation in North America as well as the manufacture of high quality natural products under the brand name NaturoSources intend for the sectors of the aromatherapie</p>', ''),
(109, 1, 'Anivac Corporation ', 'inquiries@anivaccorp.com', '8-484 Plains Road E, BURLINGTON - Ontario, , ', 'www.anivacfirst.com', '+1 (905) 690-4416 ', '+1 (905) 690-6042 ', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Welcome to Anivac - animal bathing systems Clean your animal twice as well in half the time! Clean your animal the easy, portable, mess-free way without using volumes of water - up to 90% water savings!  Anivac\'s patented nozzles deep clean from the skin up, removing dirt and hair, leaving a clean glossy coat.  Anivac&rsquo;s Vacuum Bathing Systems are an entirely new way of looking at the issue of dirt on an animal, and how to get that dirt out! Anivac systems actually clean from the skin up instead of the top down, are virtually mess free, can be used in winter with only common sense precautions, and the groom stays dry! Using your Anivac will enable you to get ALL the dirt out and will drastically cut your grooming chore.  Anivac is ideal for: Horse owners  Dog owners  Commercial stables  Commerical kennels  Veterinarians  Cattle owners</p>', '');
