(128, 1, 'TITAN CONTRACT WELDING LTD. ', 'titanwelding@xplornet.com', 'P.O. Box 19, WARDLOW, Alberta, , ', 'www.titantough.ca', '+1 (403) 566-2432', '+1 (403) 566-2433', '', '<p>Manufacturers of TITAN TOUGH products and TITAN TOUGH services. An aggresively growing steel manufacturing company producing farm and ranch gates, panels, feeders and other livestock equipment. We also manufacture products for the oil and gas industry such as wellhead fencing (tex fence) and cattle guards with swing gates. We have now expanded to manufacture picnic tables, park benches, bike racks and other site amenities. Available for rent is our TITAN TOUGH security fence. We also have a mobile welding unit and a shop for welding services and custom fabrication. Tube bending services are also available.</p>', ''),
