(132, 1, 'Envyrozone', 'rob@envyrozone.com', '25 Claireville Dr., ETOBICOKE, Ontario, , ', 'www.envyrozone.com', '+1-416-674-8800', '+1-416-674-4600', '', '<p>OUR STORY: Founded by the creators of the most successful public space recycling program in the world, Envyrozone takes a unique approach to clean space. Reinventing a line of products which  place an unmatched degree of emphasis on function and aesthetic appeal alike.   We proved through market research, design and state-of-the-art manufacturing capabilities,  that refuse and recycling containers can be attractive, functional and user friendly. Where we live, work and play are important to us all. Designing and building indoor,  outdoor furniture that makes your living, working and entertainment experiences Clever, Clean and Unique.</p>', ''),
