(190, 1, 'Chemie Impex Trading', 'chempex@rogers.com', '56 Gold Hill Rd, BRAMPTON, ON, , ', 'www.sanghviforge.com', '+1 (647) 436-2182', '+1 (905) 497-0450', '', '<p>We are an import &amp; export organization. At present we are marketing following products in and out of Canada, US and India 1. SS Flanges 2. SS forging and large dia Tube Sheets/Flanges up to 60&quot; and Rings 3. SS ferrules and Sanitary Fittings 4. SS Bright Bars and Rods-Round, Hex and Threaded 5. SS Wires 6.Pneumatics Valves-Manifolds, Needle and Bleed Valves We represent SANGHVI FORGING &amp; ENGINEERING LTD, Vadodara-India. They manufacture and supply quality SS Forging and SS flanges since 1996. Along with flanges we can supply SS ferrules, Sanitary Fittings and Precise CNC Machined Components   Mohamed Mehta-President</p>', ''),
