(195, 1, 'CL Activewear', 'sales@clactivewear.com', '8529 Lafrenaie St, SAINT-LÃ‰ONARD, Quebec, , ', 'www.CLactivewear.com', '+1 (514) 374-6566 ', '+1 (514) 374-6510', '', '<p>CL Activewear is a private company, established in 1989 to design and manufacture clothing for three specific markets; the sports team market, the promotional apparel market (a corporate clientele) and the private label market. From its head office in Montreal, the firm can easily increase its production capacity to meet additional market requirements by setting up new production lines. Its hallmarks are creativity, the quality of its clothing and its high capacity to adapt to each customer&rsquo;s needs and requirements. Another asset is the company&rsquo;s ability to consistently deliver its product within a very short time frame (a few weeks).   The company specializes in a new technology, dye sublimation, which involves printing a customer&rsquo;s colors, logos and patterns directly into a cloth&rsquo;s fibre. Although clothing styles vary according to each customer, the firm&rsquo;s specialty is jackets (summer-winter), jerseys (tods-men-women), pants, shorts, leotards, swimsuits and other specialty garments</p>', ''),
