(213, 1, 'Dylis Innovative Systems Inc.', 'dylis@dylis.com', '1401 Meyerside Dr, MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, , ', 'www.dylis.com', '+1 (905) 564-6436 ', '+1 (905) 564-7840', '', '<p>Dylis Innovative Systems has been a designer and manufacturer of intelligent automation based solutions for more than ten years. Our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction is reflected in all we do from simple workstations to turnkey assembly lines. All of our equipment is built utilizing standard components in a custom engineered solution. Dylis Innovative Systems started out in the field of flexible automation providing robotic tooling and fixturing solutions to local manufacturers. As our company grew, the depth of our staff\'s expertise expended and we began to develop specialpurpose assembly and material handling equipment for applications not suited to robotics. Today we offer a blend of flexible automation and custom engineered solutions to manufacturers through out North America.</p>', ''),
