(257, 1, 'PaddleOne', 'marioblackburn@paddleone.com', '27 Champoux, Sorel-Tracy , Quebec, , ', 'www.paddleone.com', '+1 (450) 494-3799', '+1 (450) 494-3799', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\">PaddleOne products are specifically designed for canoe and kayak workouts. It simulates the perfect strokes performed while paddling Outrigger, Dragon Boat, Marathon Canoe and Kayak. It is an excellent cardiovascular training apparatus. As you begin your stroke on your PaddleOne , it automatically replicates the sport-specific movement and water resistance. Just like being in your boat. Being away from your crewmates before the weekend&rsquo;s race gets you nervous? With PaddleOne, you can perform your workout in the comfort of your home and feel the same sensation and benefit as an outdoor training. Whether you are a top paddler or an amateur, PaddleOne will certainly fill your needs. Mario Blackburn, president, marioblackburn@paddleone.comThis e-mail address is being protected from spam bots, you need JavaScript enabled to view it Call anytime at 450 494-3799</p>', ''),
(258, 1, 'Distribution Laurent Leblanc (DLL) Inc.', 'dll@dllinc.com', '600-E Blvd Industrial, Saint-Jean-sur-Richelieu, Quebec, , ', 'www.dllinc.com', '+1-450-346-7044', '+1-450-346-0643', '', '<p>We have the pleasure to introduce DLL Inc as a North American  industrial leader in the manufacturing and repairing of high  tech products.  In October 1995, DLL Inc was created by is actual president  Laurent Leblanc in Saint-Jean-sur-Richelieu, Quebec, Canada as  a small manufacturing company with only 4 employees. Today the company includes three divisions: Railway, Petroleum  and Industrial with more then 40 full time employees.  DLL Inc serves the Railway, the Petroleum and the Industrial  market through its activities in the fields of manufacturing  new products. DLL Inc also supply rebuild parts as Utex,  Outright or on Repair-Return base. The company&rsquo;s expertise  lies in the design, development and manufacture of a  comprehensive range of electrical and mechanical components,  while maintaining good quality, reasonable price level and  quick turnarounds.</p>', ''),
(259, 1, 'Tri Pac Inc.', 'sales@tripacinc.com', '300 Gage Ave, KITCHENER, Ontario, , ', 'tripacinc.com', '+1 (519) 745-5925 ', '+1 (519) 745-7582 ', '', '<p>Tri Pac Inc has been in the plastics packaging business for over 20 years. We have teamed up with some of the best plastics companies in the world, to offer our customers the very best in pricing, service and quality. Unlike most plastic manufacturers that are limited to certain types of products or plastics, Tri Pac has the ability to manufacture, and distribute virtually any type of flexible plastic. If we are unable to make it in one of our facilities, we have a partner that has the ability. Tri Pac is still a family run and operated business caring for each customer, on a personal level. Tri Pac is able to fill the smallest single order, up to multi national markets. Tri Pac is a company that not only is keeping up with the times, but has always stayed ahead of the market.  We are also a manufacturing Representative of a complete line of Polyethylene Bags and Films. Over forty years experience to draw from in the blown film industry.</p>', ''),
(260, 1, 'Malley Industries Inc.', 'gatekeeper@malleyindustries.com', '561 Ferdinand Blvd, DIEPPE, New Brunswick, , ', 'www.malleyindustries.com', '+1 (506) 859-8591', '+1 (506) 857-1745', '', '<p>Established in 1979, the company is a manufacturer and distributor of specialty vehicles; including advanced life support ambulances, custom commercial vehicles and components, rescue units, specialized police and emergency vehicles, mobile shelters, laboratories and command posts. Malley Industries is one of Canada\'s largest vehicle adaptive mobility equipment dealers / installers, specializing in lowered floor, raised roof / raised door conversions, high tech driving aids and wheelchair lift installations.   The company has two facilities in the Greater Moncton area, both within close proximity to major roadways, air and rail links. We have supplied specialized vehicles and custom-designed components to Canada, Mexico, Ireland, the U.S., and the Caribbean. Currently, we are expanding to include a broader range of targeted North American and world markets.   Malley Industries produces in excess of 700 vehicle conversions each year for a wide variety of public &amp; private clients.</p>', ''),
(261, 1, 'StarFish Medical ', 'kstrange@starfishmedical.com', '5-555 Adersier Rd, VICTORIA, British Columbia, , ', 'www.starfishmedical.com', '+1 (250) 388-3537', '+1 (250) 483-1957', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\">The StarFish Group helps medical device companies innovate. We provide design, prototype, and manufacturing capability. StarFish Medical is a multidiscipline team of engineers, physics and industrial designer, with an average of 15 years of engineering experience or more.&#65279; We excel in challenges involving the significant engineering of electro-mechanical devices that require expertise in issues, such as optics, spectroscopy, magnetics, acoustics ,&#65279;ultrasonics and manufacturing. Our expertise in engineering is equalled by our&#65279; knowledge&#65279; of the regulatory processes in Canada, Europe and the US.&#65279; The &#65279;StarFish group is fully ISO Certified and handles the manufacturing for many of our clients. We are always looking for bright people, perhaps you have the skills we need? Careers at StarFish Medical.</p>', ''),
(262, 1, 'ADHPRO ADHESIVES INC.', 'president@adhpro.com', '1650, boul. Industriel, MAGOG - Quebec, , ', 'www.adhpro.com', '+1 (819) 847-2269 ', '+1 (819) 847-4990 ', '', '<p>Adhpro Adhesives Inc. has been established since 1990. We develop and manufacture adhesives for industrial and commercial use. Primarily centred towards the paper and carton industry, we are also committed to the following fields :  Carpentry, Commercial construction, Coating and varnish, Labelling, Printing and bookbinding, Textile and clothing. Adhpro Adhesives Inc. is a young company that is expanding their skills from coast to coast. The Head Office is situated in Magog, Qu&eacute;bec.  Adhpro Adhesives Maritimes Inc. offices and manufacturing plant are located in Darmouth, Nova Scotia. Adhpro Adhesives - Ontario sales office is situated in Toronto, Ontario. The West Coast is serviced by our distributors.  A service combining by quality and efficency, supported by a dedicated technical team, We have the qualifications to serve industries that are searching for products of quality that perform without conditions.</p>', ''),
(263, 1, 'WD Plastics Ltd. ', 'wdplastics@shaw.ca', '826-56th St. E., SASKATOON, Saskatchewan, , ', 'www.wdplastics.com', '(306) 934-6844 ', '(306) 934-6842 ', '', '<p>about wdplastics..................  We are Saskatchewans premiere plastics molding company. Founded in 1993, WD continues to move forward in our capability to remain the &quot;best in the industry&quot;.   WD Plastics desires to offer customers a &ldquo;total solution&rdquo; to their plastic material needs. From our manufacturing capabilities and large plastics inventory through to our in-house mold manufacturing and CAD operators, we are commitied to you, our customer, on providing exceptional service.</p>', ''),
