(325, 1, 'Canadian Dip Mouldings Inc. ', 'cd1@bellnet.ca ', '798 Fuller Ave., PENETANGUISHENE, Ontario, , ', 'www.manta.com/coms2/dnbcompany_lyd73t ', '+1 (705) 549-0030', '+1 (705) 549-0034', '', '<p>\r\n\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\r\n\n<meta name=\"ProgId\" content=\"PowerPoint.Slide\">\r\n\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Microsoft PowerPoint 12\"> </meta>\r\n\n</meta>\r\n\n</meta>\r\n\n</p>\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">About Canadian Dip Mouldings Inc.</span></p>\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 4pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\"><br />\r\n\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">Throughout Canadian Dip Mouldings working history they have served as a problem solver for customers of Dip Mouldings or Power Coatings. Canadian Dip Mouldings takes pride in bringing you the latest in state of the art technology in this field. Providing you with the initial design, through production of the moulds, manufacture of the materials and final production. Every step of the process is performed efficiently, resulting in custom vinyl dip mouldings of the highest quality - delivered on time. Our design engineers will work with you to develop and produce a custom moulding for Original Equipment Manufacturers associated with practically every industry from automotive to consumers products, communications, electrical and medical applications. Any specifications you have to conform to, such as C.S.A., F.D.A., U.L., F.B.M.S., A.S.T.M., S.A.E., etc., just give us a <br />\r\n\ncopy of the appropriate number and challenge Canadian Dip Mouldings to provide you with a durable Powder Coating or Dip Moulding that will withstand the harshest of environments at reasonable cost to suit your budget. Solve design problems economically, practically, precisely with vinyl dip mouldings by the industry\'s standard.</span></p>\r\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 4pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\"><br />\r\n\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">Canadian Dip Mouldings Inc. - We\'ve done it for major automotive, appliance, air craft, construction, electrical, food industry and health care. Product manufactured time and time again. Our technical expertise and years of experience in manufacturing custom PVC mouldings and powder coatings has earned us a reputation for reliability and performance our customers depend on.</span></p>\r\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', ''),
