(1918, 1, 'Techno-Logic Machining Inc. ', 'bdevereaux@t-logic.ca', 'P.O. Box 290 , MONCTON, New Brunswick, , ', 'www.t-logic.ca', '+1 (506) 389-3956', '+1 (506) 855-4686', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; unicode-bidi: embed; direction: ltr; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black; font-size: 10pt\">Techno-Logic  Machining is an innovative company involved in Plant Automation, custom  machine design, equipment refurbishing, component manufacturing,  hydraulic and machining services. The company has been in operation  since April, 1997 and was incorporated in May, 1998 in the province of  New Brunswick. The company currently employs 28 people and is located in  the Caledonia Industrial Park in Moncton, New Brunswick.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nT-Logic has built its foundation providing design engineering and  manufacturing of automated production machinery to clients in the saw  mill, value added wood processing, furniture, window and door, and sheet  metal industries. T-Logic recently received the award for Excellence in  Innovation 2003 from the Greater Moncton Chamber of Commerce. With a  proven track record for creating innovative solutions to production  problems and in-efficiencies and having established credibility with  large firms such as the Irving Group, </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', ''),
(1916, 1, 'TECHMIRE', 'info@techmire.com', '185 rue Voyageur, Pointe-Claire, QuÃ©bec , , ', 'www.techmire.com', '+1 (514) 694-4110', '+1 (514) 694-2634', '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Techmire is the world  leader in the design and manufacture of multiple-slide die-casting  systems for precision components in zinc, lead and magnesium alloys.  Located in Montreal, Canada, Techmire has full turnkey systems  capability, including design, manufacture and testing of die-casting  machines and fully automated insert die cast systems; training of  customers\' operators and maintenance personnel, and full after-sales  service. Re-manufacturing of Techmire die-casting systems and major  components are also undertaken. Techmire\'s line of multiple-slide, hot  chamber machines has the capability to economically produce complex  zinc, magnesium and lead parts. The machines feature: &middot; Fully automatic  operation for the highest degree of repeatability and reliability. &middot;  Parting line injection to significantly improve the shot-weight to  part-weight ratio, by eliminating the sprue and reducing the runner  system to a minimum. This results in savings in raw materials, lower  energy costs</p>', ''),
(1917, 1, 'Techniserv AG Inc. ', 'info@techniserv.ca ', '3420, 1st St, SAINT-HUBERT, Quebec, , ', 'www.techniserv.ca', '+1 (450) 443-3658', '+1 (450) 443-3142', '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Welcome to Techniserv</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">At Techniserv AG Inc we  are committed to providing you with quality electronic and electric  control systems &amp; panels that suit your specific requirements. Our  team of qualified engineers and technicians have met the expectations of  our clients since 1972.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Our services are sought  after by a wide range of small to large companies that count on our  expertise, efficiency and competitive prices to help them with simple  and complex control systems &amp; panels and electronic control  systems/products requirements.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Whether you are a plant  engineer, consultant, contractor or equipment manufacturer, our team is  ready to discuss your requirements and offer you the optimum solutions.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" class=\"MsoNormal\">Just get in touch with us and we&rsquo;ll take it from there!</p>', ''),
(372, 1, 'Avior Integrated Products Inc.', 'jmarcheschi@avior.ca', '1001 Aut. 440 Laval W, LAVAL - Quebec, , ', 'www.avior.ca', '+1 (450) 629-6200 ', '+1 (514) 324-6241 ', '', '<p>\r\n<meta content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" http-equiv=\"Content-Type\">\r\n<meta content=\"PowerPoint.Slide\" name=\"ProgId\">\r\n<meta content=\"Microsoft PowerPoint 12\" name=\"Generator\">     </meta>\r\n</meta>\r\n</meta>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">Avior Integrated Products Inc. is a full-service supplier of lightweight structural assemblies for the international aerospace industry. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\"><br />\r\nThe company&rsquo;s core manufacturing operations include manufacturing capabilities for composites, metal or hybrid details and sub-assemblies.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\"><br />\r\nEngineering is a core competency with research &amp; development of new products, prototypes, qualification, certification to OEM or Aviation norms and product support.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\"><br />\r\nAvior Integrated Products, Metal Products Division\'s (Laval, Quebec), 68 444 square feet (6 358 square meters) expertise is the fabrication of lightweight structures for the aerospace industry. The 