(440, 1, 'DICA Electronics Ltd. ', 'info@dica.ca', '160 Industrial Ave., CARLETON PLACE, Ontario, , ', 'www.dica.ca', '+1 (613) 257-5379', '+1 (613) 257-8430', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">DICA was established in 1983 as a high-quality Printed Circuit Board assembly facility in response to the rapid growth in the Ottawa hi-tech industry. Since then, DICA has established itself as a valuable and reliable supplier to many Ottawa area technology companies by providing high quality and cost efficient assembly services<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">DICA&rsquo;s competitive advantage is its ability to integrate and co-ordinate its highly skilled production team, state-of-the art production equipment, and its expansive supply chain network to provide unparalleled manufacturing services that meet not only DICA&rsquo;s strict quality standards, but also those of industry leaders in fiber optics, telecommunications, and the military<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We pride ourselves in our manufacturing flexibility that allows customers to implement design changes on the fly with a minimum of production delay. With a reputation of being able to turn on a dime, DICA&rsquo;s customer list reads like who&rsquo;s who of Silicon Valley North.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
