(453, 1, 'Socomec Industriel ', 'socomec@socomec.ca', '3200, rue des Chantiers, SOREL-TRACY, QuÃ©bec, , ', 'www.socomec.ca', '+1 (450) 743-0017', '+1 (450) 743-2654 ', '', '<p>\r\n\n<meta content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" />\r\n\n<meta content=\"PowerPoint.Slide\" name=\"ProgId\" />\r\n\n<meta content=\"Microsoft PowerPoint 12\" name=\"Generator\" />\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">Socomec Industriel is a specialized general contractor in heavy industries. This is covering all aspects in the installation of mechanical equipment and piping manufacturing in our own shops.</span></p>\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\"> </span></p>\r\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;; color: black;\">Rigorous standards and constant growth Socomec Industriel Inc. is primarily engaged in major projects that often require the plant to fabricate and install carbon steel, stainless steel or fiberglass components. The scope and quality of the work performed at Socomec Industriel Inc. meet very stringent standards. Certified ISO 9001-2000 since two years, Socomec is justly proud of this certification, as it reassures its customers that the products and services the company offers meet or exceed their requirements. The level of business activity has seen constant growth, making the company a key player in the development of the Sorel-Tracy region. Its annual sales figures lie between 15 and 20 million dollars.</span></p>\r\n\n<p style=