(459, 1, 'Canadian Exports Corp.', 'info@canadianexports.org', '1315 Jules-Poitras, Suite: 202, Montreal - Qc, , ', 'www.canadianexports.org', '+1-877-575-2022', '+1-514-331-4775', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Welcome to Canada&rsquo;s first and only, Export Promotion Tool .  &ldquo;Canadian Exports&rdquo; is a publication that helps International importers source the products and services they need from Canada.  We offer assistance and guidance throughout the import/export process. You are welcome to contact us at any step of the way. Our services are:     1. Identifying and checking out any Canadian businesses for you.    2. Helping you contact them.    3. Facilitating your negotiations with them.    4. Arranging business travels to meet with them.    5. Informing you about Trade Missions, Business Delegations, Trade Fairs, Payment Terms and much more.  To receive &ldquo;Canadian Exports&rdquo; publication, contact the Canadian business council or chamber of commerce in your country. Or, follow the link &ldquo;Join our Mailing List&rdquo; above and we will e-mail it to you for free. Be sure to visit our website frequently as it is updated daily. Contact us for all your inquiries.  About Us (What is Canadian Exports) .  &ldquo;Canadian Exports&rdquo; is a publication that matches Canadian &amp; International businesses;      * Helps them find each other.     * Helps them meet.     * Helps them conclude successful business transactions.  It is issued by &ldquo;Canadian Exports Inc&rdquo;, a Canadian company located in Montreal &ndash; Canada. &ldquo;Canadian Exports Inc&rdquo; offers a wide range of export-related consulting services that cover the entire import/export process. Our services are:      * Identifying and checking out any market and/or business for you.     * Helping you contact them.     * Facilitating your negotiations with them.     * Arranging business travels to meet with them.     * Informing you about Trade Missions, Business Delegations, Trade Fairs, Payment Terms and much more.  Contact us for more information to grow your business.</p>', '');
., BRACEBRIDGE, Ontario, , ', 'www.wilshireworks.com', '+1 (705) 706-0227 ', '+1 (705) 646-2922', '', '<p>Wilshire Works Inc. - Who Are We? Wilshire Works Inc. is a Canadian-based healthcare product manufacturing company that provides infection control solutions benefiting hospitals and long term care facilities worldwide. We develop products based on workplace needs shared by frontline healthcare staff and create commercially viable solutions using CAD design, modeling and prototyping techniques. As a business we can compete worldwide through the utilization of state-of-the-art automatic PLC controlled manufacturing equipment. Wilshire Works Inc. takes great pride in our quality products and attention to customer service. Our product development team is always up for new design challenges with commercial potential. Please contact us if you have a good idea that we can help you commercialize. Wilshire Works welcomes good ideas from frontline healthcare staff and offers royalty based remuneration.</p>', ''),
(467, 1, 'Yes Biotech Laboratories Ltd.', 'info@yesbiotech.co', '23-2355 Derry Rd. E., MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, , ', 'www.yesbiotech.com', '+1 (905) 677-9221', '+1 (905) 677-0023', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anogen - trade name of Yes Biotech Laboratories Ltd., a Canadian biopharmaceutical company located in Ontario, Canada. We have been producing antibody products for research, diagnostic and therapeutic applications for more than twenty-five years. Our broad technology platform enables us to design and develop a variety of products including monoclonal and polyclonal antibodies, immunoassay kits, matched antibody pairs, immunoglobulin, bioactive peptides, recombinant proteins and humanized monoclonal antibodies with high producers. We distribute our products world widely. Our name is a recognized quality supplier to many large antibody syndicates and suppliers.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">We are committed to developing and commercializing antibody-related therapeutics and diagnostics to combat various diseases including inflammatory and autoimmune disorders, cardiovascular diseases and cancer. Anogen\'s major project is advancing a New Bio-Defense Strategy to prevent &quot;Cytokine Storm&quot; using their anti-cytokine antibodies.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">To ensure that our customers are provided with the highest level of quality products and services, we have registered under the international organization for standards. We are certified ISO 13485 Medical Devices under the general practice of the ISO 9001 Quality System.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(469, 1, 'Centennial Solar ', 'info@centennialglobaltechnology.com', '8114B Trans-Canada Hwy, SAINT-LAURENT, Quebec, , ', 'www.centennialglobaltechnology.com', '+1 (450) 424-7532', '+1 (514) 461-9824', '', '<p>CentennialSolar is a Canadian-based company involved in the photovoltaic industry.  As an eco-friendly 				company, our goal is to promote the use of renewable energy sources; more precisely we are committed to 				solar-power systems.</p>\r\n<p>Benefiting from already available components from across the globe, our company is positioned as an 					integrator for the design of low-cost energy solutions.  Using best-of-breed components  from across 					the world (Germany, Italy, USA, Canada, etc), we manufacture solar panels that are amongst  the most 					efficient on the marketplace today.</p>\r\n<p>Our manufacturing plant can produce solar panels in the range of as little as 5 watts, up to 250 watts. 					Some of our panels  have the IEC 61215 certification therefore  we use materials that insure 					lightweight and robustness in extreme conditions.  We  offer both Polycrystalline and Thin Film 					modules, based on what our clients require.  In order to better serve the marketplace, we also offer 					custom panels for projects requiring specific orders.</p>', ''),
(470, 1, 'Centennial Solar ', 'info@centennialglobaltechnology.com', '8114B Trans-Canada Hwy, SAINT-LAURENT, Quebec, , ', 'www.centennialglobaltechnology.com', '+1 (450) 424-7532', '+1 (514) 461-9824', '', '<p>CentennialSolar is a Canadian-based company involved in the photovoltaic industry. As an eco-friendly company, our goal is to promote the use of renewable energy sources; more precisely we are committed to solar-power systems.</p>\r\n<p>Benefiting from already available components from across the globe, our company is positioned as an integrator for the design of low-cost energy solutions. Using best-of-breed components from across the world (Germany, Italy, USA, Canada, etc), we manufacture solar panels that are amongst the most efficient on the marketplace today.</p>\r\n<p>Our manufacturing plant can produce solar panels in the range of as little as 5 watts, up to 250 watts. Some of our panels have the IEC 61215 certification therefore we use materials that insure lightweight and robustness in extreme conditions. We offer both Polycrystalline and Thin Film modules, based on what our clients require. In order to better serve the marketplace, we also offer custom panels for projects requiring specific orders.</p>', ''),
(471, 1, 'Centennial Solar ', 'info@centennialglobaltechnology.com', '8114B Trans-Canada Hwy, SAINT-LAURENT, Quebec, , ', 'www.centennialglobaltechnology.com', '+1 (450) 424-7532', '+1 (514) 461-9824', '', '<p>CentennialSolar is a Canadian-based company involved in the photovoltaic industry. As an eco-friendly company, our goal is to promote the use of renewable energy sources; more precisely we are committed to solar-power systems.</p>\r\n<p>Benefiting from already available components from across the globe, our company is positioned as an integrator for the design of low-cost energy solutions. Using best-of-breed components from across the world (Germany, Italy, USA, Canada, etc), we manufacture solar panels that are amongst the most efficient on the marketplace today.</p>\r\n<p>Our manufacturing plant can produce solar panels in the range of as little as 5 watts, up to 250 watts. Some of our panels have the IEC 61215 certification therefore we use materials that insure lightweight and robustness in extreme conditions. We offer both Polycrystalline and Thin Film modules, based on what our clients require. In order to better serve the marketplace, we also offer custom panels for projects requiring specific orders.</p>', ''),
