(510, 52, 'Top Option Mortgage', 'info@topoptionmortgage.ca', '200 - 4257 Sherwoodtowne Boulevard, Mississauga, Ontario, Canada', 'http://www.topoptionmortgage.ca', '866-899-0156', '', '', '<p>In Toronto, Ontario, and all across Canada, <a href=\"http://www.topoptionmortgage.ca\" target=\"_blank\">Top Option Mortgage</a> is the first choice for customized lending services. As a Toronto mortgage broker, we provide a full-service experience to our customers that is unmatched in the region, and our rates can&rsquo;t be beat.</p>', ''),
