(521, 68, 'Holley Home Inspections', 'info@holleyhomeinspections.ca', '14 Hillborn Ave, Toronto, Ontario, Canada', 'http://www.holleyhomeinspections.ca/', '', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;<strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px; text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">In 2009, after 30 years of building quality new homes and renovating old ones</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19.5px; text-align: justify;\">, Mike Holley decided to change his focus. Instead of building homes, he wanted to focus on inspecting them &ndash; on making sure that new and young home buyers got what they paid for and received no nasty surprises after making their purchase.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(145, 144, 144); font-family: arial; line-height: 19.5px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(145, 144, 144); font-family: arial; line-height: 19.5px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">Mike became a certified home inspector.</strong>&nbsp;He applied for, and passed, the necessary inspection certifications for the&nbsp;Canadian Association of Home and Property Inspectors&nbsp;(CAHPI) and the&nbsp;Ontario Association of Home Inspectors&nbsp;(OAHI) and subsequently &ldquo;interned&rdquo; with one of Ontario&rsquo;s largest professional home inspector agencies. Around his 30 years of experience, and his certifications, he formed Holley Home Inspections.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(145, 144, 144); font-family: arial; line-height: 19.5px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(145, 144, 144); font-family: arial; line-height: 19.5px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">The idea for Mike&rsquo;s home inspection business</strong>&nbsp;was to focus his experience and skills on inspecting homes in west Toronto &ndash; the same area where he had spent years renovating or building homes of every type. His idea was particularly to cater to new buyers &ndash; the less experienced buyer - and to make sure new home buyers had a first-rate and thorough inspection, but also a resource to consult&nbsp;<em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">after</em>&nbsp;the purchase as they begin to confront the realities of their new purchase.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(145, 144, 144); font-family: arial; line-height: 19.5px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(145, 144, 144); font-family: arial; line-height: 19.5px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(70, 70, 70);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">Today, Mike inspects dozens of homes a week and enjoys the privilege</strong>&nbsp;of helping home buyers, home sellers, and real estate agents complete quality-based purchase transactions.&nbsp;</span></p>', ''),
(522, 68, 'FDA Construction', 'info@fdaconstruction.com', '181, rue de Plaisance, Terrebonne, Quebec, Canada', 'http://fdaconstruction.com/', '514-513-7020', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">FDA Construction is one of Montreal\'s most versatile commercial construction, construction planning, construction management and turnkey construction specialists.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Founded in 2005, the company focuses on challenging construction projects whether they be challenging in their very nature, or by virtue of an aggressive schedule, unusual venue, or a tight budget. Since it\'s formation, FDA Construction has established an enviable track record in quality construction practice for office renovations, unique additions and new construction projects, retail design/build projects and commercial rooftop add-ons.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">At the core of FDA Construction expertise is a small cadre of experienced engineers and contractors with a broad range of commercial construction experience. This team is supported by a proven and loyal troupe of local trades groups.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">If you have a unique commercial project - small or large - or if you need experienced construction management, contact us and we\'ll show you exactly what we can do for you.<o:p></o:p></p>', ''),
(523, 68, 'JT Promotions', 'info@jtadspecialtiessportswear.ca', '30 Lakeshore Drive, Hastings, Ontario, Canada', 'http://jtadspecialtiessportswear.ca/', '(705) 696-3320', '', '', '<p>&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-family: arial; line-height: 20px;\">Based in Hastings, Ontario, JT Promotions has been offering</strong><span style=\"font-family: arial; line-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: arial; line-height: 20px;\">its advertising specialty products to businesses, not-for-profit agencies, and government institutions in Ontario for more than 14 years. &nbsp;We service a variety of customers, both large and small, local, provincial and national. &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-family: arial; line-height: 20px;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 1.538em;\">Our company specializes in customized and logoed sportswear</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.538em;\">&nbsp;but also offers, buttons, badges, pens, executive gifts and other personalized or branded items.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-family: arial; line-height: 20px;\"><strong>We serve organizations as far away as Huntsville</strong>&nbsp;but most of our customers come from Peterborough, Cobourg, Belleville, Oshawa, Port Hope, Warkworth, Brighton, Bowmanville, Hastings, and other nearby communities.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; font-family: arial; line-height: 20px;\"><strong>If you\'re looking for a creative way</strong>&nbsp;to advance your business, team, office or organization, please&nbsp;<a href=\"http://jtadspecialtiessportswear.ca/contact-us\">contact us</a>.</p>', ''),
