(525, 79, 'MobyServices', 'fieldservicemanagement@yahoo.com', '1050 Stainton Drive, Unit #136,, Mississauga, Ontario, Canada', 'http://www.fieldservicemanagement.ca/', '416-566-6024', '', '', '<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px 13px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\">Effective Field Service management solution is paramount to manage skilled technicians and dispatch them to repair site to adeptly locate faults and leverage various solutions. The quality of your service depends upon various factors like timely and accurate communication about customer equipment and past repair history. That\'s why most of the organizations stress on maintaining the proper maintenance records available to the service engineers. Another important aspect of the maintenance is spares and tools (material management). The quality of your service directly affects the business continuity of your customer. To improve the communication and past history you should deploy proficient IT support processes, which gives you an efficient field service management system, which results in enhanced customer service and experience.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 5px 0px 13px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 13px; line-height: 22px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\">MobyService offers very effective Hosted Field Service solution, it includes the use of Mobile and Web enabled tools, which helps the technician to access the relevant information. With complete history of equipment and spares, your service personnel can offer unmatched quality service, which leaves a lasting impression on your customer.</p>', ''),
